\toc1 Y…õb…ôc ya Asom a Yesu
\mt1 Y…õb…ôc ya Asom a Yesu
\c 1
\s1 As…ĒŇč asom a Yesu temer ta k…ôder ka Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu
\p 
\v 1 Wanapa Teyofil,
\p Inacic…ôs kitabu kem k…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē disr…õ mes mm…õ Yesu …õnacop k…ôy…Ē k…Ē k…ôt…ôks…õ m…Ē,
\v 2 haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ anap…õn…õ k…Ē darenc, nt…õ elip k…ôsom asom …Ēn Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu disr…õ, aŇč…õ …õnay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.
\v 3 Asom akak…Ē Ňč…Ē Yesu …õnament…ôr kance ka mes m…õlar…ôm nt…õ …õnay…õf…õ pucuy pa defi m…Ē. K'owur…ôr Ňča mata 40 p…ôyi w…ôy…õŇč, p…ôcloku Ňča mes ma d…õb…õ da Kanu.
\v 4 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma nt…õ Ňčayi k…ôdi yeri k…Ē Yesu m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęTa n…ôb…Ēl…õ dare da Yerusal…õm, mba n…ôkar tes nt…õ Papa …õnas…ĒŇč temer k…ôdes…ĒŇč m…Ē, t…Ēk…Ē n…ônane icloku m…Ē:
\v 5 D…ôromun SaŇč …õncgb…ôt afum teta Kanu, mba n…ôna k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun d…ôAmera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu disr…õ k…Ē n…ôndes…Ēt…Ē mata mam…õ.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôp…õ ka Yesu d…ôk…Ēm
\p 
\v 6 Ak…Ē ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ m…Ē k…Ē Ňčayif Yesu: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, t…õm tant…õ t…Ē m…ôndelomp…ôs…õ Yisrayel d…õb…õ ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 K'oloku Ňča: ¬ęT…õnc…ôm…õ f…õ nu d…Ēp…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ ka t…õm k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Apa Kanu …õnc…õmc…õmn…õ k…ôy…Ē t…õfaŇč t…Ēn k…ôtam k…Ēn disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 8 Mba n…ôndes…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčendeder nu-…õ, t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôndey…Ēn…õ at…ôŇčn…õ aŇč…õ mes mencep…ôr f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč m…Ē nde dare da Yerusal…õm, at…Ēf Ňča Yude f…ôp k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Samari k…ôk…Ēb…ôp c…ôp…ôc ca doru f…ôp.¬Ľ
\v 9 Nt…õ elip k…ôloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp Ňčanagb…ôtn…õ Yesu nt…õ ancp…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôp k…ôŇčkump k…Ē, Ňčanctam f…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē.
\v 10 Nt…õ Asom …Ēn Ňčanagb…ôtn…õ k…Ēm Yesu p…ôcp…õ darenc m…Ē haŇč k'…Ēs…Ēl…õ. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…õr…ôŇč m…õmb…õrn…õ yamos yomot…ôr-mot…ôr mement…ôrn…õ Ňča,
\v 11 k…Ē moloku: ¬ęAfum a Kalile, ta ake t…Ē n…ônc…ôm…õn…õ k…ôm…Ēm…ôn k…Ēm-…õ? Yesu, w…ôkak…Ē …õmp…õ d…ôk…Ēm f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč m…Ē, tant…õ n…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ē p…ôcp…õ m…Ē, t'endes…Ē-der.¬Ľ
\s1 W…ôc…Ēnc ka Yudas
\p 
\v 12 K'asom a Yesu Ňčalukus Yerusal…õm k…ôy…õf…õ nde t…Ēr…Ē t…Ēk…Ē aŇčwe ¬ęT…Ēr…Ē ta t…Ēk ya \tl Olif\tl*¬Ľ, mp…õ p…Ēnt…Ēb…Ēl…õn…õ dare m…Ē. P…ôbol-bolu mp…õ din…õ da aSuyif doncwos…õ fum k…ôk…Ēt pab…ôp simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē.
\v 13 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ dare m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamp…õ d…ôk…ôl…Ē da k…ôroŇč nde Ňčancnd…õ m…Ē. Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē: Piy…õr, IsaŇč, Sak k…Ē And…ôre, Filip k…Ē T…Ēma, Bartelemy k…Ē Matiye, Sak wan ka Alfe, Sim…ĒŇč w…ôsims…õ teta at…Ēf, k…Ē Yudas wan ka Sak.
\v 14 F…ôp faŇčan k…ôfo kin k…Ē Ňčanck…Ē k…ôtola Kanu t…õm o t…õm k…Ē aran, k…ôb…ôp ka aw…õnc a Yesu, k…Ē iya k…Ēn Mari.
\p 
\v 15 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma mata mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē, Ňčanck…Ē haŇč afum tasar tin k…Ē w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč (120). K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ aw…õnc …Ēn dac…Ē, k'oloku:
\v 16 ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča: P…ônamar yecic…ôs ya d…ôkitabu y…õlar…õ. Ti disr…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu nŇč…õ Dawuda …õnanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôloku teta Yudas, nw…õ …õnasol…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanasump…ôr Yesu m…Ē.
\v 17 Anal…Ēm Yudas su dac…Ē, s…ôpaŇčn…õ y…õb…ôc yin yayi.
\v 18 Nt…õ elip k…ôs…Ēt…Ēn…õ ab…Ēf p…ôsam pa kiciya k…Ēn m…Ē, k'…õŇčgb…õkn…õ, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ tekiriŇč k'…õwalin…õ kor k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ sumpa s…Ēn f…ôp k…ôsams…ôr d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 19 Tes t…Ē nt…õ aka Yerusal…õm f…ôp Ňčanac…ôr…õ m…Ē, ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ pawe dal…õ dad…Ēk…Ē ‚ÄĻHakeldama‚Äļ, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē kusu k…ôŇčan ‚ÄĻDal…õ da mecir‚Äļ.\f + \fr 1:19 \ft ¬ęKiciya ka Yudas¬Ľ, m…ôm…Ēm…ôn Matiye 26.47-53, 27:3-8.\f*
\v 20 Bawo anacic nde Yabura Dawuda disr…õ:
\q1 ‚ÄĻK…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ôy…Ē fos,
\q1 ali fum ta p…ôyi ki!‚Äļ
\m K'…õnacic…ôs s…Ē:
\q1 ‚ÄĻW…ôl…Ēma p…ôl…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēn!‚Äļ \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Yabura 69.26; 109.8\x*
\m 
\v 21-22 M…õn…õ pam…Ēm…ôn…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčancc…ômb…ôr su t…õm nt…õ Yesu …õncp…õ p…ôctor k…Ē s…ôna m…Ē, m…õn…õ w…ôkin p…ôyi su dac…Ē nw…õ endey…Ēn…õ w…ôt…ôŇčn…õ mes mm…õ m…õnacep…ôr f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč k…ôy…õf…õ ka Yesu afi dac…Ē, m…õn…õ w…ôkayi s…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ônat…ôŇčn…õ mes f…ôp k…ôl…õk k…ôgb…ôt ka SaŇč teta Kanu, haŇč d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Yesu …õnay…õf…õ su dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 23 Awa k…Ē Ňčament…ôr afum m…õr…ôŇč: Matiyas, k…Ē Isifu nw…õ ancwe Barsabas, pacdeŇč…ôr k…Ē s…Ē tewe ta Yusutu.
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčantola Kanu nt…õ: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, m…ôna nw…õ m…ônc…ôr…õ b…ôk…ôc ya f…ôp m…Ē, m…ôment…ôr su gbasŇča w…ôkin nw…õ m…ôl…õk k…ôdec…Ēnc Yudas akaŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 25 T…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ w…ôkayi k…ôcop su dac…Ē y…õb…ôc y…Ēn, p…ôl…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ nd…õ Yudas …õnasak a k'…ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôfo nk…õ k…ômar k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 26 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkot yampuŇčpuŇč \f + \fr 1:26 \ft Nt…õ ŇčanafaŇč k…ôc…ôr…õ t…õfaŇč ta Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr ca yowur…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇč d…ôl…Ēba. Pin tewe ta Matiyas, p…Ēk…Ē tewe ta Barsabas. D…ôk…ôwur…õ da yi, k…Ē w…ôkin (Matiyas) …Ēs…Ēt…Ē.\f* k…Ē tosur…õn…õ Matiyas nw…õ anab…õr…õn…õ Asom aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin m…Ē.
\c 2
\s1 K…ôder ka Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ D…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôsata ka Tataka ta w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt d…õnab…ôp m…Ē, alaŇč a Yesu f…ôp ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ k…ôfo kin.\f + \fr 2:1 \fq K…ôsata ka Tataka ta w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt\ft : M…ôm…Ēm…ôn ALewy 23.15-21, Sariy…õ 16.9-11. It…Ē k…ôren o k…ôren aSuyif Ňčamboc k…ôsata ka k…ôt…õl tat…Ēk…Ē tataka ta w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50) k…Ē k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr k…ôncep…ôr-…õ.\f*
\v 2 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē pukul…õ p…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm mp…õ p…õnawur…õn…õ pukul…õ pa afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…Ē p…õlas k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē Ňčanand…õ disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē memer mowur…ôr Ňča mm…õ m…õnawur…õn…õ ma n…õnc m…Ē. K…Ē meyer…ôs…õn…õ f…ôp faŇčan, k…Ē temer t…õnt…ôpn…õ nw…õ o nw…õ d…ôtobu.
\v 4 K…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčender Ňča f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôc…Ēp nw…õ o nw…õ kusu k…ôcuru. Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēncs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…Ēp tat…Ēk…Ē.\f + \fr 2:4 \ft M…ôm…Ēm…ôn 1.5,8 (toloku ta k…ôs…ĒŇč temer Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu.) \f*
\p 
\v 5 Awa t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē aSuyif asump…ôr din…õ gbiŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp m…Ē, Ňčanand…õ dare da Yerusal…õm.
\v 6 Nt…õ Ňčane pukul…õ mp…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ē di. K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ acik…ôra f…ôp nt…õ Ňčane afum a Kalile Ňčacc…Ēp nw…õ o nw…õ kusu k'ac…ôk…ôra m…Ē.
\v 7 P…ôciyan…õ, k…Ē kusu k…ôwos kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ, k…Ē Ňčayif…õn…õ: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ Ňčalok-loku m…Ē, baf…Ē aka Kalile Ňč…Ē ba?
\v 8 Ake's…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ s…ôna dac…Ē, fum o fum ene Ňčacc…Ēp kusu k…Ēn m…Ē?
\v 9 AParto, aMede, aka Elam, aka Mesopotami, aka Yude, aka Kapados, aka Ponto, k…Ē aka Asi,
\v 10 aka Firiki, aka PaŇčfili, aka Misira, aka Libi and…õ a at…Ēf Ňča Sir…õn, aRom,
\v 11 aSuyif k…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčanctubucn…õ p…ôt…Ēt pa din…õ da aSuyif m…Ē: Aka Krit, aka Arabi, s…ôŇčne Ňča Ňčacloku cusu cosu mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč ma Kanu!¬Ľ
\v 12 K…Ē cusu c…ôwos Ňča k…Ē p…ôyi Ňča yamayama, k…Ē Ňčayif…õn…õ taŇčan: ¬ęC…ôke c…Ē tant…õ toloku-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 13 Mba k…Ē al…Ēma ŇčaŇčfani Ňča, Ňčacloku: ¬ęMember mobotu m…Ē Ňčan…õmb…ôr…õ!¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôcam ka Piy…õr
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k'…õnc…ôm…õ k…Ē asom a Yesu aŇč…õ w…ôco k…Ē pin, k'…õmp…õn…õ dim p…ôcloku k…ônay nk…õ: ¬ęAfum a Yude k…Ē n…ôna aŇč…õ n…ônd…õ dare da Yerusal…õm m…Ē, n…ôsu l…ôŇč…ôs, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl belbel moloku mem! N…ôc…ôr…õ ti:
\v 15 Afum akaŇč…õ Ňčancis f…õ p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē n…ôc…õmc…õmn…õ ti m…Ē, bawo b…ôtb…ôt b'ayi bamb…õ. \f + \fr 2:15 \fq Bawo b…ôtb…ôt b'ayi bamb…õ \ft = it…Ē kusu ka aka Kresi koloku: ¬ęDec maas da d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ē dand…õ¬Ľ = 9:00, b…ôrb…ôt. \f*
\v 16 Mba t…Ēk…Ē aŇčnabi Yow…õl …õnaloku m…Ē teyi k…ôcep…ôr:
\q1 
\v 17 ‚ÄĻK…Ē Kanu k…ôloku mata m…õlp…ôs:
\q1 ¬ęIndesams…ôr Amera Ňčem nn…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčayi m…Ē.
\q1 Awut anu arkun k…Ē aran Ňčande Ňčacd…ôŇčk c…ôsayib…õ-e.
\q1 Indes…ĒŇč awut at…õmp anu k…ôn…ôŇčk ka m…Ēy…Ē mem,
\q1 indew…õr…ôp…ôs s…Ē afum anu atem.‚Äļ
\q1 
\v 18 ‚ÄĻ∆źy,‚Äļ Kanu k…ôloku, ‚ÄĻIndeyer…ôs Amera Ňäecempi Ňčem acar em arkun k…Ē aran,
\q1 mata mam…Ēk…Ē, Ňčanded…ôŇčk c…ôsayib…õ-e.
\q1 
\v 19 Indement…ôr mes m…õw…õyw…õy m…õlar…ôm d…ôk…Ēm
\q1 k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ma Kanu nn…Ē d…ônt…Ēf: Mecir, n…õnc, k…Ē acul Ňča kinim…õ.
\q1 
\v 20 Dec dendes…ôkp…õ kubump,
\q1 k…Ē Ňčof Ňč…õs…ôkp…õ mecir.
\q1 Mam…Ēk…Ē mendecep…ôr a d…Ēs…Ēk da W…ôb…õ dedeb…ôp,
\q1 d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…õmb…õk k…Ē dentes…õ.
\q1 
\v 21 Nw…õ o nw…õ endekorn…õ Mariki m…Ē endefis.‚Äļ\x - \xo 2:21 \xt Yow…õl 2.28-32 \x*
\p 
\v 22 Afum aka Yisrayel, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mam…õ! : Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt, fum nw…õ Kanu k…ôment…ôr…õ nu debeki d…Ēn m…Ē, d…ômes m…õw…õy-w…õy, d…ôm…Ēp…ĒŇč, d…ôm…õgb…õk…ôr…õ p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē n…ônc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē,
\v 23 fum w…ôkaw…õ anas…ĒŇč nu k…ôdif k…Ēn p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônawos…õ ti k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč t…Ēk…Ēt…õn…õ ta ti m…Ē. N…ônim k…Ē n…ôncaŇč k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl k…ômar ka waca wa acik…ôra. \f + \fr 2:23 \fq Acik…ôra\ft = afum at…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr sariy…õ, at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif.\f*
\v 24 Kanu k…ôyekti k…Ē k…ôŇčgbint…ôr k…Ē p…ôcuy pa defi, bawo defi d…õnatam f…õ k…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ k…Ē.
\v 25 Dawuda …õnanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôloku d…ôyecic…ôs yecempi teta Yesu:
\q1 ‚ÄĻIncn…ôŇčk Mariki t…õm f…ôp f…Ēr yem kiriŇč,
\q1 if…Ēyikc…õ, bawo ey'im k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt.
\q1 
\v 26 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňčem Ňčeyi d…ôk…ôsata m…Ē, k…Ē temer tem tesik…ôl…õ d…ôp…ôbotu.
\q1 Dis dem yati dendek…ĒŇčes…ôm…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôr amera.
\q1 
\v 27 Bawo m…ôf…Ēdek…Ēsak im dabiya
\q1 m…ôf…Ēdek…Ēsak w…ôsoku kam p…ôte.
\q1 
\v 28 M…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôc…ôr…õ s…ôp…Ē sa k…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ doru,
\q1 kiyi kam ina k…ôs…ôk k…ôndek…Ēlas im p…ôbotu.‚Äļ\x - \xo 2:28 \xt Yabura 16.8-11\x*
\p 
\v 29 Aw…õnc im aŇča! N…ôwos…õ iloku nu nt…õ k…ôlaŇč disr…õ teta w…ôtem Dawuda: ∆źnafi, k'awup k…Ē, k…Ē kufu k…Ēn k…ôyi su s…Ē m…Ēk…Ē dac…Ē.
\v 30 Mba nt…õ Dawuda …õnay…Ēn…õ sayib…õ m…Ē, …õnc…ôr…õ s…Ē a Kanu k…ônad…õrm…õ k…Ē a k…ônded…ôs wans…Ē k…Ēn w…ôl…Ēma d…Ēc…Ēm da d…õb…õ d…Ēn k…ôroŇč.
\v 31 Dawuda …õnanuŇčk…õn…õ p…ôn…ôŇčk k…ôy…õf…õ ka Krist d…ôkufu \f + \fr 2:31 \fq Krist\ft = W…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē, W…ôy…õk-y…õk ka Kanu \f*, …õnan…ôŇčk nt…õ tendeder m…Ē k'oloku ti: a anasak f…õ Krist dabiya, dis d…Ēn d…õnate f…õ d…ôkufu.
\v 32 Yesu w…ôkak…Ē, Kanu k…ôyekti k…Ē, s…ôna f…ôp s…ôy…Ēn…õ sede aka ti.
\v 33 K…Ē Kanu k…ômp…õn…õ Yesu k…ôfo k…ôleli, k'…õnd…ôs k…Ē k…ôca k…Ēn k…ôt…Ēt. K…Ē Yesu …Ēs…Ēt…ôr nk…Ēn apa Kanu Amera Ňäecempi nŇč…õ analoku k…ôdes…ĒŇč m…Ē, k'eyer…ôs tat…Ēk…Ē n…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē n…ône m…Ē.
\p 
\v 34 Baf…Ē Dawuda …õnap…õ darenc, nk…Ēn yati oloku:
\q1 ‚ÄĻMariki Kanu oloku Mariki mem: ‚ÄĻM…ônd'em nn…Ē k…ôca kem k…ôt…Ēt,
\q1 
\v 35 haŇč iclip k…ôboc ater…õn…õ am w…õc…ôk wam d…ônt…Ēf m…ônas-nas Ňča.‚Äļ\x - \xo 2:35 \xt Yabura 110.1\x*
\p 
\v 36 P…ômar aka Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčac…ôr…õ ti belbel: Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Yesu k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôy…õk-y…õk k…Ēn, Yesu w…ôkak…Ē n…ôncaŇč d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 37 Nt…õ afum Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē mosump…ôr Ňča, k…Ē Ňčayif Piy…õr k…Ē asom a Yesu ak…Ē: ¬ęAw…õnc su aŇča, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar s…ôy…Ē oŇč-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 38 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôs…ôkp…ôr mera yonu, n…ôlomp! Nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun tewe ta Yesu Krist disr…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paŇčaŇč…ôn…õn…õ kiciya ka w…ôkayi m…Ē, n…ôndes…Ēt…Ē s…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu.
\v 39 Bawo, k…ôpoc…õ nk…õ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ temer m…Ē, konu k…Ē, k…Ē awut anu k…ôb…ôp ka ak…Ē Ňčayi p…ôb…Ēl…õ m…Ē, haŇč k…ônay ka afum nk…õ W…ôb…õ Kanu kosu endewe m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 40 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku Ňča s…Ē moloku m…õlar…ôm nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčanen…õ k…Ē mes mm…õ m…õnacep…ôr f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč m…Ē. K'eŇčgbiŇč…ôr Ňča, p…ôcloku: ¬ęN…ôyacn…õ d…õt…õmp dand…õ d…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ-kaf…ôl…õ m…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 41 Afum alar…ôm Ňčawos…õ k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu. D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē afum wul maas (3.000) Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ ak…Ē ŇčananuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôlaŇč m…Ē.
\p 
\v 42 K…Ē Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl t…õm f…ôp k…Ē belbel m…õt…ôks…õ ma asom a Yesu, kiyi k…ôŇčan tes tin, k…ôpaŇčn…õ k…ôŇčan dap da yeri,\f + \fr 2:42 \fq K…ôpaŇčn…õ k…ôŇčan dap da yeri\ft = c…ôKresi ¬ęk…ôtep…õn…õ k…ôcom k…ôyer…õn…õ ki m…Ē¬Ľ \f* k…Ē k…ôtola Kanu.
\v 43 K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôsump…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ bawo Kanu k…ôncment…ôr…õ mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč k…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy m…õlar…ôm waca wa asom a Yesu.
\v 44 Ak…Ē ŇčanalaŇč m…Ē f…ôp Ňčanayi tes tin Ňčacyer…õn…õ mp…õ o mp…õ ŇčaŇčs…Ēt…Ē m…Ē.
\v 45 K…Ē Ňčancam…ôs daka d…Ēk…Ē Ňčanay…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayer p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē Ňčacm…Ēm…ôn t…Ēk…Ē p…ôcucan…õ pencep…ôr…õn…õ m…Ē.
\v 46 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk ŇčancloŇčkan…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, Ňčacdin…õn…õ yeri k…ôfo kin nde w…Ēl…Ē waŇčan, Ňčacdin…õ yi mera yobotu k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yoforu.
\v 47 Ňäackor-koru Kanu, k…Ē mes maŇčan m…Ēmb…Ēt afum f…ôp. K…Ē Mariki nk…Ēn …õmb…õr…õn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk k…ôgba ka aŇč…õ …õncyac m…Ē.
\c 3
\s1 W…ôb…ôc w…ôt…Ēk…Ēt …õntamn…õ
\p 
\v 1 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčamp…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu dec d…ôr…Ēf…Ēy, dec nd…õ antola Kanu m…Ē.
\v 2 Tosur…õn…õ pasar…õ w…ôb…ôc nw…õ aŇčkom…õ k…ôt…Ēk…Ēt m…Ē. D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk anckek…ôr…õ k…Ē pad…ôs nde kusuŇčka ka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu. D…ôndo w…ôb…ôc nw…õ onctolan…õ daka n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr disr…õ afum aŇč…õ Ňčancb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē. KusuŇčka nk…õ ancwe ¬ęKusuŇčka K…ôt…Ēt¬Ľ.
\v 3 Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanck…Ē k…ôb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôtola akak…Ē n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr disr…õ.
\v 4 Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč ŇčaŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ē, k…Ē Piy…õr oloku: ¬ęM…ôgb…ôtn…õ su!¬Ľ
\v 5 K'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ Ňča p…ôckar k…ôdes…Ēt…ôr Ňča paka p…Ēl…Ēm.
\p 
\v 6 Mba k…Ē Piy…õr oloku oŇč: ¬ęAli p…ôsam iy…Ē f…õ, mba mp…õ iy…Ē m…Ē, ip'indes…ĒŇč'…ôm: Tewe ta Yesu Krist w…ôka Nasar…õt, m…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôk…Ēt!¬Ľ
\v 7 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt k…Ē Ňčayekti, w…õc…ôk k…Ē m…Ēgb…Ēlk…Ēc m…Ēn y…õnc…ôp.
\v 8 K…ôs…Ērn…õ katin k'…õy…õf…õ k'…õnc…ôm…õ, k'…õl…õk w…õc…ôk k…ôk…Ēt. K'osol k…Ē Ňča, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ, p…ôck…Ēt, p…ôcyok…õ, p…ôckor-koru Kanu.
\v 9 K…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčan…ôŇčk fum nw…õ p…ôck…Ēt, p…ôckor-koru Kanu.
\v 10 Ancn…õp…ôl k…Ē, nk…Ēn …õncnd…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč nde ¬ęKusuŇčka K…ôt…Ēt¬Ľ, p…ôctolan…õ daka n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr disr…õ. K…ônes…õ k…Ē p…ôciyan…õ k…ômb…ôp afum f…ôp teta t…Ēk…Ē t…õnab…ôp k…Ē m…Ē.
\s1 Moloku ma Piy…õr nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu
\p 
\v 11 Nt…õ fum nw…õ …õnader p…ôyi oŇč ta …õŇčy…õf…õ Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē, k…ônes…õ disr…õ k…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ē nde ak…õr nŇč…õ aŇčwe ¬ęAk…õr Ňča Sulemani¬Ľ, nde Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčanayi m…Ē.
\v 12 Nt…õ Piy…õr …õn…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k'oloku afum: ¬ęAka Yisrayel! Ake's…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ tant…õ t'enciyan…õ nu m…Ē? T'ake t…Ē n…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õn…õ su p…ôm…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fosu, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, dosoku dosu disr…õ d…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ k…ôk…Ēt?
\v 13 Baf…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē de! Mba ti disr…õ, Kanu ka atem asu Kanu ka Abraham, Kanu ka Siyaka, k…Ē Kanu ka Yakuba k…ônayek-yek…ôs w…ômar…ôs k…Ēn Yesu. Mba nk…Ēn n…ôna n…ônal…õk, k…Ē n…ôs…ĒŇč ab…õ, n…ôce k…Ē f…Ēr ya Pilat kiriŇč, ali nt…õ Pilat …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôsak k…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 14 N…ôna n…ônace nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôcempi k…Ē w…ôlompu k…Ē n…ôloku a pawos…õ k…ôsak…õ nu w…ôdif…ôt afum dare disr…õ.
\v 15 N…ônadif w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka doru, mba Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē. S…ôn'…Ēy…Ēn…õ at…ôŇčn…õ aka ti.
\v 16 Anas…ĒŇč f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fum w…ôkaw…õ n…ôŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ē n…ônc…ôr…õ m…Ē. K…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Yesu gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč fum w…ôkaw…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. K…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Yesu k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôtamn…õ keŇč f…Ēr ya f…ôp fonu kiriŇč.
\p 
\v 17 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, aw…õnc im aŇča, inc…ôr…õ a k…ôt…Ēc…ôr…õ konu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ nu k…ôy…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē, n…ôna k…Ē ab…õ anu.
\v 18 Kanu k…ônalas t…Ēk…Ē k…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôlok…õ cusu ca sayib…õ …Ēn f…ôp m…Ē: A p…ônamar dis d…Ēl…Ēl Krist, w…ôy…õk-y…õk k…Ēn.
\v 19 N…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc yonu, n…ôluks…ôrn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paŇčaŇčn…õn…õ kiciya konu m…Ē,
\v 20 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ W…ôb…õ Kanu p…ôgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôk…õr…õ nu t…õm ta k…ôŇčes…ôm, Yesu nw…õ ananuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôy…õky…õk…õ nu m…Ē.
\v 21 Nk…Ēn k…Ēm k…ônt…Ēmp…ôr haŇč t…õm nt…õ mes mm…õ Kanu k…ônalok…õ t…õm tobol-bolu cusu ca sayib…õ …Ēn s…ôcempi m…Ē m…õlar…õ.
\v 22 AŇčnabi Musa …õnaloku: ‚ÄĻW…ôb…õ, Kanu konu, endek…õr…õ nu sayib…õ p…ôm…Ē ina. Fum w…ôkin w…ôka aw…õnc anu dac…Ē endeyi, n…ôde n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mam…Ēk…Ē ende p…ôcloku nu m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 23 Nw…õ o nw…õ …Ēnt…Ēdec…ôŇčk…ôl w…ôd…ôŇčk w…ôkak…Ē m…Ē, andel…ôs…ôr k…Ē. Endem…ôlk…õ afum a Kanu dac…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 3:23 \xt Sariy…õ 18.15,18,19\x*
\p 
\v 24 Sayib…õ f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ aŇčnabi Samiy…õl haŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanac…Ēnc k…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanaloku teta mataka mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčd…ôŇčk mi.
\v 25 N…ôna, awut a sayib…õ Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ, k…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē awut a temer t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônacaŇč…ôs k…Ē atem anu m…Ē, k…ôcloku Abraham: ‚ÄĻAfum a doru f…ôp Ňčandes…Ēt…Ē k…ôpoc…õ k…ôt…Ēt kem teta k…ôb…ônda ka dokom dam.‚Äļ\x - \xo 3:25 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 22.18; D…ôk…ôcop 26.4\x*
\v 26 Te tonu t…Ē, Kanu k…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôyekti w…ôcar k…Ēn, k'osom k…Ē k…ôdetolan…õ nu, p…ôs…ôkp…ôr nu nw…õ o nw…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēn Ňč…õl…õc, Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē Ňč…Ēt…Ēt.¬Ľ
\c 4
\s1 Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč f…Ēr ya aboc kiti aSuyif kiriŇč
\p 
\v 1 Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčanayi k…ôlok-lok…ôr afum t…õm nt…õ aloŇčn…õ a k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu Ňčanab…õr…õ k…Ē w…ôb…õ ka as…Ēdar aŇč…õ Ňčancbum ki m…Ē, k…Ē aSadisi.
\v 2 P…ônat…õl…õ Ňča nt…õ Ňčanane Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčact…ôks…õ afum a f…ôp f…ôndef…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē p…ôm…Ē nt…õ Yesu …Ēf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč, k…Ē Ňčand…ôs Ňča pacbum Ňča d…ôbili haŇč d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, bawo p…ônabiy…õ.
\v 4 Afum alar…ôm al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanane moloku maŇčan m…Ē, ŇčanalaŇč, d…õlay daŇčan d…õnab…ôp arkun wul k…ôcam…ôt (5.000).
\p 
\v 5 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk ab…õ aŇčan, abeki ap…ĒŇč a d…Ēt…Ēf, k…Ē at…ôks…õ a yecic…ôs ya AŇčnabi Musa Ňčamb…ôps…õn…õ Yerusal…õm
\v 6 k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč Anas, k…Ē Kayifa, IsaŇč, Al…õksand…ôr, k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ aka k…ôb…ônda ka dokom da aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč m…Ē.
\v 7 K…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč k…ôyif…ôt: ¬ęF…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôre, k…Ē tewe ta ana t…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ tant…õ-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 8 Awa k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õlar…õ Piy…õr, k…Ē Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôloku Ňča: ¬ęAb…õ a afum k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf:
\v 9 Ayif…ôt su m…Ēk…Ē teta p…ôt…Ēt mp…õ ay…Ēn…õ w…ôlanyuru m…Ē, k…Ē nt…õ antam…ôs k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 10 N…ôc…ôr…õ ti belbel, f…ôp fonu k…ôb…ôp ka aYisrayel: Tewe ta Yesu Krist w…ôka Nasar…õt, w…ôk…Ē n…ônacaŇč d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl, ak…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē, tewe t…Ēn t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ fum w…ôkaw…õ …õnc…ôm…õ nu dac…Ē p…ôtamn…õ m…Ē.
\v 11 Nk…Ēn Yesu ‚ÄĻ…Ēy…Ēn…õ togbu mp…õ n…ôna ac…ômb…ôr k…ôl…Ē n…ônafani m…Ē, mba …õnay…Ēn…õ togbu p…Ēt…Ēt pa dac…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 4:11 \xt Yabura 118.22\x*
\v 12 Nk…Ēn gb…ôc…ôr…ôm …õntam k…ôs…ĒŇč su k…ôfis. Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč f…õ tewe t…Ēl…Ēma ta fum nn…Ē doru dand…õ nt…õ p…ômar payacn…õn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 Nt…õ abeki aŇč…õ Ňčan…ôŇčk Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčab…ôkn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônciyan…õ Ňča, bawo Ňčanac…ôr…õ a afum gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňčanayi aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēt…ôk…ôs m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčan…õp…ôl Ňča dac…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanayi k…Ē Yesu m…Ē.
\v 14 Mba nt…õ abeki ap…ĒŇč Ňčancn…ôŇčk fum nw…õ anatam…ôs p…ôc…ôm…õ Ňča f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē, Ňčanay…Ē f…õ toloku.
\v 15 K…Ē aboc kiti aSuyif Ňčaloku Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč k…ôwur ka d…ôk…ôl…Ē nd…õ ancyif…ôt Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčam…õŇčks…õn…õ taŇčan,
\v 16 k…Ē Ňčayif…õn…õ: ¬ęC…ôke c'andey…Ē afum akaŇč…õ-…õ? Bawo t…Ēs…Ēk…ôr aka Yerusal…õm f…ôp a Ňča Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta Kanu tant…õ teyi. Af…Ētam k…ôgb…õk…ôl ti.
\v 17 Mba, nt…õ aŇčy…Ē a ta t…õsam nn…Ē afum Ňčayi m…Ē, pabeŇčn…õ Ňča, pam…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôclok-lok…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ tewe tat…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 18 K…Ē Ňčawe Ňča, k…Ē ŇčambeŇčn…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēloku k…Ē k…ôt…Ēt…ôks…õ afum tewe ta Yesu.
\v 19 Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčayif Ňča: ¬ęP…ômar f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč palel…ôs n…ôna patas Kanu Nk…Ēn ba? N…ôna n…ôm…Ēm…ôn ti belbel,
\v 20 bawo s…ôna s…ôf…Ētam k…ôyi ta s…ôloku t…Ēk…Ē s…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē s…ône m…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē aboc kiti ŇčaŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôbeŇč…ôsn…õ Ňča, k…Ē Ňčasak Ňča. Ňäanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ tes nt…õ andeŇč…õ Ňča a pat…Ēr…ôrs…õ Ňča ti m…Ē bawo afum f…ôp Ňčanckor-koru Kanu teta t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 22 Fum nw…õ …õnas…Ēt…Ē t…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ta k…ôtam…ôs tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, …õnatam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ p…ôcep…ôr.
\s1 K…ôtola ka alaŇč
\p 
\v 23 Nt…õ asak Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčal…Ēm…ôr afum aŇčan t…Ēk…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf Ňčanaloku Ňča m…Ē.
\v 24 Nt…õ Ňčane moloku mam…õ m…Ē, k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ disr…õ k…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ sim nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, m…ôna nw…õ m…ôlomp…ôs k…Ēm, ant…Ēf, k…ôba k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē yeyi ki m…Ē f…ôp,
\v 25 d…ôAmera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ē m…ônalok…õ kusu ka kas kosu Dawuda w…ômar…ôs kam:
\q1 ‚ÄĻAkes…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…õt…õl…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč mencep…ôr…ôr afum a t…Ēf m…Ē?
\q1 Akes…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ afum Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ mes mm…õ m…Ēnt…Ēdel…ôps…ôr m…Ē?
\q1 
\v 26 Ab…õ a doru k…Ērk…Ēr Ňčalomp…ôsn…õ teta k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ,
\q1 k…Ē akiriŇč ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ p…ôl…õc
\q1 nn…Ē W…ôb…õ Kanu k…Ē w…ôy…õk-y…õk k…Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 4:26 \xt Yabura 2.1-2\x*
\p 
\v 27 Bawo kance, Herodu k…Ē P…ĒŇčse Pilat Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ p…ôl…õc dare dand…õ disr…õ at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif k…Ē aYisrayel nn…Ē w…ômar…ôs kam w…ôcempi Yesu eyi m…Ē, nw…õ m…ônay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.
\v 28 Ňäanay…Ē mes f…ôp mm…õ m…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôwos…õ k…ôy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 29 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, W…ôb…õ, m…ôgb…õk…ôr…õ k…ôbeŇč…ôsn…õ k…ôŇčan, m…ôs…ĒŇč…õ acar am k…ôb…ôkn…õ k…ôloku toloku tam kance disr…õ.
\v 30 M…ôtenci k…ôca nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôtam…ôs, m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ, k…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy meyi tewe ta w…ôcar kam w…ôsoku Yesu.
\p 
\v 31 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôtola Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôfo k…ôŇčk…Ē ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ m…Ē k…ôyikc…õ, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ f…ôp faŇčan k…ôloku toloku ta Kanu k…ôb…ôkn…õ disr…õ.
\s1 AlaŇč Yesu Ňčawos…õ k…ôyer…õn…õ daka daŇčan
\p 
\v 32 K…ônay nk…õ k…ônalaŇč m…Ē, Ňčas…Ēt…Ē b…ôk…ôc yin yayi, k…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ s…Ē akin ayi. Nw…õ o nw…õ oncloku f…õ a nk…Ēn sona …Ēy…Ē daka d…Ēn, mba a f…ôp faŇčan f…Ē ŇčanapaŇčn…õ di.
\v 33 Asom a Yesu Ňčancloku t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk k…ôf…Ēt…õ ka Mariki Yesu afi dac…Ē m…Ē. K…Ē k…ômar ka Kanu k…ôyi alaŇč f…ôp k…ôroŇč.
\v 34 Afum akaŇč…õ dac…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…õnal…õc…õ f…õ s…Ē teta k…ôt…Ēy…Ē k…Ēn daka, bawo aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ē dal…õ, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti w…Ēl…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanacam…ôs yi. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ k…ôway ka ca yay…Ēk…Ē,
\v 35 k…Ē Ňčamboc…ôr ki asom a Yesu d…ônt…Ēf. K…ôway kaŇčk…Ē k'ancyer nw…õ o nw…õ k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē p…ôcuca peyi k…Ē m…Ē.
\p 
\v 36 Isifu w…ôka kor ka Lewy …õnayi, nw…õ asom a Yesu Ňčancwe Barnabas m…Ē, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē kusu k…ôŇčan ¬ęW…ôc…ôp…ôs b…ôk…ôc.¬Ľ Nde dare da Sip…ôr anakom k…Ē.
\v 37 Nk…Ēn …õnacam…ôs ant…Ēf nŇč…õ …õnay…Ē m…Ē, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē f…ôp k'ender p…ôboc…ôr ki asom a Yesu d…ônt…Ēf.
\c 5
\s1 Ananiyas k…Ē Safira
\p 
\v 1 W…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi pacwe k…Ē Ananiyas, k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Safira, k…Ē Ňčancam…ôs ant…Ēf ŇčaŇčan.
\v 2 K…ôt…ôŇčn…õ disr…õ k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn, k'Ananiyas embel…ôr k…ôway ka ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē k'…õŇčk…õr…õ k…ôway k…ôl…ôp…ôs nk…õ k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôboc…ôr ki asom a Yesu d…ônt…Ēf.
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē Piy…õr eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAnaniyas, ake's…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ôwos…õ Sentani s…ôs…ĒŇč am k…ôyemb…ôr Amera Ňäecempi m…Ē? M…ômbel…ôr k…ôway ka dal…õ.
\v 4 Nt…õ dal…õ dand…õ d…õnay…Ēn…õ dam m…Ē, ak'…õnas…ĒŇč…õ ta m…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ di-…õ? Ali nt…õ m…ônacam…ôs di m…Ē, p…ôsam pap…Ēk…Ē, baf…Ē pam p…õnayi ba? Akes…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ē tant…õ-…õ? Baf…Ē afum Ňč…Ē m…ôyemb…ôr de, mba Kanu!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 Nt…õ Ananiyas ene moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ, k'eŇčgbiŇč kifir, k'efi. K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôsump…ôr ak…Ē Ňčanane ti m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 6 K'at…õmp Ňčay…õf…õ k…Ē Ňčan…õps…ôr k…Ē ar…Ēf…ôn, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčawup.
\p 
\v 7 Nt…õ dec maas dencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôran ka Ananiyas …õmb…õr…õ, ta …õnc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē t…õnacep…ôr m…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē Piy…õr eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôlok'im ma kance: K…ôway kaŇčk…õ k…Ē n…ôncam…ôs dal…õ ba?¬Ľ
\p K…Ē w…ôran nw…õ oloku ¬ę∆źy, k…ôway kaŇčk…Ē yati k…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęAkes…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ n…ônt…ôŇčn…õ k…Ē n…ôwak Amera Ňča W…ôb…õ m…Ē-…õ? M…ôc…ôr…õ a aŇč…õ Ňčawup wos …ôm m…Ē, Ňčayi nde d…ôkusuŇčka, k…ôkek…ôr…õ k…Ē Ňčander s…Ē m…ôna.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ k…Ē w…õc…ôk d…ônt…Ēf, k'eŇčgbiŇč kifir. K…Ē at…õmp Ňčamb…õr…õ k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp k…Ē p…ôfi. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčawup wos k…ôs…ôk.
\v 11 K…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč k…ôsump…ôr k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč f…ôp k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčanane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\s1 Asom a Yesu Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr mes m…õw…õy-w…õy m…õlar…ôm ma Kanu
\p 
\v 12 Asom a Yesu Ňčancy…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ k…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy m…õlar…ôm mm…õ m…õnayi afum dac…Ē m…Ē. AlaŇč f…ôp Ňčanac…ôm…õ k…ôfo kin nde ak…õr nŇč…õ ancwe ¬ęAk…õr Ňča Sulemani¬Ľ m…Ē.
\v 13 Afum alp…ôs Ňčancnes…õ k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl Ňča, mba Ňčancyekyek…ôs Ňča.
\v 14 K…ônay ka arkun k…Ē aran aŇč…õ ŇčanalaŇč W…ôb…õ m…Ē, Ňčancla oŇč k…ôla d…ôm.
\v 15 Pack…õr…õ at…Ētamn…õ s…ôp…Ē f…ôp pack…õr…õ Ňča d…ôyala k…Ē d…ôs…ôpoko nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē Piy…õr ender-…õ, andulu Ňč…Ēn gb…ôc…ôr…ôm Ňč…õtam k…ôb…ôp w…ôl…Ēma m…Ē.
\v 16 K…ônay ka afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi s…ôdare ns…õ s…ônak…õl Yerusal…õm m…Ē, Ňčancy…õks…õ k…ôk…õr…õ Yerusal…õm at…Ētamn…õ nde asom a Yesu Ňčanayi afum aŇč…õ y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc y…õnas…ĒŇč dotoŇčkulu m…Ē, f…ôp faŇčan anatam…ôs Ňča.
\s1 Ant…Ēr…ôs asom a Yesu teta k…ôlaŇč k…ôŇčan
\p 
\v 17 W…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē aSadisi aŇč…õ Ňčasol m…Ē Ňčay…õf…õn…õ k…ôraca.
\v 18 K…Ē Ňčant…ôp asom a Yesu waca k…Ē Ňčamb…õr Ňča d…ôbili.
\v 19 Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē disr…õ k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma W…ôb…õ Kanu meŇčgbiti cumba ca bili bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē mowur…õn…õ Ňča. K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku Ňča:
\v 20 ¬ęN…ôk…Ē k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč, n…ôloku afum moloku k…Ē mes f…ôp ma t…Ēk…Ēt…õn…õ ta doru dand…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 Nt…õ Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē asom a Yesu ŇčaŇčk…Ē b…ôtb…ôt suy nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňčancop k…ôt…ôks…õ di afum.
\p K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč ender k…Ē ak…Ē …õnasol…õ m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčawe aboc kiti alp…ôs aSuyif k…Ē abeki ap…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčasom a pak…Ē pawur…õn…õ asom a Yesu d…ôbili, pak…õr…õ.
\v 22 K…Ē as…Ēdar Ňčaf…Ē Ňčak…Ē afum aŇč…õ Ňčawur Ňčamb…ôp f…õ Ňča d…ôbili, k…Ē Ňčalukus. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaloku ti ab…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanasom Ňča m…Ē, Ňčacloku:
\v 23 ¬ęS…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôb…ôp cumba ca bili pacaŇč ci belbel, abum a ci Ňčac…ôm…õ d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ daŇčan, mba s…ôŇčgbiti ali fum s…ômb…ôp f…õ bili disr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 24 Nt…õ Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôyi w…ôb…õ ka as…Ēdar a k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč yamayama teta afum akaŇč…õ, k…Ē Ňčayifn…õ c…ôke c…Ē tes tant…õ tendel…ôp…ôs…ôr-…õ?
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē fum w…ôl…Ēma ende p…ôloku Ňča: ¬ęAfum aŇč…õ n…ônab…õr d…ôbili m…Ē Ňčayi nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč, Ňčact…ôks…õ afum.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 As…Ēdar a k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…ôl…õk asom a Yesu, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ Ňča p…ôforu disr…õ, bawo Ňčananes…õ afum k…ôca-cas Ňča.
\v 27 Nt…õ as…Ēdar ŇčaŇčk…õr…õ asom a Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr Ňča f…Ēr ya aboc kiti aSuyif kiriŇč. K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč eyif…ôt Ňča,
\v 28 k'oloku: ¬ęBaf…Ē s…ônam…Ēn…õ nu k…ôt…ôks…õ s…Ē afum teta tewe tant…õ ba? N…ôlas Yerusal…õm m…õt…ôks…õ monu! K…Ē n…ôloku gb…õs a m…õn…õ n…ôloŇč…ôr su p…ôl…õc pa defi da fum w…ôkaw…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 29 Piy…õr k…Ē asom a Yesu Ňčaloku: ¬ęK…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl…õ Kanu k…ôncep…ôr ka afum!
\v 30 Kanu ka atem asu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Yesu k…ôf…Ēt…õ d…ôdefi, nw…õ n…ônacaŇč d…ôk…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl m…Ē.
\v 31 Kanu k…ônd…ôs…ôrn…õ k…Ē k…ôs…ôk bawo nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč k…Ē w…ôyac, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôs…ĒŇč aka Yisrayel k…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc Ňčac…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu dar…ôŇč, paŇčaŇčn…õn…õ Ňča kiciya k…ôŇčan m…Ē.
\v 32 S…ôna s…ôy…Ēn…õ at…ôŇčn…õ a moloku k…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, s…ôna k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi nŇč…õ Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč aŇč…õ Ňčalel…ôs k…Ē Ňčawos…õ toloku t…Ēn m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 33 P…ônat…õl…õ aboc kiti aŇč…õ Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl Ňča m…Ē haŇč p…ôcep…ôr…ôr, k…Ē ŇčafaŇč k…ôdif Ňča.
\v 34 Mba w…ôFarisi w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi Ňča dac…Ē, pacwe k…Ē Kamaliyel. W…ôt…ôks…õ sariy…õ …õnayi, nw…õ afum f…ôp Ňčanab…Ēt…ôr m…Ē. K'…õy…õf…õ aboc kiti aSuyif dac…Ē, k'oloku a pawur…õn…õ afum akaŇč…õ k…ôr…õsna,
\v 35 k'oloku: ¬ęArkun a Yisrayel! N…ôkemb…ôrn…õ belbel nt…õ n…ôndey…Ē afum akaŇč…õ m…Ē.
\v 36 Towon f…õ, Tudas …õnadot banca, afum masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (400) Ňčanac…õk k…Ē dar…ôŇč. Mba anam…ôl…ôk k…Ē, afum ak…Ē …õnasol…õ m…Ē f…ôp k'amb…õl…ôs Ňča. Ali w…ôkin anasak f…õ.
\v 37 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Yudas w…ôKalile …õy…õf…õ t…õm nt…õ ancl…Ēm afum a d…Ēt…Ēf m…Ē. K'osol…õ s…Ē afum alar…ôm. Nk…Ēn s…Ē anam…ôl…ôk k…Ē, aŇč…õ …õnas…õp k…ôkaf…ôli k…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč m…Ē f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčasam…ôs…ôr.
\v 38 Nd…õk…ôl icloku nu, ta n…ôc…õps…ôr afum akaŇč…õ, n…ôsak Ňča Ňčak…Ē. K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a m…õfaŇč, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti m…Ēy…Ē maŇčan nda fum m…õŇčy…õf…õ-…õ, mendes…Ēl…õ.
\v 39 Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a nda Kanu m…õŇčy…õf…õ-…õ, n…ôf…Ēdetam k…ôs…Ēl…õn…õ mi de! N…ôk…õm…ôrn…õ k…ôdey…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Kanu de!¬Ľ K…Ē Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē Kamaliyel …õnas…õp k…ôloku Ňča m…Ē.
\p 
\v 40 K…Ē Ňčawe asom a Yesu, k…Ē Ňčasut Ňča, k…Ē Ňčam…Ēn…õ Ňča k…ôt…Ēs…Ēlok-lok…õ tewe ta Yesu, k…Ē Ňčasak Ňča.
\p 
\v 41 K…Ē asom a Yesu Ňčawur Ňča aboc kiti aSuyif dac…Ē. K…Ē p…ômb…Ēt Ňča k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…ôŇčan teta k…ôlel…ôs ka tewe ta Yesu.
\v 42 D…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk p…ôy…Ēn…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti nde w…Ēl…Ē waŇčan, Ňčanasak f…õ k…ôct…ôks…õ k…Ē k…ôcam moloku m…Ēt…Ēt: A Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist, w…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē.
\c 6
\s1 Ay…õk-y…õk arkun cam…ôt-m…ôr…ôŇč k…ômar ka asom a Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē nt…õ ac…õps…õ a Yesu Ňčancla k…ôla d…ôm m…Ē, aSuyif ac…Ēp kusu ka Kresi Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôc…Ēp…ôsn…õ teta ak…Ē Ňčancc…Ēp Eb…ôre m…Ē. Aran ac…Ēp c…ôKresi aŇč…õ awos aŇčan Ňčafi m…Ē Ňčancs…Ēt…Ē f…õ yeri p…ôm…Ē ac…Ēp Eb…ôre d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē andeyer-…õ.
\v 2 K…Ē Asom w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč Ňčawe k…ônay ka ac…õps…õ a Yesu k…ôn…ôŇčk…õn…õ, k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęP…ômar f…õ su k…ôsak k…ôcam k…Ē k…ôt…ôks…õ toloku ta Kanu teta k…ôyer yeri.
\v 3 Awa aw…õnc su aŇča, n…ôy…õk-y…õk…õn…õ arkun cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, aŇč…õ afum Ňčanc…ôr…õ k…ôy…Ē mera y…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē, Ňčalar…õ s…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt. S…ôs…ĒŇč ay…õk-y…õk anu akak…Ē y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē.
\v 4 S…ôna s…ôsump…ôr belbel k…ôtola ka Kanu k…Ē y…õb…ôc ya k…ôcam k…Ē k…ôt…ôks…õ toloku ta Kanu t…õm f…ôp.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēmb…Ēt afum f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčay…õk-y…õk Etiy…õn, fum w…ôlaŇč Kanu w…ôp…ĒŇč, p…ôlar…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu, k…Ē Filip, k…Ē Pir…Ēk…Ēr, k…Ē Nikan…Ēr, k…Ē Timon, k…Ē Parmenas, k…Ē Nikola, w…ôka dare da Antiy…Ēk, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôcik…ôra k…ôb…õr…õ ka din…õ da aSuyif m…Ē.
\v 6 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčament…ôr ay…õk-y…õk akak…Ē asom a Yesu nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôtola Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčandeŇč Ňča waca k…ôd…ôs k…ôŇčan.
\p 
\v 7 Moloku ma Kanu mm…õ anct…ôks…õ m…Ē m…õncsam k…ôsam d…ôm, k…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu Ňčala kat…ôna kat…ôna Yerusal…õm, k…Ē aloŇčn…õ Kanu alar…ôm Ňčawos…õ k…ôlaŇč Yesu.
\s1 K…ôsump…ôr ka Etiy…õn
\p 
\v 8 Kanu k…ônamar Etiy…õn k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôtam k…ôy…Ē ka mes m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ m…Ēp…ĒŇč ma Kanu afum dac…Ē.
\v 9 Afum al…Ēma aka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif aŇč…õ ancwe ki ¬ęk…ôl…Ē ka Awur dacar¬Ľ m…Ē, Ňčanayin…õ f…õ Etiy…õn. Ňäa Ňčanay…Ēn…õ afum aka at…Ēf Ňča Sir…õn, aka dare da Al…õksand…ôr k…Ē afum a at…Ēf Ňča Silisi, k…Ē aka at…Ēf Ňča Asi. Nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē Etiy…õn.
\v 10 Mba Ňčanatam f…õ k…ôsump…ôr k…Ē d…ômoloku, bawo Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õnas…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôlok-lok…õ d…õc…õr…ôn.
\p 
\v 11 Ti disr…õ, k…Ē afum akak…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč calbante p…ôsam aŇč…õ Ňčanaloku nt…õ: ¬ęS…ôna s…ônen…õ k…Ē k…ôl…Ēm…ôs Musa k…Ē Kanu!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…ôs afum m…õr k…ôy…õf…õ abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf haŇč at…ôks…õ sariy…õ. K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr Etiy…õn, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē f…Ēr ya aboc kiti aSuyif kiriŇč.
\v 13 K…Ē ŇčaŇčken…õn…õ s…Ē calbante akak…Ē Ňčanawos…õ k…ôyem…õ m…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ eyi f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ m…õn…õ k…ôloku p…ôl…õc pa k…ôfo k…ôsoku kaŇčk…õ k…Ē sariy…õ sa Musa.
\v 14 S…ônen…õ k…Ē p…ôcloku a Yesu w…ôNasar…õt w…ôkaw…õ endel…ôs…ôr k…ôfo kaŇčk…õ, p…ôs…ôkp…ôr s…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mm…õ Musa …õnasak…õ su m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 Aboc kiti aSuyif f…ôp Ňčanagb…ôtn…õ Etiy…õn, bawo k…ôro k…Ēn k…ôncmot p…ôm…Ē ka m…õl…õk…õ.
\c 7
\s1 Etiy…õn nde f…Ēr ya aboc kiti kiriŇč
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu eyif Etiy…õn: ¬ęIt…Ē teyi ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 2 K…Ē Etiy…õn oloku: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča, Papa kem aŇča, N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im! Kanu nk…õ debeki d…Ēn doŇčmot m…Ē k…ônawur…ôr Abraham, w…ôtem kosu, nt…õ …õnayi Mesopotami, ta …õntadeder k…ônd…õ HaraŇč m…Ē.
\v 3 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abraham: ¬ęM…ôwur at…Ēf Ňčam, d…ôŇčkom dam, m…ôk…Ē nde at…Ēf nŇč…õ indek…Ēment…ôr …ôm m…Ē.¬Ľ\x - \xo 7:3 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 12.1\x*
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē Abraham owur at…Ēf Ňča Kaldi, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ dare da HaraŇč. D…ôndo, nt…õ defi da kas dencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ n…ônd…õ oŇč nd…õk…ôl m…Ē.
\v 5 Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč f…õ Abraham k…õ at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ, ali d…ôk…ôc…ômb…ôr k…ôc…ôk, mba k…ônal…õk…õ k…Ē temer k…ôdes…ĒŇč k…Ē Ňči k…ôb…ôp k…ôb…ônda ka dokom d…Ēn k…Ē nk…Ēn encep…ôr-…õ, mba t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē ta …õntay…Ē wan-…õ.
\v 6 K…Ē Kanu k…ôloku Abraham nt…õ: ¬ęK…ôb…ônda ka dokom dam k…ôndeyi decik…ôra at…Ēf Ňč…Ēl…Ēma. Andek…Ēc…ômb…ôr Ňča di dacar, pat…Ēr…ôs Ňča meren masar maŇčk…ôl…õ (400).
\v 7 Mba afum aka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčandek…Ēc…ômb…ôr Ňča dacar m…Ē, in'endek…Ēboc…ôr Ňča kiti. K…Ē tencep…ôr-…õ, Ňčandewur Ňčadekor-kor im nn…Ē k…ôfo kaŇčk…õ.¬Ľ\x - \xo 7:7 \xt D…ôk…ôcop 15.13-14\x*
\p 
\v 8 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôncaŇč…ôs kiyi k…Ēn tetin k…Ē Abraham, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ ka k…ôk…ônc arkun. Ti disr…õ k…Ē Abraham oŇčkom Siyaka, k'…õŇčk…ônc k…Ē tataka t…Ēn ta cam…ôt-maas. It…Ē Siyaka …õnay…Ē s…Ē Yakuba, k…Ē Yakuba …Ēy…Ē s…Ē ti awut …Ēn arkun w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč, aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ cas ca cusuŇčka w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč ca Yisrayel m…Ē.
\p 
\v 9 Nt…õ atem asu, awut a Siyaka, Ňčanay…Ēn…õ w…õnc k…ôŇčan Isifu k…ôraca m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčancam…ôs k…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ pakek…ôr…õ k…Ē Misira m…Ē. Mba Kanu k…ônayi k…Ē Isifu,
\v 10 k…ônayac k…Ē p…ôcuca f…ôp. Kanu k…ôncmar Isifu, k…ôcs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt nde Firawona w…ôb…õ ka Misira f…Ēr kiriŇč. Firawona …õnas…ĒŇč Isifu dekiriŇč da Misira k…Ē da k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp m…Ē.
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē dor d…Ēp…ĒŇč dende deyi Misira f…ôp k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč. P…ôcuca p…õnab…õk, atem asu Ňčancs…Ēt…Ē f…õ yeri.
\v 12 K…Ē Yakuba ende p…ône a c…ôgbay c…ôyi Misira, k'osom t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē awut …Ēn aŇč…õ Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ atem asu m…Ē.
\v 13 Tam…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē Isifu owur…ôrn…õ aw…õnc …Ēn, nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē Firawona …Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ oŇč akom…õn…õ a Isifu.
\v 14 K…Ē Isifu osom aw…õnc …Ēn a pak…õr…õ k…Ē kas Yakuba, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ ka afum …Ēn f…ôp, aŇč…õ Ňčancb…ôp afum w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē k…ôcam…ôt (75) m…Ē.
\v 15 K…Ē Yakuba ontor at…Ēf Ňča Misira. Dif…Ē …õnafi, k…Ē atem asu al…Ēma.
\v 16 K'aŇčkek…ôr…õ c…ôbel c…ôŇčan S…ôk…õm, k'aŇčk…Ē pawup nde kufu nk…õ Abraham …õnaway…õ p…ôsam nn…Ē kusuŇčka ka Ham…Ēr k…ôyi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 T…õm nt…õ p…ônamar a Kanu k…ôlas temer nt…õ k…ônal…õk…õ Abraham m…Ē t…õnal…Ēt…ôrn…õ. K…Ē dokomb…ôra d…õmb…õk, k…Ē afum ŇčaŇčla oŇč k…ôla d…ôm Misira,
\v 18 haŇč k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôl…Ēma ender p…ônd…õ d…õb…õ da at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē nw…õ …õnat…Ēc…ôr…õ Isifu m…Ē.
\v 19 W…ôb…õ w…ôkak…Ē ender p…ôcn…õmp…ôs, p…ôct…Ēr…ôs atem asu. K'ende p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôsak c…ônaka c…ôŇčan, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta akak…Ē Ňčantam k…ôyi doru m…Ē.
\p 
\v 20 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t'anakom Musa, nw…õ …õnab…Ēt Kanu k…ôn…ôŇčk m…Ē. K'ant…Ēmp…ôr k…Ē yof maas nde k…ôl…Ē ka kas disr…õ,
\v 21 mba nt…õ t…Ēy…Ē t…õnat…Ēyi m…õn…õ k…ôgbal k…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē wan ka w…ôb…õ ka Misira w…ôran efir k…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôdusum p…ôy…Ē k…Ē wan.
\v 22 K…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôk…Ēt f…ôp k'aMisira k'anadusum…õ Musa, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr d…ômoloku k…Ē d…ôm…Ēy…Ē.
\p 
\v 23 Nt…õ Musa …Ēs…Ēt…Ē meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) m…Ē, k'ende p…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk aw…õnc aŇča, afum a Yisrayel.
\v 24 K…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôt…ôŇčn…õ w…õnc w…ôkin w…ôka Misira paccak…ôra, k'…õnc…ôm…õn…õ w…õnc w…ôkak…Ē anct…Ēr…ôs m…Ē. K'oluks…õ ay…õk Ňča w…õnc, k'endif w…ôMisira.
\v 25 K…Ē Musa …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ a aw…õnc aŇča ŇčaŇčtam k…ôcgb…õk…ôr…õ a Kanu k…ôntam k…ôbaŇč Ňča k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč-…õ, mba Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ ti.
\v 26 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, k…Ē Musa …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp aYisrayel m…õr…ôŇč Ňčacsut…õn…õ, k'…õyac Ňča, k'olomp…ôs Ňča dac…Ē. K'eyif Ňča: ‚ÄĻTa ake t…Ē n…ôŇčsutn…õn…õ tant…õ-…õ? D…õw…õnca d…Ē n…ôy…Ē!‚Äļ
\p 
\v 27 Mba w…ôk…Ē …õnccak…ôra w…õnc m…Ē, …õw…õn Musa p…ôcyif: ‚ÄĻAn'…Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ k…Ē w…ôboc kiti s…ôna dac…Ē-…õ?
\v 28 K…ôdif im k…Ē m…ôfaŇč ba, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē m…ôndifsa w…ôMisira m…Ē?‚Äļ\x - \xo 7:28 \xt K…ôwur 2.14\x*
\v 29 K…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Musa k…ôy…õks…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ônd…õ decik…ôra at…Ēf Ňča MadiyaŇč. Dif…Ē …õnakom awut arkun m…õr…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 30 Nt…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ mencep…ôr (40) m…Ē, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mowur…ôr Musa nde t…õgb…ôr…õ ta t…Ēr…Ē ta Turisnina d…ômemer ma n…õnc nd…õ d…õncmar d…õr…ônt…ôm m…Ē.
\v 31 Nt…õ Musa …õn…ôŇčk ti m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônciyan…õ k…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk ka tes t…õw…õy-w…õy tat…Ēk…Ē, nt…õ …Ēncc…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôk…Ēgb…õk…ôr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē dim da W…ôb…õ Kanu dender k…Ē:
\v 32 ‚ÄĻIn'…Ēf…Ē, Kanu ka atem am: Kanu ka Abraham, ka Siyaka k…Ē ka Yakuba!‚Äļ\x - \xo 7:32 \xt K…ôwur 3.6\x* Musa p…ôcyikc…õ, ta oŇčwos…õ s…Ē k…ôgb…ôtn…õ di-…õ.
\p 
\v 33 K…Ē W…ôb…õ oloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôwur…õ c…Ēfta cam d…ôw…õc…ôk, bawo k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē m…ônc…ôm…õ m…Ē, k…ôfo k…ôcempi k…Ē.
\v 34 In…ôŇčk p…ôcuy pa afum em aŇč…õ Ňčayi Misira m…Ē, ine kigbis k…ôŇčan: K…ôtor k'inder ideyac Ňča. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, m…ôder isom …ôm Misira.‚Äļ\x - \xo 7:34 \xt K…ôwur 3.5,7,8,10\x*
\p 
\v 35 Musa w…ôkak…Ē Ňčanace a Ňčacloku: ¬ęAn'…Ēs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ k…Ē w…ôboc kiti s…ôna dac…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ Nk…Ēn Kanu k…ônasom p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ k…Ē w…ôyac, k…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ m…õnawur…ôr k…Ē nde d…õr…ônt…ôm m…Ē.
\v 36 Nk…Ēn Musa …õnawur…õn…õ aYisrayel Misira p…ôcy…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ma Kanu, nde k…ôba K…ôyim k…Ē nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ, meren mm…õ w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) disr…õ.
\p 
\v 37 Nk…Ēn Musa w…ôkak…Ē yati …õnaloku aYisrayel: ‚ÄĻKanu k…ôndek…õr…õ nu sayib…õ p…ôm…Ē ina, nw…õ k…ôndey…õk-y…õk aw…õnc anu dac…Ē m…Ē, p…ôsom k…Ē nn…Ē n…ôyi m…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 7:37 \xt Sariy…õ 18.15\x*
\v 38 Nk…Ēn Musa, nt…õ afum ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, nk…Ēn …õnay…Ēn…õ s…Ē w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ moloku atem asu dac…Ē k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ monclok-lok…ôr k…Ē nde d…ôt…Ēr…Ē ta Turisnina m…Ē. K'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē moloku meyi w…ôyeŇč, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôc…ôr…õ mi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 39 Atem asu ŇčanafaŇč f…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčaw…õn…ôs k…Ē. Ňäanac…õm-c…õmn…õ d…ôb…ôk…ôc k…ôluks…ôrn…õ Misira.
\v 40 K…Ē atem asu Ňčaloku Aruna, ‚ÄĻM…ôlomp…ôs…õ su m…õr…ôŇčka, mm…õ mendesol…õ su m…Ē, bawo Musa nw…õ owur…õn…õ su Misira m…Ē, s…ônc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 41 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs t…õr…ôŇčka ta tura, k…Ē ŇčaloŇčn…õ nn…Ē t…õr…ôŇčka kiriŇč, k…Ē Ňčamboc…õ k…ôsata y…õb…ôc ya waca waŇčan.
\v 42 Mba k…Ē Kanu k…ômb…õr Ňča kumunt, k…Ē k…ôsak…õ Ňča k…ôkor-koru ca ya darenc. It'ancic ti buk ba sayib…õ disr…õ:
\q1 ‚ÄĻN…ôna aka Yisrayel,
\q1 meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40) mm…õ n…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ m…Ē, in'…Ē n…ôncdif…õ s…õm k…ôloŇčn…õ disr…õ ba?
\q1 
\v 43 N…ônakek…ôr…õ abal Ňča t…õr…ôŇčka ta M…Ēl…Ēk
\q1 k…Ē t…õr…ôŇčka ta k…Ēs ka kanu konu RefaŇč.
\q1 N…ônapat m…õr…ôŇčka teta k…ôctontn…õn…õ ka mi f…Ēr kiriŇč!
\q1 Ti disr…õ k…ôkek…ôr…õ nu k'inder decik…ôra Babil…ĒŇč tadar…ôŇč.‚Äļ\x - \xo 7:43 \xt Amos 5.25-27\x*
\p 
\v 44 Atem asu Ňčanay…Ē d…ôndo d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ aŇčgbancan Ňča sede nŇč…õ anam…õŇčk walak…õ wa masar nw…õ Kanu k…ônacic…õ Musa m…Ē. Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē w…ôlok-lok…ôr ka Musa …õnaloku k…Ē a p…ôy…Ē, a Ňčowur…õn…õ k…Ē Ňč…Ēk…Ē …õnan…ôŇčk m…Ē.
\v 45 Nt…õ atem asu Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Ňči m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ nde at…Ēf nŇč…õ Kanu k…ônab…õl…ôs afum f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč m…Ē. Yosuwe p…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôkiriŇč. AŇčgbancan ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnayi di haŇč t…õm ta Dawuda.
\v 46 K…Ē Dawuda …Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ômar ka Kanu, k'ontola s…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôfo nk…õ …ĒŇčk…Ēc…ômb…ôr…õ Kanu ka Yakuba d…ôk…ôyi m…Ē.
\v 47 Mba Sulemani …õnader p…ôl…Ē k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē.
\p 
\v 48 M…õn…õ nt…õ W…ôb…õ w…ôka darenc …Ēnt…Ēwos…õ k…ôyi paka disr…õ mp…õ k…ôca ka fum k…ôlomp…ôs m…Ē, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sayib…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē:
\q1 
\v 49 ‚ÄĻW…ôb…õ oloku:
\q1 ¬ęK…Ēm k…ôy…Ēn…õ d…Ēc…Ēm dem da d…õb…õ,
\q1 k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ d…ôk…ôc…ômb…ôr dem w…õc…ôk.
\q1 Ake k…ôl…Ē k…Ē n…ôyi k…ôc…ômb…ôr em-…õ?
\q1 K…ôfo k…ôre k'inde icŇčes…ôm-…õ?
\q1 
\v 50 Baf…Ē k…ôca kem k…ôlomp…ôs mam…õ f…ôp ba?¬Ľ‚Äļ\x - \xo 7:50 \xt Esayi 66.1-2\x*
\p 
\v 51 N…ôna afum ataŇči l…ôŇč…ôs, ay…Ē b…ôk…ôc p…ôm…Ē bilakoro! HaŇč m…Ēk…Ē n…ôna n…ôyi k…ôw…õn…ôs Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu p…ôm…Ē atem anu!
\v 52 Sayib…õ s…ôre atem anu Ňčanat…Ēt…Ēr…ôs-…õ? Ňäanadif aŇč…õ ŇčananuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôd…ôŇčk k…ôder ka W…ôlompu nw…õ n…ôna n…ônas…ĒŇč oŇč a k…Ē andif m…Ē.
\v 53 N…ôna aŇč…õ n…ônas…Ēt…Ē sariy…õ sa Musa ns…õ m…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu m…õnaloku k…Ē m…Ē, mba n…ônak…Ēt…õn…õ f…õ si, n…ôm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ f…õ s…Ē si.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôdif ka Etiy…õn
\p 
\v 54 Nt…õ Etiy…õn onclok-loku m…Ē, afum ak…Ē Ňčancne moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, p…ônanaŇčkan…õ k…ôt…õl…õ Ňča haŇč ŇčancŇčaŇč…ôr…õn…õ sek nn…Ē eyi m…Ē.
\v 55 Mba Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õncb…ôc Etiy…õn d…ôris. K'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ēm, k'…õn…ôŇčk n…Ēr…Ē da debeki da Kanu, Yesu p…ôc…ôm…õ Kanu k…ôs…ôk.
\v 56 K'oloku: ¬ęIn…ôŇčk k…Ēm k…ôgbit…õ, Wan ka W…ôrkun p…ôc…ôm…õ Kanu k…ôs…ôk!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 57 K…Ē afum aŇč…õ ŇčaŇčkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē Ňčasuncn…õ l…ôŇč…ôs, k…Ē Ňčaw…õtn…õ f…ôp faŇčan k…ôk…Ēb…ôp Etiy…õn.
\v 58 K…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs k…Ē haŇč k…Ē Ňčawur…õn…õ k…Ē dare, k…Ē Ňčanca-cas k…Ē masar. At…ôŇčn…õ aka ti Ňčanaboc suma saŇčan sa k…ôroŇč w…ôt…õmp d…ônt…Ēf, nw…õ ancwe Sol m…Ē.
\p 
\v 59 Nt…õ Ňčancca-cas k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Etiy…õn ontola p…ôcloku: ¬ęMariki Yesu, m…ôbaŇč amera Ňčem.¬Ľ
\v 60 Nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē Etiy…õn …õnc…ôp suwu, k'oŇčkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, ta m…ôsars…ôr Ňča kiciya kaŇčk…õ!¬Ľ Nt…õ elip k…ôloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'eŇčgbiŇč kifir.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 Sol …õnawos…õ k…ôdif ka Etiy…õn.
\s1 Sol …Ēnct…Ēr…ôs k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu
\p D…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d'anacop k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu d…ôndo Yerusal…õm. K…Ē alaŇč f…ôp faŇčan Ňčasam…ôs…ôr nde t…Ēf ya Yude k…Ē Samari, m…õn…õ asom a Yesu.
\v 2 K…Ē afum alompu al…Ēma Ňčawup Etiy…õn, k…Ē Ňčambok k…Ē belbel.
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē Sol nk…Ēn …õy…õf…õ k…ôt…Ēr…ôs ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu, p…ôcb…õr…õ d…ôw…Ēl…Ē waŇčan, p…ôcwur…õn…õ Ňča, p…ôcsump…ôr arkun k…Ē aran, p…ôcb…õr Ňča d…ôbili.
\s1 Filip k…ôcam k…Ēn moloku m…Ēt…Ēt at…Ēf Ňča Samari
\p 
\v 4 AlaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanasam…ôs…ôr m…Ē, Ňčanccam moloku m…Ēt…Ēt mofo f…ôp mm…õ Ňčanccep…ôr m…Ē.
\v 5 Filip nw…õ …õnator dare da Samari m…Ē, …õnccam teta \wg Krist\wg*, nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk k…ôy…Ēn…õ W…ôb…õ m…Ē.
\v 6 K…ônay k'afum k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ disr…õ Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl belbel t…Ēk…Ē Filip oncloku m…Ē, nt…õ Ňčancne k…Ē Ňčacn…ôŇčk s…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ ma Kanu mm…õ …Ēncy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 7 Y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc yonckul…õ-kul…õ k…ôwur afum alar…ôm d…ôris aka dare dad…Ēk…Ē. Anatam…ôs ator…ôr k…Ē afum alar…ôm ak…Ē Ňčanafi w…õc…ôk m…Ē.
\v 8 K…Ē p…ôbotu p…Ēp…ĒŇč p…õmb…õr…õ dare da Samari.
\p 
\v 9 W…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi di pacwe k…Ē Sim…ĒŇč. ∆źnawon dare dad…Ēk…Ē, p…ôy…Ēn…õ dure, p…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ aka Samari cusu k…ôwos, p…ôcwen…õ s…Ē fum w…ôp…ĒŇč.
\v 10 Afum f…ôp k…ôy…õf…õ wanf…õt haŇč w…ôbeki Ňčanalel…ôs k…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa Kanu, f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôk…Ē aŇčwe ‚ÄĻF…ôp…ĒŇč‚Äļ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 11 Ňäanac…ôm…õ k…Ē dar…ôŇč, bawo …õnawon k…ôwos…ôs Ňča cusu teta dureya d…Ēn.
\v 12 Mba nt…õ ŇčanalaŇč moloku ma Filip, nw…õ …õnccam moloku m…Ēt…Ēt ma d…õb…õ da Kanu k…Ē tewe ta Yesu Krist m…Ē, k'aŇčgb…ôt arkun k…Ē aran d…ôromun teta Kanu.
\v 13 K…Ē Sim…ĒŇč nk…Ēn yati …õlaŇč moloku ma Filip, k'owos…õ k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun. K'…õnc…ôm…õ Filip d…ônt…Ēf t…õm f…ôp. Nt…õ Sim…ĒŇč …õn…ôŇčk m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ k…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy ma Kanu mm…õ mencyi m…Ē, k…Ē kusu k…ôwos k…Ē.
\p 
\v 14 Nt…õ asom a Yesu Ňčanayi Yerusal…õm k…Ē Ňčane a aka Samari Ňčawos…õ toloku ta Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasom Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč k…ôk…Ē di.
\v 15 Nt…õ Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčantor dare da Samari m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantolan…õ Ňča nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu m…Ē,
\v 16 bawo haŇč t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…õnator…ôr f…õ nw…õ o nw…õ k…ôr…õsna d…ôndo. M…õn…õ k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…Ē tewe ta Yesu Krist.
\v 17 Awa Piy…õr k…Ē IsaŇč ŇčandeŇč…ôr Ňča waca, k…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu.
\p 
\v 18 Nt…õ Sim…ĒŇč …õnan…ôŇčk a k…ôdeŇč…ôr k…ôca ka asom a Yesu gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ônas…ĒŇč afum Amera Ňäecempi m…Ē, k'…õŇčk…õr…õ Ňča p…ôsam p…ôcloku:
\v 19 ¬ęN…ôs…ĒŇč im ina s…Ē k…ôtam! Nw…õ o nw…õ indedeŇč…ôr waca m…Ē, w…ôkayi p…ôs…Ēt…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 Mba k…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôl…õc…õ k…Ē p…ôsam pam, bawo m…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôs…Ēt…õn…õ pi k…ôpoc…õ ka Kanu!
\v 21 M…ôna m…ôy…Ē f…õ daka, m…ôy…Ē f…õ tofok…ôl nn…Ē tes tant…õ disr…õ, bawo ab…ôk…ôc Ňčam Ňčolomp f…õ f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč.
\v 22 M…ôluks…ôrn…õ W…ôb…õ Kanu, m…ôl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē, m…ôtola k…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôŇčaŇčn…õn'am m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õl…õc ma ab…ôk…ôc Ňčam m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôwos…õ ti-…õ.
\v 23 Bawo in…ôŇčk a m…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…õl…õc ma k…ôraca m…õntam …ôm, k…Ē k…ôt…Ēlomp k…ôsek…ôt …ôm.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 24 K…Ē Sim…ĒŇč oloku k…Ē: ¬ęN…ôtolan'em Kanu W…ôb…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ mam…õ n…ôloku m…Ē ta t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…Ēs…Ēt'em.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 Piyer k…Ē IsaŇč Ňčancam nt…õ Ňčanan…ôŇčk k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčanane teta Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalukus Yerusal…õm, Ňčaccam toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Kanu s…ôdare s…ôlar…ôm sa Samari.
\s1 Filip k…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Ecopi
\p 
\v 26 M…õl…õk…õ ma W…ôb…õ m…Ēl…Ēma mender nde Filip eyi m…Ē mocloku: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē ntende k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, m…ôsoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē deyer-yer nd…õ d…õŇčy…õf…õ Yerusal…õm doctor Kasa m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 27 K…Ē Filip …õy…õf…õ katin, k'…õntas. W…ôrkun w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka Ecopi …õnayi paban…õ k…Ē. Nk…Ēn …õnat…Ēmp…ôr k…ôc…ômb…ôr-c…ômb…ôr ka daka da Kandas, w…ôbera w…ôka at…Ēf Ňča Ecopi f…ôp. ∆źnader Yerusal…õm k…ôdekor-koru Kanu.
\v 28 K…ôlukus k'…õncnd…õ nd…Ēr…Ēn p…ônd…õ p…õy…õks…õn…õ p…Ēn k…ôroŇč, p…ôckaraŇč p…ôp…ĒŇč buk ba aŇčnabi Esayi.
\v 29 K…Ē Amera Ňča Kanu Ňčoloku Filip: ¬ęM…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ m…ôl…Ēt…ôrn…õ p…ôy…õks…õn…õ mp…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē Filip …õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ē d…ôndo, k'ene w…ôka Ecopi nw…õ p…ôckaraŇč buk ba aŇčnabi Esayi. K'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ônc…ôr…õ nt…õ m…ôyi k…ôkaraŇč m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 31 K…Ē w…ôEcopi nw…õ oloku Filip: ¬ęC…ôke c'intam ti k…ôc…ôr…õ-…õ, k'int…Ēy…Ē nw…õ …õnt…ôks'em m…Ē?¬Ľ K'oloku Filip a p…ôp…õs…õ p…ônd…õ k…Ē k…ôs…ôk p…õy…õks…õn…õ p…Ēn k…ôroŇč.
\p 
\v 32 Moloku ma Buk mb…õ …õnckaraŇč m…Ē m…õnay…Ēn…õ mm…õ:
\q1 ¬ęK'aŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē d…ôk…ôdif p…ôm…Ē aŇčkesiya.
\q1 P…ôm…Ē aŇčkesiya Ňčowut nŇč…õ Ňč…Ēnt…Ēkul…õ-kul…õ w…ôfon w…ôka Ňči d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē,
\q1 …õnawani f…õ kusu.
\q1 
\v 33 Owos…õ k…ôtor…õ k…Ēn banca, k'ambaŇč…ôr k…Ē kance k…Ēn.
\q1 An'endetam k…ôl…Ēm teta k…ôb…ônda ka dokom d…Ēn-…õ?
\q1 Bawo anim kiyi k…Ēn doru ant…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ k…ôroŇč.¬Ľ\x - \xo 8:33 \xt Esayi 53.7\x*
\p 
\v 34 K…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôban…õ nw…õ eyifn…õ Filip: ¬ęIl…õts…õn'am, m…ôlok'im: Tes ta ana t…Ē sayib…õ s…ôloku tant…õ-…õ? Ta nk…Ēn w…ôs…ôrka ba, ka fum w…ôcuru?¬Ľ
\v 35 K…Ē Filip …õl…õk moloku k'oncop d…ômoloku ma Buk bab…Ēk…Ē, k'oloku k…Ē toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Yesu.
\p 
\v 36-37 Nt…õ Ňčanasoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē Ňčack…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp domun. K…Ē w…ôrkun w…ôban…õ oloku: ¬ęDomun d…Ē dand…õ: Ak'endeyam…ôs oŇč k…ôgb…ôt kem d…ôromun teta Kanu-…õ?¬Ľ\f + \fr 8:36-37 \ft Yecic…ôs y…Ēl…Ēma aŇčdeŇč…ôr moloku m…Ēl…Ēma: ¬ęK…Ē Filip oloku: ‚ÄĻK…Ē m…ôlaŇč ab…ôk…ôc Ňčam f…ôp-…õ, s…ôntam ti.‚Äļ K…Ē w…ôEcopi w…ôban…õ oloku: ‚ÄĻIlaŇč a Yesu Krist …Ēy…Ēn…õ Wan ka Kanu.‚Äļ¬Ľ\f*
\v 38 K…Ē Filip oloku a p…ôc…ômb…ôr p…õy…õks…õn…õ, k…Ē Ňčantor d…ôromun. k…Ē Filip …õŇčgb…ôt k…Ē d…ôromun teta Kanu.
\v 39 Nt…õ Ňčamp…õ d…ôromun m…Ē, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča W…ôb…õ Kanu Ňč…õmp…õn…õ Filip. Ti disr…õ, w…ôban…õ w…ôka Ecopi nw…õ …õn…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē s…Ē, k'osoln…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēn ab…ôk…ôc Ňčobotu disr…õ.
\v 40 K…Ē Filip …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôn…ôŇčkn…õ dare da Asot. K'oloku moloku m…Ēt…Ēt ma Kanu s…ôdare f…ôp ns…õ enccep…ôr m…Ē, haŇč k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp dare da Sesari m…Ē.
\c 9
\s1 Kanu k…ônc…ômb…ôr Sol d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēt…Ēt
\r 22.3-16; 26.9-20
\p 
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Sol p…ôcbeŇč…ôsn…õ k…ôdif…ôt ac…õps…õ a Mariki dar…ôŇč, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē ndena w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu.
\v 2 K…Ē Sol ewer w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč reka teta w…Ēl…Ē wa d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif nde Damas, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k'…õmb…ôp di akin akin-…õ, p…ôy…Ēn…õ arkun p…ôy…Ēn…õ aran aŇč…õ Ňčanc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Yesu dar…ôŇč m…Ē, p…ôtam k…ôsump…ôr Ňča p…ôkek…ôr…õ Yerusal…õm.
\v 3 D…Ēp…Ē Sol …õnayi p…ôcl…Ēt…ôrn…õ dare da Damas, gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē p…ômot p…õy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm, k…Ē p…Ēs…ĒŇč p…ôwaŇčk…ôra mp…õ p…õnak…õl k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 4 K'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf. K'ene dim nd…õ d…õnayif k…Ē: ¬ęSol! Sol! T'ake t…Ē m…ônt…Ēr…ôs em-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 5 K…Ē Sol eyif k…Ē, ¬ęW…ôb…õ, m…ôna an'…Ēf…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p ¬ęIna, Yesu iy…Ēn…õ, nw…õ m…ôyi k…ôt…Ēr…ôs m…Ē.
\v 6 Mba m…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôb…õr…õ dare, aŇčk…Ēlok'…ôm t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar m…ôy…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 7 K…Ē arkun aŇč…õ Ňčanasol k…Ē nk…Ēn Sol m…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ, ta Ňčantam k…ôlok-loku-…õ k…ônes…õ disr…õ, Ňčacne dim mba ta ŇčaŇčn…ôŇčk fum-…õ.
\v 8 K…Ē Sol …õy…õf…õ d…ônt…Ēf p…ômepi f…Ēr, mba ta …õŇčn…ôŇčk paka o paka-…õ. K'asump…ôr k…Ē k…ôca, k'amb…õrs…õn…õ k…Ē dare da Damas.
\v 9 K'eyi di mata maas ta …õŇčn…ôŇčk-…õ, …Ēf…Ēdi peri, …Ēf…Ēmun.
\p 
\v 10 D…ôndo dare da Damas w…ôc…õps…õ w…ôka Mariki dar…ôŇč w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi di pacwe k…Ē Ananiyas. K…Ē W…ôb…õ oloku k…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk disr…õ: ¬ęAnaniyas!¬Ľ
\p K'owos…õ: ¬ęIyi nn…Ē, Mariki!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē Mariki oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēk…Ē aŇčwe ‚ÄĻDolompu‚Äļ m…Ē, m…ôk…Ē m…ôt…õn nde k…ôl…Ē ka Yudas fum w…ôk…Ē aŇčwe Sol m…Ē, w…ôka dare da Tar…ôs …Ēy…Ēn…õ. Bawo ontola Kanu,
\v 12 k…Ē Kanu k…ônament…ôr k…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk disr…õ fum nw…õ aŇčwe Ananiyas m…Ē p…ôb…õr…ôr k…Ē. K'endeŇč…ôr Sol waca, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 13 Mba Ananiyas oluks…õ: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, inen…õ afum alar…ôm Ňčacl…Ēm p…ôl…õc mp…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē …Ēy…Ē afum am acempi nde Yerusal…õm m…Ē.
\v 14 Nn…Ē k…ôfo kaŇčk…õ yati k…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč aSuyif Ňčanawur…õ Sol a p…ôdesump…ôr nw…õ o nw…õ ombonc tewe tam m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 Mba k…Ē W…ôb…õ oloku Ananiyas: ¬ęM…ôk…Ē! Bawo fum w…ôkak…Ē paka p…Ē mp…õ inay…õk-y…õk k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ tewe tem nn…Ē ab…õ a t…Ēf ya doru k…Ē aka Yisrayel f…Ēr kiriŇč m…Ē.
\v 16 Ina yati in'endement…ôr Sol p…ôcuy f…ôp p…Ēk…Ē p…ômar p…ôdecep…ôr…õn…õ teta tewe tem m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē Ananiyas …ĒŇčk…Ē. Nt…õ …õmb…ôp k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr…õ, k'endeŇč…ôr Sol waca. K'oloku: ¬ęSol W…õnc im, Mariki Yesu, nw…õ …õnawur…ôr …ôm nde d…Ēp…Ē nd…õ m…ônasoln…õ m…ôcder Damas m…Ē, osom im nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč'am s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk, a m…ôlar…õ s…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 18 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē ca yoŇčkoŇč…õ k…Ē d…ôf…Ēr p…ôm…Ē wokwok, k…Ē f…Ēr y…Ēn y…õntam s…Ē k…ôcn…ôŇčk. K…Ē Sol …õy…õf…õ, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu.
\v 19 Nt…õ elip k…ôdi yeri m…Ē, k'…Ēs…Ēt…Ē s…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr.
\s1 Sol k…ôcam k…Ēn toloku ta Kanu dare da Damas
\p K…Ē Sol encep…ôr…õn…õ mataka m…Ēl…Ēma k…Ē ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu ak…Ē Ňčanayi dare da Damas m…Ē.
\v 20 K'…õy…õf…õ k…ôcam katina d…ôw…Ēl…Ē wa d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, p…ôcloku a Yesu Wan ka Kanu …Ēy…Ēn…õ.
\v 21 K…Ē p…ônciyan…õ afum f…ôp aŇč…õ Ňčancne polok-loku pa Sol m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayif: ¬ęBaf…Ē nk…Ēn nde Yerusal…õm …õncfaŇč k…ôm…ôl…ôk aŇč…õ Ňčancbonc tewe tant…õ m…Ē ba? Baf…Ē k…ôsump…ôr k…ôŇčan k'…õnader…õn…õ nn…Ē, p…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča nde aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč Ňčayi m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\v 22 Mba Sol p…ôcs…Ēt…Ē k…ôs…Ēt…Ē d…ôm k…ôtam p…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanayi dare da Damas m…Ē k…ôciyan…õ, k…ôcment…ôr a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist, w…ôb…õ w…ôy…õk-y…õk w…ôka Kanu.
\p 
\v 23 Nt…õ mataka m…Ēl…Ēma mencep…ôr m…Ē, aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanayi Damas m…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ônim ka Sol.
\v 24 K…Ē Sol ende p…ôc…ôr…õ t…õt…ôŇčn…õ taŇčan. ASuyif Ňčancbum daŇč k…Ē pibi k…ôdewur k…Ēn dare nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčatam k…ônim k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 25 Mba pibi pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčamb…õr k…Ē d…ôk…ôsaksaka, k…Ē Ňčayok…õn…õ k…Ē damba da saŇčka sa dare dar…ôŇč.
\s1 K…ôyi ka Sol Yerusal…õm
\p 
\v 26 Nt…õ Sol …õmb…õr…õ Yerusal…õm m…Ē, k'…õŇčs…õp k…ôn…ĒŇčk…ôl…õn…õ ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč. Mba f…ôp f…ôncnes…õ k…Ē, ta ŇčalaŇč a nk…Ēn s…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôc…õps…õ w…ôka Yesu dar…ôŇč-…õ.
\v 27 Mba k…Ē Barnabas …õl…õk k…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde asom a Yesu Ňčayi m…Ē. K…Ē Barnabas …Ēl…Ēm…ôr Ňča nt…õ Sol …õnan…ôŇčk Mariki d…Ēp…Ē, a k…Ē Yesu olok-lok…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē nt…õ tewe ta Yesu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôb…ôkn…õ k…ôlokk-loku m…Ē.
\v 28 Sol …Ēnck…Ē p…ôcder k…Ē Ňča d…ôndo Yerusal…õm p…ôclok-lok…õ k…ôlaŇč disr…õ tewe ta Mariki.
\v 29 Sol p…ôclok-loku, p…ôcgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē afum aKresi, mba, Ňča s…Ē, Ňčact…õn k…ônim k…Ē.
\v 30 Nt…õ aw…õnc alaŇč Ňčanc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ Sol k…ôtor Sesari, k'…õl…õk d…Ēp…Ē k'…ĒŇčk…Ē dare da Tar…ôs.
\p 
\v 31 K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu a at…Ēf Ňča Yude, at…Ēf Ňča Kalile k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Samari, Ňča f…ôp Ňčanayi p…ôforu disr…õ. AlaŇč Yesu Ňčanc…ôp…ôs…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc, Ňčayin…õ k…ônes…õ ka W…ôb…õ Kanu disr…õ. Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õncmar…ôs k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu, ti disr…õ Ňčancla k…ôla d…ôm.
\s1 K…ôtam…ôs ka Eney
\p 
\v 32 Piy…õr nw…õ …õnccep…ôr s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē f…ôp m…Ē, …õnader p…ôtor s…Ē ndena afum acempi aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ dare da Lida m…Ē.
\v 33 K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp di fum nw…õ ancwe Eney m…Ē, ta …ĒŇčk…Ēt-…õ, p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ debik meren cam…ôt-maas disr…õ.
\v 34 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku k…Ē: ¬ęEney, Yesu Krist …õntam…ôs …ôm! M…ôy…õf…õ m…ôna w…ôs…ôrka m…ôn…õp abik Ňčam!¬Ľ Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k'…õy…õf…õ, k'…õnc…ôm…õ.
\v 35 Nt…õ aka Lida k…Ē aka Sar…ĒŇč f…ôp Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkaf…ôli mera yaŇčan nn…Ē Mariki eyi m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôyekti ka Tabita defi
\p 
\v 36 W…ôran w…ôc…õps…õ ka Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi dare da Yope, pacwe k…Ē Tabita. Kusu k…ôŇčan disr…õ ancwe k…Ē s…Ē Dorkas, ti t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ¬ęwere¬Ľ. W…ôran w…ôkak…Ē …Ēncy…Ē mes m…Ēt…Ēt m…õlar…ôm, k…Ē k…ômar.
\v 37 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ docu, k'efi. K'ambik…õ k…ôbel k…Ēn, k'amp…õn…õ ki nde dukul…Ē da k…ôl…Ē darenc.
\v 38 Nt…õ ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčane a Piy…õr eyi Lida nd…õ d…Ēl…Ēt…ôrn…õ dare da Yope m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasom arkun m…õr…ôŇč k…ôk…Ēl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē: ¬ęTa m…ôwon k…ôcep…ôr nde ndorosu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 39 K…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…Ē asom aŇč…õ m…õr…ôŇč. Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ m…Ē, k'amp…õn…õ k…Ē nde dukul…Ē da k…ôl…Ē darenc. K'ac…ôbok…ôra f…ôp Ňčander Ňčab…ôp k…Ē Ňčacbok, Ňčacment…ôr k…Ē s…ôbrumus k…Ē yamos ny…õ Dorkas …õnalomp…ôs nt…õ …õnayi k…Ē Ňča m…Ē.
\p 
\v 40 K…Ē Piy…õr owur…õn…õ afum f…ôp nde doru, k'…õnc…ôp suwu, k'ontola Kanu tet…Ēn. Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ nde k…ôbel k…ôyi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęTabita, m…ôy…õf…õ!¬Ľ Awa k…Ē Tabita emepi f…Ēr, nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk Piy…õr m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ, k'…õnd…õ.
\v 41 K…Ē Piy…õr …Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôca, k'eyekti k…Ē. K'ewe afum acempi k…Ē ac…ôbok…ôra, k'ement…ôr Ňča Tabita p…ôyi w…ôyeŇč.
\v 42 K…Ē aka dare da Yope f…ôp Ňčanc…ôr…õ ti, k…Ē alar…ôm Ňčancop k…ôlaŇč Mariki.
\v 43 K…Ē Piy…õr eyi dare da Yope mataka m…õlar…ôm, ndena Sim…ĒŇč w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ …õncb…ôc kata m…Ē.
\c 10
\s1 K…ôwe ka Piy…õr ndena K…Ērneli
\p 
\v 1 W…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi Sesari pacwe k…Ē K…Ērneli, p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka k…ôgba ka as…Ēdar tasar tin (100). K…ôgba kaŇčk…Ē k'ancwe ¬ęK…ôgba Itali.¬Ľ
\v 2 Nk…Ēn k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp Ňčancnes…õ Kanu, Ňčac…ôm…õ t…õfaŇč ta ki dar…ôŇč. K…Ērneli …Ēncy…Ēn…õ afum n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, p…ôctola Kanu t…õm f…ôp.
\v 3 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma dec d…Ēr…Ēf…Ēy, k'…õn…ôŇčk p…ôsoku p…õs k…ôn…ôŇčk disr…õ, m…õl…õk…õ ma Kanu m…Ēl…Ēma m…õb…õr…õ nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ, k…Ē mewe k…Ē: ¬ęK…Ērneli!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 K'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ mi, k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôyi k…Ē, k'eyif mi: ¬ęAc…ôke W…ôb…õ?¬Ľ
\p K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mam…Ēk…Ē moloku k…Ē: ¬ęMotola mam k…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ kam afum n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr, mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp m…õmp…õ nde Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč, k…Ē k…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ mi.
\v 5 M…ôsom oŇč afum dare da Yope Ňčak…Ēwen'am fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ aŇčwe Sim…ĒŇč m…Ē, pacdeŇč…ôr k…Ē tewe ta ‚ÄĻPiy…õr‚Äļ.
\v 6 Ndena Sim…ĒŇč w…ôl…Ēma eyi, w…ôkak…Ē w…ôb…ôc kata …Ēf…Ē, k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ôyi k…ôba k…ôs…ôk.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 Nt…õ m…õl…õk…õ mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnalok-lok…ôr k…Ē m…Ē m…õnadelukus, k…Ē K…Ērneli ewe amar…ôs …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôc…ôm…õ m…õfaŇč ma Kanu dar…ôŇč w…ôl…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanayi k…Ē d…ônt…Ēf m…Ē.
\v 8 Nt…õ K…Ērneli elip k…ôl…Ēm…ôr as…Ēdar …Ēn mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr nk…Ēn k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ dac…Ē m…Ē, k'osom Ňča Yope.
\p 
\v 9 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, nt…õ Ňčanayi d…Ēp…Ē, a Ňčacl…Ēt…ôrn…õ dare da Yope m…Ē, k…Ē Piy…õr …õmp…õs…õ ak…õr Ňča k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn kak…ôroŇč k…ôk…Ētola Kanu, t…õnat…ôŇčn…õ daŇč d…õcb…ôp.
\v 10 K…Ē dor d…Ēy…Ē k…Ē, k'…õfaŇč k…ôdi yeri. T…õm t…Ēk…Ē anayi k…ôlomp…ôs…õ k…Ē yeri m…Ē, k'…õn…ôŇčk tes t…Ēl…Ēma nt…õ t…õy…õf…õ d…ôKanu m…Ē.
\v 11 K'…õn…ôŇčk k…Ēm k…ôgbit…õ, paka p…Ēl…Ēma mp…õ p…õnawur…õn…õ k…Ē manta m…Ēp…ĒŇč mm…õ anasump…ôr moŇčkubut maŇčk…ôl…õ m…Ē, montor haŇč k…Ē m…õf…ônt…ôr…õ d…ônt…Ēf.
\v 12 S…õm dokom f…ôp y…õnayi manta mam…Ēk…Ē disr…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ s…õm ya w…õc…ôk maŇčk…ôl…õ, yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ haŇč k…ôb…ôp b…õmp ya darenc.
\v 13 K…Ē dim d…Ēl…Ēma doloku k…Ē: ¬ęPiy…õr, M…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôdif, m…ôs…Ēm!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku: ¬ęAla W…ôb…õ! T…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…õntas…ĒŇč…õ f'em k…ôs…Ēm paka mp…õ sariy…õ s…ôm…Ēn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 Tam…õr…ôŇč k…Ē dim nd…õ dolok-lok…ôr k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęPaka mp…õ Kanu k…ôcemp…ôs m…Ē, ta m…ôna m…ôyik-yik…ôs pi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē teyi k…ômaas, p…ôwon f…õ k'amp…õn…õ d…ôk…Ēm manta mam…Ēk…Ē m…õnay…Ē s…õm m…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē tedisr…õ ta k…ôn…ôŇčk kaŇčk…Ē teyi Piy…õr yamayama. T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē asom a K…Ērneli, nt…õ ament…ôr Ňča k…ôl…Ē ka Sim…ĒŇč m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ki nde d…ôkusuŇčka.
\v 18 K…Ē Ňčawe, k…Ē Ňčayif k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…Ē k…ôl…Ē kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē Sim…ĒŇč nw…õ andeŇč…ôr tewe ta ¬ęPiy…õr¬Ľ m…Ē eyi-…õ.
\p 
\v 19 Nt…õ Piy…õr eyi k…ôc…õm-c…õmn…õ tedisr…õ ta k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Amera Ňča Kanu Ňčoloku k…Ē: ¬ęArkun maas Ňčayi nde dabaŇčka Ňčact…õn …ôm.
\v 20 M…ôtor, n…ôsol n…ôk…Ē k…Ē Ňča, ali k…ônes…õ ta k…ôy'im, bawo In'osom Ňča.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē Piy…õr ontor k'eyif arkun aŇč…õ: ¬ęIna n…ônt…õn, ta ake t…Ē n…ônder…õn…õ nn…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęK…Ērneli, w…ôb…õ w…ôka as…Ēdar tasar tin (100), fum w…ôlompu p…ôcnes…õ Kanu, nw…õ aSuyif f…ôp Ňčanc…ôr…õ d…Ēt…Ēt d…Ēn ak…Ē ŇčaŇčloku mes m…Ēn m…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē, nd…Ēr…Ēn Kanu k…ôsom m…õl…õk…õ mosoku, a p…ôsak su s…ôdew'am p…ôk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl …ôm nt…õ p…ômar m…ôloku k…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 23 Awa k…Ē Piy…õr …õmb…õrs…õ Ňča d…õk…õr, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča d…ôkiyi.
\p D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē k…Ē Ňča. K'aw…õnc alaŇč a dare da Yope al…Ēma Ňčanc…ômb…ôr k…Ē.
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ Sesari d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, K…Ērneli p…ôckar Ňča, k'ewe akom…õn…õ …Ēn al…Ēma nde nd…Ēr…Ēn k…Ē anapa …Ēn at…Ēt.
\v 25 K…ôb…õr…õ ka Piy…õr, k…Ē K…Ērneli …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôfayn…õ k…Ē, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ k…Ē w…õc…ôk d…ônt…Ēf. K'…õnc…ôp…õ k…Ē suwu.
\v 26 Mba k…Ē Piy…õr eyekti k…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ, ina s…Ē fum iy…Ēn…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 Ňäayi k…ôlok-loku k…Ē K…Ērneli, k'…õmb…õr…õ k'…õmb…ôp afum alar…ôm ŇčaloŇčkan…õ.
\v 28 K…Ē Piy…õr oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ônc…ôr…õ a am…Ēn…õ aSuyif k…ôb…Ēt k…Ē acik…ôra, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, p…ôb…õr…õ nd…Ēr…Ēn. Mba Kanu k…ôment…ôr im a p…ômar f…õ a pakul…õ fum o fum a eyik-yik, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, p…ômar f…õ s…Ē a pakul…õ fum o fum a …Ēs…Ēk f…õ f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč.
\v 29 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ m…ôsom a pak…Ēw'em m…Ē, k'inder ali ta inc…õmc…õmn…õ-…õ. Nd…õk…ôl iyif …ôm, T'ake t…Ē m…ôwen'em-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē K…Ērneli oloku: ¬ęT…Ēs…Ēt…Ē mata maŇčk…ôl…õ ictola nn…Ē nderem, d…Ēf…Ēy dendeb…ôp. K'in…ôŇčk f…Ēr yem kiriŇč w…ôrkun w…ôl…Ēma p…ôb…õrn…õ yamos yomot…ôr-mot…ôr.
\v 31 K…Ē fum w…ôkak…Ē oloku: ‚ÄĻK…Ērneli, Kanu k…ômbaŇč k…ôtola kam, k'…õnc…õmc…õmn…õ s…Ē k…ôy…Ēn…õ kam afum n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr.
\v 32 M…ôsom fum dare da Yope pak…Ēwen'am Sim…ĒŇč nw…õ andeŇč…ôr tewe ta ¬ęPiy…õr¬Ľ m…Ē, nde k…ôl…Ē ka Sim…ĒŇč, w…ôb…ôc kata, nw…õ k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ôyi k…ôba k…ôs…ôk m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 33 K'isom katina fum, k…Ē m…ôna m…ôs…Ēt…Ē ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēt…Ēt k…ôder. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč s…ôyi f…ôp fosu Kanu f…Ēr kiriŇč, s…ôdec…ôŇčk…ôl moloku m…Ēk…Ē W…ôb…õ osom …ôm k…ôloku m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Moloku ma Piy…õr ndena K…Ērneli
\p 
\v 34 Awa k…Ē Piy…õr …õl…õk moloku, k'oloku: ¬ęKance: Inc…ôr…õ oŇč a Kanu k…ôyi f…õ k…ôs…ôk kin.
\v 35 Mba afum f…ôp dac…Ē m…ôna nw…õ m…ôŇčnes…õ Kanu, m…ôc…ôm…õ p…ôlompu dar…ôŇč m…Ē, Kanu k…ômbaŇč …ôm.
\v 36 Kanu k…ônaken…õ aka Yisrayel toloku, p…ôcloku Ňča moloku m…Ēt…Ēt ma p…ôforu mp…õ Yesu Krist …õŇčk…õr…õ afum f…ôp m…Ē: Nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ W…ôb…õ ka afum f…ôp.
\v 37 N…ôna n…ônc…ôr…õ t…Ēk…Ē teyi Yude f…ôp m…Ē, Kalile t…õnacop, nt…õ SaŇč …õnad…ôŇčk k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun m…Ē.
\v 38 Kanu k…ônab…Ēy Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēn k…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. Nn…Ē o nn…Ē enccep…ôr m…Ē, …Ēncy…Ē p…ôt…Ēt, p…ôctam…ôs afum f…ôp aŇč…õ amera Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…Ēnct…Ēr…ôs m…Ē, bawo Kanu k…ônayi k…Ē nk…Ēn Yesu.
\p 
\v 39 S…ôy…Ēn…õ at…ôŇčn…õ a mes f…ôp mm…õ Yesu …õnay…Ē nde at…Ēf Ňča aSuyif k…Ē Yerusal…õm m…Ē. Nk…Ēn nw…õ Ňčananim, ŇčacaŇč k…Ē d…ôk…ôt…Ēk m…Ē,
\v 40 mba Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôf…Ēt…õ d…ôdefi tataka t…Ēn ta maas. K…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč k…Ē k…ôment…ôrn…õ,
\v 41 baf…Ē nn…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčayi m…Ē, mba nn…Ē at…ôŇčn…õ mes aŇč…õ Kanu k…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôy…õk-y…õk, k…Ē s…ôna aŇč…õ s…ônadi yeri, s…ômun k…Ē nk…Ēn nt…õ …õnaf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 42 K'osom su k…ôloku afum, s…ôment…ôr a nk…Ēn Yesu, nk…Ēn …Ē Kanu k…ônc…ômb…ôr k…ôy…Ēn…õ nw…õ endeboc…õ afum afi k…Ē ayi w…ôyeŇč kiti m…Ē.
\v 43 Sayib…õ f…ôp s…ônaloku tet…Ēn: Nw…õ o nw…õ …õgb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Yesu m…Ē, endes…Ēt…Ē nde Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ka mes m…Ēn m…õl…õc teta tewe ta Yesu.¬Ľ
\s1 At…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu
\p 
\v 44 Moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē Piy…õr …õnayi k…ôloku, nt…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õnator…ôr afum ak…Ē Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku m…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 45 Cusu c…ônawos alaŇč a Kanu, ak…ônc ak…Ē Ňčanader k…Ē Piy…õr m…Ē, k…ôn…ôŇčk a k…ôpoc…õ ka Amera Ňäecempi k…ônasam…ôs…ôr k…ôb…ôp haŇč acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…Ē,
\v 46 bawo Ňčancne Ňča k…ôkor-koru Kanu cusu c'acik…ôra.
\p Awa k…Ē Piy…õr …ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ:
\v 47 ¬ęAntam k…ôfat…õn…õ k…ôgb…ôt afum d…ôromun nn…Ē akaŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē Amera Ňäecempi p…ôm…Ē s…ôna m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\v 48 K'oloku a pagb…ôt akak…Ē d…ôromun tewe ta Yesu Krist. K…Ē Ňčal…õts…õn…õ Piy…õr k…ôyi d…ôndo mataka m…Ēl…Ēma.
\c 11
\s1 Piy…õr k…ôs…Ēks…ôr alaŇč a Yerusal…õm mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr dare da Yope m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 Asom a Yesu k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanayi at…Ēf Ňča Yude m…Ē Ňčane a acik…ôra, aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…Ē, Ňčawos…õ toloku ta Kanu.
\v 2 Nt…õ Piy…õr …õnap…õ Yerusal…õm m…Ē, k…Ē afum aŇč…õ anak…ônc m…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ônal k…Ē,
\v 3 Ňčacloku: ¬ęM…ômb…õr…õ ndena afum aŇč…õ ant…Ēk…ônc m…Ē, k…Ē m…ôndi yeri k…Ē Ňča, bawo aSuyif Ňčanam…Ēn…õ ti!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 Awa k…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k…ôl…Ēm…ôr Ňča tin tin tin mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õnacep…ôr m…Ē:
\v 5 ¬ęIna, nde dare da Yope inayi, d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē ictola Kanu k…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk k…ônder im. Ti disr…õ, k'in…ôŇčk paka p…Ēl…Ēma poctor powur…õn…õ k…Ē manta pasump…ôr pi moŇčkubut maŇčk…ôl…õ, k…Ē pontor k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm haŇč nn…Ē inayi m…Ē.
\v 6 Nt…õ inagb…ôtn…õ pi disr…õ m…Ē, k'in…ôŇčk s…õm ya w…õc…ôk maŇčk…ôl…õ, s…õm ya dop, yeliŇč…õ-liŇč…õ, k…Ē b…õmp ya d…ôk…Ēm.
\v 7 K'ine s…Ē dim doclok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôy…õf…õ Piy…õr! M…ôdif, m…ôs…Ēm.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 8 K'iloku: ‚ÄĻAla W…ôb…õ! T…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…õntas…ĒŇč…õ f'em k…ôb…õr paka p…Ēt…Ēcemp d…ôkusu, mp…õ Kanu k…ôm…Ēn…õ k…ôdi m…Ē.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē dim nd…õ d…ĒŇčgb…Ēk…ôr…õ s…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm: ‚ÄĻPaka mp…õ Kanu k…ôncemp…ôs m…Ē, ta m…ôna m…ôlok…õ pi k…ôt…Ēcemp!‚Äļ
\v 10 K…Ē teyi k…ômaas, p…ôwon f…õ k…Ē ca ny…õ f…ôp yolukus s…Ē d…ôk…Ēm.
\p 
\v 11 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē arkun maas aŇč…õ anasom nde nderem k…ôy…õf…õ dare da Sesari m…Ē, Ňčander Ňčac…ôm…õ d…ôkusuŇčka ka k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē s…ônayi m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňčolok'im a s…ôsol s…ôk…Ē k…Ē Ňča, ali ines…õ f…õ. K…Ē aw…õnc asu aŇča alaŇč cam…ôt-tin aŇč…õ Ňčac…ôm'em dar…ôŇč, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôb…õr…õ ndena K…Ērneli.
\v 13 K…Ē K…Ērneli oloku su nt…õ …õnan…ôŇčk m…õl…õk…õ nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, k…Ē moloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻM…ôsom fum dare da Yope pak…Ē wen'am Sim…ĒŇč, w…ôk…Ē andeŇč…ôr tewe ta ¬ęPiy…õr¬Ľ m…Ē.
\v 14 Nw…õ endelok'…ôm moloku mm…õ mendeyac …ôm, k…ôb…ôp aka k…ôl…Ē kam disr…õ f…ôp m…Ē.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 15 Iyi k…ôlok-loku, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčontor…ôr Ňča p…ôm…Ē nt…õ Ňč…õnator…ôr s…ôna s…Ē d…ôk…ôcop m…Ē.
\v 16 Awa k'inc…õm-c…õmn…õ toloku ta Mariki nt…õ …õnaloku: ‚ÄĻD…ôromun SaŇč …õnagb…ôt afum, mba n…ôna Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…Ē n…ôndes…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu.‚Äļ
\v 17 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôpoc…õ kin kayi k…Ē Ňčanas…Ēt…ôr Kanu p…ôm…Ē s…ôna aŇč…õ s…ôlaŇč Yesu Krist m…Ē-…õ, an'inatam k…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ nt…õ iŇčk…Ēyams…ôr Kanu m…Ē?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 18 Nt…õ Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē b…ôk…ôc yontor Ňča, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkor-koru Kanu, Ňčacloku: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč s…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…Ē k…ôtam k…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčas…Ēt…Ē tecep…ôr…õn…õ doru nt…õ Kanu k…ôfaŇč m…Ē!¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu nde dare da Antiy…Ēk
\p 
\v 19 Nt…õ andif Etiy…õn m…Ē, k'ancop k…ôt…Ēr…ôs afum alaŇč k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôsams…ôr. Al…Ēma Ňčanak…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Fenisi, al…Ēma Ňčak…Ē Sip…ôr, al…Ēma Ňčak…Ē haŇč Antiy…Ēk, Ňčancluks…õ f…õ nw…õ o nw…õ s…Ē toloku ta Kanu m…õn…õ aSuyif gb…ôc…ôr…ôm.
\v 20 Afum akak…Ē dac…Ē, al…Ēma Ňčanayi, aŇč…õ Ňčanader dare da Antiy…Ēk k…ôy…õf…õ ka s…ôdare sa Sip…ôr k…Ē Sir…õn m…Ē, Ňčancc…Ēp…ôr aKr…õk, Ňčacloku Ňča toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Mariki Yesu.
\v 21 K…ôca ka Mariki k…ônayi alaŇč akak…Ē k…ôroŇč. K…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňčay…Ēn…õ alaŇč, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkaf…ôli b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan nn…Ē Mariki eyi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…õmb…õr…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu ka Yerusal…õm d…ôl…ôŇč…ôs, k'asom Barnabas Antiy…Ēk.
\v 23 K…ôb…õr…õ k…Ēn di, nt…õ …õnaden…ôŇčk p…ôt…Ēt k…Ē p…ôbotu mp…õ Kanu k…ônay…Ēn…õ alaŇč a Antiy…Ēk m…Ē, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt k…Ē. K'eŇčgbiŇč…ôr Ňča k…ôgb…õk…ôr ka Mariki mera yaŇčan f…ôp k…ôlaŇč disr…õ.
\v 24 Barnabas fum w…ôt…Ēt …õnayi. K…ôlaŇč k…ônayi k…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčeyi k…Ē s…Ē dar…ôŇč. K…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňčanc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Mariki dar…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Barnabas …ĒŇčk…Ē dare da Tar…ôs k…ôl…õk Sol.
\v 26 Nt…õ Barnabas …õn…ôŇčk Sol m…Ē, k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē Antiy…Ēk. Teren tin camcam, Ňčact…ôŇčn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč, k…Ē ŇčaŇčt…ôks…õ k…ônay ka afum. D…ôndo Antiy…Ēk, dif…Ē anacop t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…ôwe ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč ¬ęaka Krist.¬Ľ\f + \fr 11:26 \fq Aka Krist\ft = c…ôTabo ¬ę chr√©tiens¬Ľ, it…Ē t…Ēk…Ē kusu ka Kresi ¬ękristianos¬Ľ, it…Ē'ment…ôr c…ôBaka ¬ęaŇč…õ Ňčawur…õn…õ Krist m…Ē¬Ľ.\f*
\p 
\v 27 Mata mam…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē sayib…õ sa Kanu s…ôl…Ēma Ňčantor dare da Antiy…Ēk k…ôy…õf…õ Yerusal…õm.
\v 28 W…ôkin …õnayi Ňča dac…Ē pacwe k…Ē Akabus, k'…õy…õf…õ, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôd…ôŇčk a dor dendeyi doru f…ôp. Dor dad…Ēk…Ē d…õnader deyi t…õm nt…õ K…ôlod …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp m…Ē.
\v 29 K…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôf…õk teta k…ômar ka aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanayi at…Ēf Ňča Yude m…Ē, nw…õ o nw…õ k…Ē nt…õ …õnatam k…ôf…õk m…Ē.
\v 30 It…Ē Ňčanay…Ē: K…Ē Ňčasom Barnabas k…Ē Sol k…ôken…õ ki abeki aŇč…õ Ňčanayi k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yude m…Ē.
\c 12
\s1 K…ôdif ka Sak, k…Ē k…ôb…õr ka Piy…õr d…ôbili
\p 
\v 1 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka at…Ēf Herodu …õnat…ôps…ôr afum alaŇč al…Ēma waca teta k…ôt…Ēr…ôs k…ôŇčan.
\v 2 K'endif…õ Sak w…õnc ka IsaŇč dakma.
\v 3 Nt…õ Herodu …õnan…ôŇčk a m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēn mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ēncb…Ēt aSuyif m…Ē, k'…õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ s…Ē k…ôt…ôp Piy…õr waca, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôcaŇč…ôr k…Ē m…Ē. Mataka ma k…ôsata k…ôp…ĒŇč ka aSuyif m…õnayi: K…ôsata ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēn…ĒŇčk…ôl lebin.
\v 4 Nt…õ Herodu osump…ôr Piy…õr, k'…õmb…õr k…Ē d…ôbili m…Ē, k'…Ēs…ĒŇč c…ôgba maŇčk…ôl…õ ca as…Ēdar k…ôbum k…Ēn, k…ôgba o k…ôgba k…ônay…Ē as…Ēdar maŇčk…ôl…õ. ∆źncc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôboc…ôr Piy…õr kiti f…Ēr ya afum f…ôp kiriŇč k…Ē k…ôsata ka K…ôcep…ôr ka M…õl…õk…õ Medif k…ôncep…ôr-…õ.
\p 
\v 5 Ancbum Piy…õr d…ôbili, mba afum alaŇč Ňčanctolan…õ k…Ē belbel nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē t…õm f…ôp.
\s1 K…ôwur…õ ka Piy…õr d…ôbili
\p 
\v 6 Nt…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ Herodu …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôboc…ôr Piy…õr kiti d…õmb…ôp m…Ē, pibi pap…Ēk…Ē, pakot…õ Piy…õr gbekce m…õr…ôŇč, p…ôf…ônt…ôr…õ p…ôcdir…õ as…Ēdar m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē. Nde d…ôkumba, as…Ēdar Ňčanac…ôm…õ s…Ē d…ôndo Ňčacbum bili.
\v 7 Gb…ôncana babak…Ē, k…Ē w…ôsom w…ôka darenc, m…õl…õk…õ ma W…ôb…õ, mender, k…Ē p…ômot p…Ēs…ĒŇč p…ôwaŇčk…ôra bili disr…õ. K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ mentimi Piy…õr m'ocsut-sut k…Ē k…ôs…ôk, k…Ē moloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ kat…ôna!¬Ľ K…Ē gbekce yoŇčkoŇč…õ k…Ē d…ôwaca.
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôl…õk yamos yam, m…ôb…õrn…õ c…Ēfta cam!¬Ľ K…Ē Piy…õr …Ēy…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē m…õl…õk…õ moloku k…Ē s…Ē: ¬ęM…ôb…õrn…õ yi, m…ôc…ôm'em dar…ôŇč!¬Ľ
\v 9 K…Ē Piy…õr …õnc…ôm…õ m…õl…õk…õ mm…õ dar…ôŇč. ∆źnac…ôr…õ f…õ a k…ômar ka m…õl…õk…õ kaŇčk…Ē a kance k…Ē: k…ôn…ôŇčk ka darenc k…Ē nk…Ēn …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ.
\v 10 Nt…õ Ňčancep…ôr abum ac…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē k…Ē aka m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp kumba ka f…õc nk…õ k…ônat…õf…ôrn…õ dare m…Ē. K…Ē kumba k…ôŇčgbit…õ kis…ôrka f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč, k…Ē Ňčawur, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēl…Ēma. Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ m…õsak Piy…õr.
\p 
\v 11 Nt…õ p…ôndec…õrŇč…õ Piy…õr m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęInc…ôr…õ oŇč a W…ôb…õ osomna m…õl…õk…õ m…Ēn, mede m…õbaŇč im waca wa Herodu disr…õ, k…Ē p…ôl…õc p…Ēk…Ē aSuyif ŇčanafaŇč'em m…Ē f…ôp.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 Nt…õ …õnc…ôr…õ ti oŇč m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde k…ôl…Ē ka Mari, iya w…ôka IsaŇč, nw…õ ancdeŇč…ôr tewe ta ¬ęMark¬Ľ m…Ē, nde afum alar…ôm ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ Ňčactola Kanu m…Ē.
\v 13 Nt…õ Piy…õr osut-sut kumba ka d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôyec…ôra w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Rodu, …Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ k…ôk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl.
\v 14 K…Ē Rodu …õn…õp…ôl dim da Piy…õr, mba p…ôbotu disr…õ …õŇčgbiti f…õ kumba. K'…õy…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēloku afum aŇč…õ Ňčanayi d…ôk…ôl…Ē m…Ē a Piy…õr ender, k'…õnc…ôm…õ d…ôkumba.
\p 
\v 15 K…Ē afum Ňčaloku Rodu: ¬ęM…ôna m…ôntamn…õ f…õ!¬Ľ Mba k'…õŇčgb…ôc a t…Ēk…Ē oloku m…Ē it…Ē teyi. K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęM…õl…õk…õ m…Ēn m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 Piy…õr nk…Ēn p…ôcsut-sut k…ôsut-sut d…ôm kumba. Nt…õ ŇčaŇčgbiti kumba k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk Piy…õr m…Ē, k…Ē cusu c…ôwos Ňča.
\v 17 K'olok-lok…ôr…õ Ňča k…ôca a ŇčacaŇčk, k'…Ēl…Ēm…ôr Ňča nt…õ W…ôb…õ owur…õ k…Ē d…ôbili m…Ē. K'oloku: ¬ęN…ôloku ti Sak k…Ē aw…õnc asu.¬Ľ K'owur k'…ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma.
\p 
\v 18 Nt…õ dec d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôyamayama p…Ēp…ĒŇč peyi as…Ēdar dac…Ē: Akes…Ēt…Ē Piy…õr-…õ, Deke eyi-…õ?
\v 19 K…Ē Herodu osom a pat…õn Piy…õr, mba Ňčanan…ôŇčk f…õ k…Ē. K'omboc…ôr as…Ēdar akak…Ē Ňčancbum Piy…õr m…Ē kiti, k…Ē Herodu oloku a padif Ňča. Nt…õ telip m…Ē, k…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Yude, k'ontor dare da Sesari k…ôk…Ēcep…ôr…õn…õ di t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma.
\s1 K…ôfi ka w…ôb…õ Herodu
\p 
\v 20 Herodu …õnayi k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē aka s…ôdare sa Tir k…Ē Sid…ĒŇč. Mba k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ disr…õ aka s…ôdare sas…Ēk…Ē Ňčander Ňčab…ôp Herodu. Nt…õ Ňčas…õp k…ôs…Ēt…ôr B…ôlastus nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôt…Ēmp…ôr ka mes ma k…ôl…Ē disr…õ ma w…ôb…õ Herodu m…Ē, p…ômar Ňča k…ôs…Ēt…ôr Herodu p…ôforu, bawo nd…Ēr…Ēn t…Ēf yaŇčan y…Ēncs…Ēt…Ē yeri.
\p 
\v 21 Nt…õ tataka taŇčan t…õt…ôŇčn…õ t…õmb…ôp m…Ē, k…Ē Herodu …õmb…õrn…õ yamos y…Ēn ya d…õb…õ, p…ônd…õ nde aŇčgbancan Ňč…Ēn p…ôclok-lok…ôr Ňča.
\v 22 T…õm nt…õ afum f…ôp Ňčanckul…õ-kul…õ, a Ňčacloku: ¬ęBaf…Ē dim da fum d…Ē dand…õ, mba da kanu d…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 23 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē m…õl…õk…õ ma W…ôb…õ mosut k…Ē, bawo …õnayek-yek…ôs f…õ Kanu, k…Ē y…õt yoncop k…ôs…Ēm k…Ē, k'efi.
\p 
\v 24 Toloku ta W…ôb…õ t…õncsam oŇč k…ôsam d…ôm t…Ēck…Ē kiriŇč.
\p 
\v 25 Barnabas k…Ē Sol nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ k…ôsom k…ôŇčan nde dare da Yerusal…õm m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalukus, Ňčacl…õk…õn…õ IsaŇč, nw…õ ancdeŇč…ôr tewe ta ¬ęMark¬Ľ m…Ē.
\c 13
\s1 Ay…õk-y…õk Barnabas k…Ē Sol k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ ka moloku ma Kanu
\p 
\v 1 K…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanayi dare da Antiy…Ēk m…Ē, sayib…õ-e k…Ē at…ôks…õ Ňčanayi Ňča dac…Ē: Barnabas, Simey…ĒŇč nw…õ ancdeŇč…ôr tewe ta ¬ęW…ôbi¬Ľ m…Ē, Lusiyus w…ôka Sir…õn, Manah…õŇč nw…õ anadusum k…ôfo kin k…Ē Herodu w…ôb…õ w…ôka topoc tin k'ayer at…Ēf k…ômaŇčk…ôl…õ-…õ, k…Ē Sol.
\v 2 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, alaŇč akak…Ē Ňčanckor-koru Kanu, ŇčasuŇč…õn…õ s…Ē, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčoloku: ¬ęN…ôc…ômb…ôr em k…ôs…ôk Barnabas k…Ē Sol, teta y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē inawen…õ Ňča m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 3 Nt…õ alaŇč Ňčalip k…ôsuŇč k…Ē k…ôtola Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčandeŇč…ôr Barnabas k…Ē Sol waca, k…Ē Ňčasom Ňča.
\s1 K…ôyi ka Barnabas k…Ē Sol nde Sip…ôr
\p 
\v 4 Nt…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčosom Barnabas k…Ē Sol m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantor at…Ēf Ňča Selusi, d…ôndo Ňčanal…õk abil k…Ē Ňčancali k…ôk…Ē ka mokuru ma Sip…ôr.
\v 5 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ Salamin m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčancop k…ôluks…õ toloku ta Kanu nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif. IsaŇč …õnayi di p…ôcmar Ňča.
\p 
\v 6 Nt…õ Ňčancali mokuru haŇč dare da Paf…Ēs m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…ôp di fum w…ôw…õŇčk…õ w…ôl…Ēma p…ôcwen…õ sayib…õ, mba ta …Ēy…Ēn…õ si-…õ. W…ôSuyif …õnayi, pacwe k…Ē Bar-Yesu.
\v 7 W…ôw…õŇčk…õ w…ôkak…Ē ndena Serkus Polu …õnayi, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka s…ôdare sa at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē. Nk…Ēn Serkus Polu w…ôrkun w…ôcempi domp …õnayi. K'ender k'ewe Barnabas k…Ē Sol p…ôct…õn k…ônen…õ Ňča toloku ta Kanu.
\v 8 Elimas, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē ¬ęw…ôw…õŇčk…õ¬Ľ kusu k…ôŇčan, …õncgb…õk…ôl moloku ma Barnabas k…Ē Sol, p…ôct…õn k…ôkaf…ôli k…ôlaŇč ka w…ôkiriŇč Serkus Polu.
\v 9 Mba Sol, nw…õ ancwe s…Ē Pol m…Ē, Amera Ňäecempi Ňčeyi k…Ē dar…ôŇč, k'…õŇčgb…ôtn…õ Elimas.
\v 10 K…Ē Sol oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôna w…ôkak…Ē m…ôla mowul k…Ē yem m…Ē, w…ôka amera Ňč…õl…õc, w…ôter p…ôlompu f…ôp, m…ôf…Ēsak k…ôkaf…ôli-kaf…ôli s…ôp…Ē sa W…ôb…õ Kanu ns…õ s…ôlomp m…Ē ba?
\v 11 Nd…õk…ôl k…ôca ka W…ôb…õ k…ôy'…ôm k…ôroŇč: W…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk m…ôndey…Ēn…õ! T…õm tendeb…ôp, m…ôndeyi ta m…ôn…ôŇčk p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa dec-…õ.¬Ľ
\p Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē f…Ēr y…Ēy…Ē k…Ē pafulu k…Ē kubump k…ôw…õk…ôrn…õ k…Ē. K'…õy…õf…õ k…ônana-nana p…ôct…õn k…ôca nk…õ k…ôŇčk…Ēsump…ôr k…Ē k…ôsol…õ m…Ē.
\v 12 Nt…õ w…ôkiriŇč ka d…Ēt…Ēf …õn…ôŇčk nt…õ t…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôlaŇč. M…õt…ôks…õ mm…õ …õnanen…õ Barnabas k…Ē Sol teta W…ôb…õ m…Ē m…õnab…Ēt k…Ē d…õb…ôk…ôc.
\s1 Pol k…Ē Barnabas dare da Antiy…Ēk nde Pisidi
\p 
\v 13 Nt…õ Pol k…Ē asol …Ēn Ňčay…õf…õ dare da Paf…Ēs m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayekti ab…õla k…ôk…Ē ka Perke, nde at…Ēf Ňča PaŇčfili. K…Ē IsaŇč Mark …õŇčgb…õy Ňča, k'olukus Yerusal…õm.
\v 14 K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ Perke Ňčac…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē daŇčan dar…ôŇč haŇč Antiy…Ēk, at…Ēf Ňča Pisidi. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif simiti, d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm, k…Ē Ňčand…õ.
\v 15 Nt…õ alip k…ôkaraŇč Tawur…õta Musa k…Ē Sayib…õ m…Ē, k…Ē ab…õ a k…ôl…Ē ka d…ôk…ôtola da Kanu nd…õ Ňčaloku Barnabas k…Ē Pol: ¬ęAw…õnc asu aŇča, k…Ē n…ôy…Ē toloku tec…ôp…ôs…õ ab…ôk…ôc nt…õ n…ôŇčfaŇč k…ôloku afum m…Ē, n…ôloku ti.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 K…Ē Pol …õy…õf…õ, k'ondot k…ôca, k'oloku: ¬ęArkun a Yisrayel, k…Ē n…ôna alp…ôs aŇč…õ n…ôŇčnes…õ Kanu m…Ē, n…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl!
\v 17 Kanu ka afum akaŇč…õ, Kanu ka Yisrayel, k…ônay…õk-y…õk atem asu, k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôla t…õm nt…õ Ňčanayi decik…ôra Misira m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu kin kaŇčk…Ē k…ôwur…õn…õ Ňča at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr fa k…ôca k…Ēn.
\v 18 K…Ē k…ôl…õk…õ Ňča mes m…õl…õc maŇčan nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40).
\v 19 Nt…õ Kanu k…ônim afum a cusuŇčka cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč nde at…Ēf Ňča KanaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē afum …Ēn nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňč…Ēy…Ēn…õ Ňča k…õ m…Ē.
\v 20 Mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp m…õnawon meren masar maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (450).
\p Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča aboc kiti, aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr d…õb…õ da aka Yisrayel m…Ē haŇč k…ôb…ôp ka t…õm ta aŇčnabi Samiy…õl.
\v 21 K…Ē t…õy…õf…õ d…ônda k…Ē aka Yisrayel Ňčawer Kanu w…ôb…õ. K…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča Sawul wan ka Kis p…ôy…Ēn…õ Ňča w…ôb…õ meren w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ (40). Fum w…ôka kusuŇčka ka BeŇčyamin …õnayi.
\v 22 Nt…õ Kanu k…ôf…ôn Sawul m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča w…ôb…õ Dawuda, nw…õ Kanu k…ônalok…õ nt…õ m…Ē: ‚ÄĻIn…ôŇčk Dawuda wan ka Yisay, fum …Ēf…Ē nw…õ s…ôwur…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc m…Ē, inc…õm-c…õmn…õ a endey…Ē m…õfaŇč mem f…ôp.‚Äļ\x - \xo 13:22 \xt 1 Samiyel 15.23\x*
\p 
\v 23 K…ôb…ônda ka dokomb…ôra da nk…Ēn Dawuda, dif…Ē Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč k…ôkom ka Yesu Krist k…ôdey…Ēn…õ ka nw…õ endeyac afum a Yisrayel, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ k…ônas…ĒŇč ti atem asu temer m…Ē.
\v 24 Ta Yesu …õntader-…õ, SaŇč …õnacam k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ afum a Yisrayel f…ôp Ňčas…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan y…õt…õf…ôrn…õ Kanu m…Ē.
\v 25 Nt…õ SaŇč …õncl…ôp…ôs y…õb…ôc ny…õ Kanu k…ônasom k…Ē m…Ē, encyif: ‚ÄĻP…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ ponu, an'iy…Ēn…õ-…õ? Nw…õ n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a nk…Ēn iy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, baf…Ē nk…Ēn iy…Ēn…õ de! Mba endeder tadar…ôŇč tem nw…õ p…ônt…Ēmar im yati k…ôsik…ôli c…Ēfta d…ôw…õc…ôk m…Ē.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 26 Aw…õnc im aŇča, n…ôna awut aka dokom da Abraham, k…Ē n…ôna ak…Ē n…ôŇčnes…õ Kanu m…Ē, s…ôna Ňč…Ē anak…õr…õ toloku nt…õ tendeyac su m…Ē.
\v 27 Mba aka Yerusal…õm k…Ē ab…õ aŇčan Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ fum nw…õ Yesu …õnay…Ēn…õ m…Ē. Ňäanagb…õk…ôr…õ f…õ s…Ē moloku ma sayib…õ mm…õ anckaraŇč simiti o simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm m…Ē, mba Ňčanader Ňčalas moloku mam…Ēk…Ē nt…õ Ňčanaboc…ôr Yesu kiti m…Ē.
\v 28 Ňäanas…Ēt…Ē f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ t…Ēk…Ē p…ônamar a Ňčadif…õ Yesu m…Ē, mba k…Ē Ňčantola Pilat k…ôdif k…Ēn.
\v 29 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôy…Ē mes f…ôp m…Ēk…Ē anacic tet…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantor…õ k…Ē d…ôt…Ēk y…õp…ômp…ôl, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaboc k…Ē d…ôkufu.
\v 30 Mba Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē.
\v 31 K…Ē Yesu owur…ôr mataka m…õlar…ôm ak…Ē Ňčanap…õ k…Ē nk…Ēn k…ôy…õf…õ Kalile k…ôk…Ē ka Yerusal…õm m…Ē. Ňäa Ňčay…Ēn…õ oŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ ka Yesu afi dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňča Ňčantam s…Ē k…ôluks…õ ti afum al…Ēma.
\p 
\v 32 K…Ē s…ôna toloku t…Ēt…Ēt tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē s…ôloku nu: Temer mp…õ anas…ĒŇč atem asu m…Ē,
\v 33 Kanu k…ôlas…õ su ti belbel, s…ôna dokom…õn…õ daŇčan, k…ôyekti ka Yesu, p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē ancic ti Yabura Dawuda ya m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ m…Ē:
\q1 ‚ÄĻWan kem m…ôy…Ēn…õ,
\q1 bawo in'okom …ôm k…ôy…õf…õ m…Ēk…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 13:33 \xt Yabura 2.7\x*
\m 
\v 34 Kanu k…ônaloku a k…ôndeyekti k…Ē afi dac…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta oluks…ôrn…õ p…ôte m…Ē. Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ p…ôloku:
\q1 ‚ÄĻIndes…ĒŇč nu memer mosoku mm…õ inas…ĒŇč Dawuda m…Ē,
\q1 memer mm…õ m…Ēy…Ēn…õ kance m…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 13:34 \xt Esayi 55.3\x*
\m 
\v 35 It…Ē Kanu k…ôlok…õn…õ k…ôfo k…ôl…Ēma Yabura Dawuda disr…õ:
\q1 ‚ÄĻM…ôf…Ēdesak W…ôsoku w…ôkam p…ôte d…ôkufu.‚Äļ \x - \xo 13:35 \xt Yabura 16.10\x*
\b
\p 
\v 36 Dawuda nk…Ēn …õnab…ôc t…õfaŇč ta Kanu d…õt…õmp d…Ēn disr…õ, k'…õf…ônt…ôr…õ k'efi, k'awup k…Ē nde atem …Ēn k…ôs…ôk, k'ente d…ôkufu.
\v 37 Mba fum nw…õ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…ôf…Ēt…õ afi dac…Ē m…Ē, nk…Ēn …õnate f…õ.
\p 
\v 38 Aw…õnc im aŇča, n…ôc…ôr…õ ti: Teta nk…Ēn Yesu t'ancam…õ nu k…ôŇčaŇčn…õn…õ ka kiciya, kiciya nk…õ sariy…õ sa Musa s…ônat…Ētam k…ôs…Ēk…ôs…õ nu m…Ē.
\v 39 Ti disr…õ, nw…õ o nw…õ …õŇčgb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Yesu m…Ē, Kanu k…ôndes…Ēk…ôs k…Ē.
\v 40 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ mes m…Ēk…Ē sayib…õ Ňčancic m…Ē ta m…õb…ôp nu:
\q1 
\v 41 ‚ÄĻN…ôm…Ēm…ôn n…ôna afum aŇč…õ n…ômb…Ēt…ôr k…ôfani m…Ē!
\q1 N…ôyi p…ôciyan…õ disr…õ, n…ôs…Ēl…õ!
\q1 Bawo ina k…ôy…Ē k'inder tes t…Ēl…Ēma kiyi konu doru kaŇčk…õ disr…õ,
\q1 tes nt…õ n…ônt…ĒdelaŇč k…Ē fum oloku nu ti-…õ.‚Äļ¬Ľ\x - \xo 13:41 \xt Habakuk 1.5\x*
\p 
\v 42 Nt…õ Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčawur d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif m…Ē, k…Ē afum Ňčal…õts…õn…õ Ňča k…ôder s…Ē simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm d…Ēk…Ē dender m…Ē k…ôdegb…Ēk…ôr…õ moloku min mayi.
\v 43 Nt…õ k…ônay k…ôsakt…õn…õ m…Ē, aSuyif alar…ôm k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ din…õ d'aSuyif m…Ē Ňčanc…õps…õ Pol k…Ē Barnabas k…ôlok-loku k…ôŇčan disr…õ. K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčas…õp k…ôc…ôp…ôs Ňča b…ôk…ôc teta k…ôsump…ôr k…ômar ka Kanu.
\p 
\v 44 Simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nd…õ d…õnac…Ēnc m…Ē, k…Ē aka dare f…ôp ŇčaloŇčkan…õ k…ôk…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta W…ôb…õ.
\v 45 Nt…õ aSuyif Ňčanan…ôŇčk k…ônay ka afum m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…Ē k…ôraca k…ôp…ĒŇč. K…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl Pol, Ňčacl…Ēm…ôs k…Ē.
\p 
\v 46 Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčamb…ôkn…õ k…ôloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôna yati p…ônamar a pacop k…ôluks…õ toloku ta Kanu. Mba nt…õ n…ônabup…ôr…õ ti, k…Ē n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a p…ômar f…õ a n…ôs…Ēt…Ē kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru m…Ē, nd…õk…ôl oŇč s…ôna s…ôndekaf…ôl…õ s…ôk…Ē ndena ak…Ē Ňčant…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…Ē.
\v 47 Bawo W…ôb…õ osom su nt…õ:
\q1 ‚ÄĻIs…ĒŇč'am k…ôy…Ēn…õ p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa t…Ēf,
\q1 nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ m…ôkek…ôr…õ k…ôyac ka afum
\q1 haŇč nde c…ôp…ôc ca doru f…ôp c…ôyi m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ\x - \xo 13:47 \xt Esayi 49.6\x*
\p 
\v 48 Nt…õ afum Ňčane ti m…Ē, k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif d…ôb…ôk…ôc. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkor-koru toloku ta W…ôb…õ, aŇč…õ Kanu k…ônac…ômb…ôr…õ kiyi w…ôyeŇč ka doru o doru m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ alaŇč.
\p 
\v 49 K…Ē toloku ta W…ôb…õ t…õsam…ôs…ôr d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp.
\v 50 Mba k…Ē aSuyif al…Ēma ŇčaŇčgbiŇč…ôr aran abeki akor-koru Kanu, k…Ē abeki a dare, k…Ē Ňčancop k…ôt…Ēr…ôs Pol k…Ē Barnabas teta k…ôlaŇč k…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčamb…õl…ôs Ňča dare daŇčan.
\v 51 Pol k…Ē Barnabas ŇčaŇčkoŇč…ôr Ňča k…ôf…ôl ka w…õc…ôk waŇčan, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ sede sa k…ôfati k…ôŇčan k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ikoniyon. \f + \fr 13:51 \fq ŇäaŇčkoŇč…ôr Ňča k…ôbof ka w…õc…ôk waŇčan\ft = p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Mariki Yesu …õnaloku ti ac…õps…õ …Ēn dar…ôŇč m…Ē: a dare o dare d…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē a tawos…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu m…Ē, a ŇčakoŇč…ôr dare dad…Ēk…Ē k…ôbof ka w…õc…ôk waŇčan. Ti t'eŇčment…ôr a Ňčanacep…ôr dare dad…Ēk…Ē ak…Ē ant…Ēwos…õ k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu.\f*
\v 52 P…ômb…Ēt ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õnayi k…Ē Ňča.
\c 14
\s1 Pol k…Ē Barnabas nde dare da Ikoniyon
\p 
\v 1 D…ôndo dare da Ikoniyon, Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčamb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif. K…Ē Ňčaloku moloku mm…õ m…õnas…ĒŇč…õ aSuyif k…Ē aKresi alar…ôm k…ôgb…õk…ôr Yesu k…ôlaŇč m…Ē.
\v 2 Mba k…Ē aSuyif ayeŇčki s…ôbomp aŇč…õ Ňčamb…õr…ôs afum at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…õr k…ôter ka aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč.
\v 3 Ti disr…õ, Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčamb…Ēl…ôs…õ kiyi k…ôŇčan d…ôndo dare dad…Ēk…Ē. K…Ē Ňčalok-lok…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôr mera yaŇčan teta MARIKI. K…Ē MARIKI …Ēs…ĒŇč Ňča f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…ôy…Ēn…õ mes m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ, p…ôcment…ôr s…Ē kance ka mes m…Ēk…Ē Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčanccam k…ômar k…Ēn disr…õ.
\v 4 K…Ē k…ônay ka afum a dare dad…Ēk…Ē Ňčayers…õn…õ. Al…Ēma Ňčanayin…õ aSuyif, al…Ēma Ňčayin…õ asom a Yesu.
\v 5 Mba, aSuyif k…Ē acik…ôra k…ôb…ôp ka ab…õ aŇčan Ňčanalomp…ôsn…õ k…ôk…Ēt…Ēr…ôs Pol k…Ē Barnabas k…ôca-cas k…ôŇčan masar haŇč Ňčadif Ňča.
\v 6 Nt…õ Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčane ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ēyacn…õ nde List…ôr k…Ē D…õrb…õ, s…ôdare sa at…Ēf Ňča Likayoni, k…Ē s…ôk…ôs…ôk sayi.
\v 7 D…ôndo s…Ē Ňčanccam toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Yesu.
\s1 Pol k…Ē Barnabas nde dare da List…ôr
\p 
\v 8 Fum w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi List…ôr p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôtoŇčkulu, w…õc…ôk w…Ēn w…õnafi. K…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ aŇčkom k…Ē m…Ē, ali …Ēnck…Ēt f…õ. ∆źnand…õ,
\v 9 p…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku ma Pol. K…Ē Pol …õŇčgb…ôtn…õ k…Ē. Nt…õ …õn…ôŇčk a w…ôtoŇčkulu …Ēy…Ē k…ôlaŇč nk…õ k…ôntam k…ôyac k…Ē m…Ē,
\v 10 k…Ē Pol olok…õ k…Ē dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč: ¬ęM…ôy…õf…õ! M…ôc…ôm…õ w…õc…ôk wam k…ôroŇč, m…ôlomp!¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôrkun nw…õ oyokn…õ, k'…õy…õf…õ k'…õnc…ôm…õ k…ôk…Ēt.
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē k…ônay ka afum akak…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk nt…õ Pol …Ēy…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē afum k…ônay Ňčamp…õn…õ c…ôbebe Ňčacloku c…ôLikayoni: ¬ęCanu c…ônt…ôŇčk…ôl…õ afum k…Ē c…ôntor nn…Ē ndorosu!¬Ľ
\v 12 Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Ňčawe Barnabas ¬ęSus¬Ľ, Ňčawe Pol nk…Ēn ¬ęH…õrm…õs¬Ľ, bawo Pol nk…Ēn enccep…ôr…õn…õ moloku. \f + \fr 14:12 \ft Din…õ da aKresi ¬ęSus¬Ľ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ ka canu, k…Ē ¬ęH…õrm…õs¬Ľ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ k…Ēn moloku. \f*
\v 13 W…ôloŇčn…õn…õ ka Sus …õnak…õr…õ mura k…Ē y…õn…õk…ôs nde d…ôk…ôb…õr…õ da k…ôl…Ē ka d…ôk…ôloŇčn…õ nd…õ deyi nde dare d…ôkusu m…Ē. P…ônabas k…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ mi, nk…Ēn k…Ē k…ônay ka afum nn…Ē Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčayi m…Ē.
\p 
\v 14 Mba nt…õ asom a Yesu Barnabas k…Ē Pol Ňčane ti m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawal-wali yamos yaŇčan, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ afum dac…Ē Ňčackul…õ-kul…õ:
\v 15 ¬ęAnapa! Ta ake t…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ tant…õ-…õ? S…ôna s…Ē, afum Ňč…Ē s…ôy…Ēn…õ, palomp…ôs su tin tayi p…ôm…Ē n…ôna. S…ôloku nu toloku t…Ēt…Ēt nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôsak mes m…õyamayama mam…õ m…Ē! N…ôkaf…ôl…ôr Kanu f…Ēr nk…õ k…ôyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē, Kanu nk…õ k…ôlomp…ôs k…Ēm, ant…Ēf k…Ē k…ôba, k…Ē ca y…Ēk…Ē yeyi ki m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 16 D…õt…õmp d…Ēk…Ē d…õnacep…ôr m…Ē, Kanu k…ônawos…õn…õ afum a t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp Ňčactam k…ôc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē dar…ôŇč d…Ēk…Ē ŇčaŇčfaŇč m…Ē.
\v 17 Ali nt…õ nk…Ēn Kanu k…ônat…Ēsak k…ôcment…ôr nu d…Ēt…Ēt d…ôm…Ēy…Ē m…Ēn m…Ē, bawo k…ôncs…ĒŇč nu w…ôcaf…ôn, k…ôncs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē y…Ēb…Ēf yonu k…ôkom p…ôlar…ôm, k…Ē k…ôncs…ĒŇč nu s…Ē yeri y…õlar…ôm, k…Ē k…ônclas nu s…Ē p…ôbotu d…ôb…ôk…ôc.¬Ľ
\v 18 Ali nt…õ Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčanaloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, p…ôcuca p…õnayi Ňča k…ôyams…ôr ka k…ônay kaŇčk…Ē k…ôloŇčn…õ c…ôna nc…õ ŇčanafaŇč k…ôloŇčn…õn…õ Ňča m…Ē.
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčander k…ôy…õf…õ Antiy…Ēk Ňča Pisidi k…Ē Ikoniyon, k…Ē Ňčas…õp haŇč k…Ē Ňčantal…ôr k…ônay ka afum akak…Ē. Nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē k…ônay ka afum aŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôca-cas Pol. T…õlp…ôs k…Ē ŇčaliŇč…ôs k…Ē haŇč dare k…ôs…ôk, Ňčac…õm-c…õmn…õ a efi.
\v 20 Mba nt…õ ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčanadek…õl Pol m…Ē, k'…õy…õf…õ, k'oluks…ôrn…õ dare. D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē dare da D…õrb…õ, nk…Ēn k…Ē Barnabas.
\s1 K…ôlukus ka Pol k…Ē Barnabas Antiy…Ēk at…Ēf Ňča Siri
\p 
\v 21 Nt…õ Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčamb…ôp dare da D…õrb…õ k…Ē Ňčancam d…ôndo toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Yesu. K…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē di afum alar…ôm aŇč…õ ŇčanalaŇč teta Yesu m…Ē. Nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē Ňčal…õk d…Ēp…Ē k…ôlukus ka List…ôr, Ikoniyon k…Ē Antiy…Ēk Ňča Pisidi.
\v 22 K…Ē Ňčac…ôp…ôs ac…õps…õ dar…ôŇč b…ôk…ôc, ŇčacgbiŇč…ôr Ňča k…ôyin…õ k…ôlaŇč, Ňčacloku: ¬ęK…Ē s…ôna, m…õn…õ s…ôcep…ôr…õn…õ p…ôcuy p…õlar…ôm a s…ôcb…õr…õ nde akip Ňča d…õb…õ da Kanu d…ônt…Ēf.¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčay…õk-y…õk…õ Ňča abeki d…ôk…ôloŇčkan…õ f…ôp da alaŇč. Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôtola Kanu k…Ē k…ôsuŇč m…Ē, Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčas…ĒŇč Ňča Mariki nw…õ Ňčanagb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč m…Ē k…ôbum k…ôŇčan.
\v 24 K…Ē Ňčancep…ôr d…Ēp…Ē da at…Ēf Ňča Pisidi k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ at…Ēf Ňča PaŇčfili.
\v 25 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôloku toloku ta MARIKI dare da Perke m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantor dare da Atali.
\p 
\v 26 D…ôndo Atali, dif…Ē Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčanal…õk abil k…Ē Ňčancali k…ôk…Ē Antiy…Ēk Ňča Siri, dare nd…õ anatolan…õ Ňča k…ômar ka Kanu teta y…õb…ôc ny…õ Ňčanalip m…Ē.
\v 27 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaloŇčka alaŇč a Antiy…Ēk f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčal…Ēm t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônay…Ēn…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē nk…Ēn Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif k…ôlaŇč m…Ē.
\v 28 Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčawon d…ôndo dare dad…Ēk…Ē k…Ē ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč.
\c 15
\s1 K…ôb…ôps…õn…õ ka alaŇč nde Yerusal…õm
\p 
\v 1 Afum al…Ēma Ňčanay…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Yude, Ňčact…ôks…õ aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč nt…õ: K…Ē n…ônt…Ēy…Ē pak…ônc nu p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē t…Ēy…Ē tokur ta Musa toloku ti m…Ē, Kanu k…ôf…Ēdewos…õ k…ôyac nu.
\v 2 Nt…õ Pol k…Ē Barnabas ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē arkun akak…Ē k…ôliŇč…õn…õ k…ôŇčan moloku m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ a nk…Ēn Pol k…Ē Barnabas k…ôb…ôp ka akin akin arkun akak…Ē dac…Ē, Ňčak…Ē Yerusal…õm k…ôk…Ēn…Ēn…õ moloku mam…Ēk…Ē nn…Ē asom a Yesu k…Ē abeki a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 3 K…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Antiy…Ēk Ňčas…ĒŇč Ňča daka nd…õ p…ônamar a Ňčay…Ē teta mar…ônt m…Ē. Nt…õ Ňčancep…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Fenisi k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Samari m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčal…Ēm…ôr Ňča nt…õ at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif ŇčaŇčkaf…ôli b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan nn…Ē Mariki eyi m…Ē, Ňčacs…ĒŇč…õ aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč f…ôp p…ôbotu.
\v 4 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ Yerusal…õm m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč, asom a Yesu, k…Ē abeki a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ŇčambaŇč Ňča. Nt…õ t…Ē Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčal…Ēm t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ônay…Ē f…ôp k…Ē Ňča m…Ē.
\p 
\v 5 Awa k…Ē aFarisi al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ alaŇč m…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęP…ômar pak…ônc at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif, pagbiŇč…ôr Ňča s…Ē k…ôlel…ôs sariy…õ sa Musa.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 Asom a Yesu k…Ē abeki a alaŇč aka Yerusal…õm Ňčanab…ôps…õn…õ k…ôk…Ēm…Ēm…ôn ka tes tat…Ēk…Ē.
\v 7 Nt…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôwon Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Piy…õr …õy…õf…õ k'oloku: ¬ęArkun, aw…õnc im aŇča, n…ônc…ôr…õ ti: A p…ôwon nt…õ Kanu k…ônay…õk-y…õk im n…ôna dac…Ē k…ôcam ka Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt ka Yesu, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif Ňčatam k…ône ti k…Ē k…ôlaŇč ti m…Ē.
\v 8 Kanu k…ônc…ôr…õ b…ôk…ôc ya afum, Ki yati k…ôment…ôr a k…ômbaŇč at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif, bawo k…ôs…ĒŇč Ňča s…Ē Amera Ňäecempi p…ôm…Ē s…ôna.
\v 9 Ali k…ôgb…õy k…ôf…õt …õŇčgb…õy f…õ su k…Ē at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif, bawo k…ôlaŇč k'…Ēs…Ēk…ôs Ňča b…ôk…ôc.
\v 10 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, ta ake t…Ē n…ôfaŇč k…ôd…ôk…ôt…ôr…õ Kanu-…õ? Nt…õ n…ôfaŇč k…ôsars…ôr ac…õps…õ a Yesu tes tocu nt…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ atem asu haŇč s…ôna yati s…ônt…Ētam k…ôsar…õ m…Ē.
\v 11 Mba s…ôlaŇč a andeyac su k…ômar ka Mariki Yesu disr…õ p…ôm…Ē Ňča at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 K…ônay ka afum f…ôp ŇčanacaŇčk, k'anc…ôŇčk…ôl oŇč moloku ma Barnabas k…Ē Pol. K…Ē Ňčal…Ēm mes m…õw…õy-w…õy k…Ē m…õgb…õk…ôr…õ mm…õ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôy…Ē at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif dac…Ē m…Ē.
\v 13 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôloku m…Ē, k…Ē Sak endeŇč…ôr: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča! N…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im!
\v 14 Simey…ĒŇč …Ēl…Ēm t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nt…õ Kanu k…ônader k…ôy…õk-y…õk t…Ēf ya doru f…ôp dac…Ē, afum aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ ak…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 15 It…Ē moloku ma sayib…õ mosoln…õ k…Ē moloku ma Simey…ĒŇč p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ancic ti m…Ē:
\q1 
\v 16 ‚ÄĻK…Ē Mariki oloku: ¬ęK…Ē tant…õ tencep…ôr-…õ, indeder s…Ē.
\q1 Indeyekti s…Ē abal Ňča Dawuda nŇč…õ Ňč…õnat…õmp…õn…õ m…Ē,
\q1 indeyekti samba sa abal ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē,
\q1 Indec…ômb…ôr Ňči s…Ē Ňčolomp,
\q1 
\v 17 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ afum alp…ôs Ňčat…õn ina Mariki m…Ē.
\q1 ∆źy, d…ôt…Ēf f…ôp ny…õ anakorn…õ tewe tem m…Ē.¬Ľ
\q1 Mariki oloku nt…õ, nw…õ …ĒŇčy…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē
\q1 
\v 18 ∆źnas…ĒŇč…õ mi k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē.‚Äļ\x - \xo 15:18 \xt Amos 9.11-12\x*
\p 
\v 19 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ, ina Sak, iŇčwos…õ s…Ē a ta pat…Ēr…ôs at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčant…õf…ôrn…õ nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē.
\v 20 Mba pacic…õ Ňča a Ňčak…õmb…ôrn…õ p…ôt…Ēcemp mp…õ p…õy…õf…õ nn…Ē k…ôtola m…õr…ôŇčka k…ôyi m…Ē, k…Ē dalak…Ē, k…Ē k…ôs…Ēm ka s…õm ny…õ ant…Ēfay m…Ē, Ňčak…õmb…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ômun mecir.
\v 21 K…ôy…õf…õ d…õt…õmp d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē, Musa …Ēy…Ē s…ôdare f…ôp afum aŇč…õ Ňčaloku tet…Ēn m…Ē, bawo aŇčkaraŇč Tawureta t…Ēn simiti o simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif.¬Ľ
\s1 Areka Ňč…Ēk…Ē anaken…õ alaŇč at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…Ē
\p 
\v 22 Asom a Yesu k…Ē abeki k…ôb…ôp ka k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč Yesu k…Ērk…Ēr Ňčande Ňčam…Ēm…ôn a p…ômar pay…õk-y…õk Ňča dac…Ē afum al…Ēma ak…Ē p…ômar a pasom Antiy…Ēk m…Ē, k…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka Pol k…Ē Barnabas. Ti disr…õ k…Ē Ňčay…õk-y…õk afum m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēmp…ôr delel aw…õnc aŇča dac…Ē m…Ē: Yudas w…ôk…Ē ancwe s…Ē Barsabas m…Ē, k…Ē Silas.
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčasom Ňča k…Ē areka ny…õ:
\p ¬ęAw…õnc anu, asom a Yesu k…Ē abeki k…Ē alaŇč Ňčancic…õ nu areka, n…ôna aw…õnc su aŇča aka Antiy…Ēk, aka Siri, aka Silisi aŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif m…Ē:
\p S…ôyif nu!
\v 24 S…ône a afum asu al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčawur nn…Ē ndorosu m…Ē, Ňčant…Ēr…ôs nu k…Ē Ňčampemp…õ nu moloku maŇčan, mm…õ s…ônt…Ēsom Ňča m…Ē.
\v 25 Nt…õ s…ônen…õn…õ ak…Ē s…ônt…ôŇčn…õ ti m…Ē, it…Ē s…ôn…ôŇčk a p…ôntes…õ s…ôy…õk-y…õk afum, s…ôsom Ňča nde n…ôyi m…Ē, k…ôb…õr…õn…õ ka Barnabas k…Ē Pol, aŇč…õ s…ômb…Ēt…ôr m…Ē,
\v 26 afum aŇč…õ Ňčancam…ôs kiyi k…ôŇčan doru tewe ta Mariki Yesu Krist m…Ē.
\v 27 It…Ē s…ôsom Yudas k…Ē Silas Ňčak…Ē Ňčaloku nu nt…õ teyi areka ŇčaŇč…õ disr…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 28 P…ônabas Amera Ňäecempi k…Ē s…ôna s…Ē, a p…ôntes…õ f…õ a s…ônuŇčk…ôr nu mes m…Ēk…Ē n…ônt…Ētam k…ôsar…õ m…Ē, m…õn…õ mes m…Ēk…Ē m…õmar nu k…ôsump…ôr m…Ē:
\v 29 Ta n…ôs…Ēm s…õm ny…õ aloŇčn…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇčka m…Ē, n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ mecir k…Ē s…õm ny…õ ant…Ēfay m…Ē, n…ôb…Ēl…õn…õ s…Ē dalak…Ē. P…ômar n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp.
\q1 Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ a n…ôtamn…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 Nt…õ anasak asom aŇč…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčawurn…õ k…ôk…Ē Antiy…Ēk. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ŇčaloŇčka di alaŇč, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč Ňča areka ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē.
\v 31 K'aŇčkaraŇč Ňči k…Ē p…ômb…Ēt Ňča, bawo areka ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnac…ôp…ôs Ňča b…ôk…ôc.
\v 32 Yudas k…Ē Silas aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ s…Ē sayib…õ m…Ē ŇčancgbiŇč…ôr aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč k…Ē Ňčac…ôp…ôs Ňča s…Ē b…ôk…ôc d…ômoloku m…õlar…ôm.
\v 33-34 Ňäanayi d…ôndo Antiy…Ēk haŇč, k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč Ňčatolan…õ Ňča mar…ônt moforu, k…Ē afum a Antiy…Ēk Ňčasak Ňča k…ôlukus nde asom aŇčan Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 35 Mba t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Pol k…Ē Barnabas Ňčanayi Antiy…Ēk, k…ôb…õr…õn…õ k…ôŇčan k…Ē afum alar…ôm al…Ēma, Ňčact…ôks…õ, Ňčaccam s…Ē toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Mariki.
\s1 Pol k…Ē Barnabas ŇčaŇčgb…õy…õn…õ
\p 
\v 36 Nt…õ mataka m…Ēl…Ēma mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Pol oloku Barnabas: ¬ęS…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…ôk…Ēn…ôŇčk aw…õnc su aŇča s…ôdare ns…õ s…ônad…ôŇčk toloku ta Mariki m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ s…ôc…ôr…õ nt…õ Ňčayi m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Ňčasump…ôr toloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 37 Barnabas nk…Ēn …õncfaŇč k…ôken…õn…õ IsaŇč, w…ôk…Ē aŇčwe s…Ē ¬ęMark¬Ľ m…Ē.
\v 38 Mba Pol nk…Ēn …õnawos…õ f…õ ti, …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ a p…ômar f…õ k…ôl…õk…õn…õ Mark, bawo d…ôndo PaŇčfili Mark …õnasak Ňča p…ôfati k…ôc…ômb…ôr Ňča k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ ka y…õb…ôc y…Ēk…Ē anasom Ňča m…Ē.
\v 39 K…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôŇčan k…ônayeŇčk haŇč k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôgb…õy…õn…õ. Nt…õ t…Ē k…Ē Barnabas …õl…õk Mark k…Ē Ňčamb…õk…õ debil k…Ē Ňčancali k…ôk…Ē Sip…ôr.
\v 40 Nt…õ Pol …õnay…õk-y…õk Silas m…Ē, aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč Ňčantolan…õ k…Ē, Ňčactola Mariki a p…ôbum Ňča k…ômar k…Ēn disr…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.
\v 41 K…ôk…Ē k…ôŇčan, k…Ē Ňčancali t…Ēf ya Siri k…Ē Silisi, Ňčacc…ôp…ôs alaŇč aka di b…ôk…ôc.
\c 16
\s1 Timote …õnc…ômb…ôr Pol k…Ē Silas
\p 
\v 1 Pol …õnab…õr…õ dare da D…õrb…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē s…Ē List…ôr. D…ôndo w…ôc…õps…õ Yesu dar…ôŇč w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi pacwe k…Ē Timote, k…õr…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôSuyif nw…õ …õnader p…ôlaŇč Yesu m…Ē, mba kas p…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôKresi.
\v 2 Aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč aka List…ôr k…Ē Ikoniyon Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ k…ôy…Ē k…Ēn mes m…Ēt…Ēt.
\v 3 K…Ē Pol …õfaŇč k…ôkek…ôr…õ Timote, k'…õl…õk k…Ē k'…õŇčk…ônc teta aSuyif ak…Ē Ňčanayi at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, bawo f…ôp f…ônac…ôr…õ a Timote kas w…ôKresi …õnayi.
\v 4 S…ôdare ns…õ Ňčanccep…ôr m…Ē, Ňčancluks…õ moloku mm…õ asom a Yesu k…Ē abeki alaŇč a Yerusal…õm Ňčanasom Ňča k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ m…Ē, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ alaŇč at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif Ňčac…ôm…õ mi dar…ôŇč m…Ē.
\v 5 AloŇčkan…õ alaŇč Ňčacc…ôp…ôs b…ôk…ôc k…ôlaŇč disr…õ, Ňčacb…õr…õn…õ k…ôla d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk.
\s1 Pol …õnas…Ēt…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk k…ôy…õf…õ darenc
\p 
\v 6 Nt…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õyams…õ Pol k…Ē Silas k…ôloku toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Kanu at…Ēf Ňča Asi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčancali at…Ēf Ňča Firiki k…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Kalat.
\v 7 Nt…õ Ňčal…Ēt…ôrn…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misi m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…õp k…ôk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Bitini, mba Amera Ňča Yesu Ňč…õnawos…õn…õ f…õ Ňča ti.
\v 8 K…Ē Ňčasoln…õ at…Ēf Ňča Misi k…Ē Ňčantor dare da Torowas.
\v 9 Pibi disr…õ k…Ē Pol …Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk k…ôy…õf…õ ka darenc. Ti disr…õ, w…ôka Masedon p…ôc…ôm…õ k…Ē k…ôs…ôk p…ôcl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôder Masedon, m…ômar su!¬Ľ
\v 10 Pol …õnades…Ēt…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk kaŇčk…Ē, k…Ē s…ônt…õn katina k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča Masedon, s…ôcboc ti a Kanu k…ôwe su k…ôk…Ēcam di toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Yesu.
\s1 Ludy k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Mariki Yesu
\p 
\v 11 K…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ Torowas k…Ē s…ôyekti ab…õla k…Ē s…ônt…õf…ôrn…õ k…ôk…Ē ka Samotiras, d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē s…ômb…õr…õ Neyapoli.
\v 12 K…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ d…ôndo, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē Filipi, dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč da at…Ēf Ňča Masedon d…Ēl…Ēma nd…õ aka Rom alar…ôm Ňčanand…õ m…Ē. K…Ē s…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ mataka m…Ēl…Ēma dare dad…Ēk…Ē.
\p 
\v 13 Simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm k…Ē s…ôwur dare d…ôkusu k…ôŇčgb…Ēk…Ē k…ôs…ôk, nde s…ônac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôfo nk…õ s…ôntam k…ôtola Kanu m…Ē. K…Ē s…ônd…õ k…ôlok-lok…ôr aran aŇč…õ ŇčanaloŇčkan…õ di m…Ē.
\v 14 W…ôran w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi Ňča dac…Ē pacwe k…Ē Ludy, p…ôccam…ôs c…ôloto ca kar…õ. Pakom k…Ē dare da Tiyatir. W…ôkor-koru Kanu …õnayi. P…ôcc…ôŇčk…ôl su, k…Ē Mariki eŇčgbiti k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôcne belbel moloku mm…õ Pol oncloku m…Ē.
\v 15 Nt…õ anagb…ôt k…Ē d…ôromun teta Kanu m…Ē, Ludy k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ, k'ewe su k…ôyi nde nd…Ēr…Ēn mataka m…Ēl…Ēma, p…ôctola: ¬ęK…Ē n…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ a ilaŇč Mariki belbel-…õ, n…ôder nn…Ē nderem, n…ôyi nn…Ē k…Ē s…ôna.¬Ľ K'…õl…õts…õn…õ su k…ôyi di.
\s1 K…ôcaŇč…ôr ka Pol k…Ē Silas nde bili ba Filipi
\p 
\v 16 D…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma s…ôck…Ē d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, k…Ē w…ôyec…ôra w…ôcar w…ôl…Ēma ender p…ôb…ôp su, p…ôy…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk nŇč…õ Ňč…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôloku nt…õ tender m…Ē. W…ôyec…ôra nw…õ …Ēncs…Ēt…Ēn…õ ti nn…Ē ab…õ …Ēn Ňčayi m…Ē p…ôsam p…õlar…ôm teta k…ôloku k…Ēn mes mm…õ mender m…Ē.
\v 17 K…Ē w…ôyec…ôra nw…õ …õnc…õps…õ su dar…ôŇč Pol k…Ē s…ôna, p…ôckul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ acar a Kanu nk…õ k…ôyi darenc m…Ē Ňč…Ē! D…Ēp…Ē da k…ôyac d…Ē Ňčayi k…ôment…ôr nu!¬Ľ
\v 18 Nt…õ w…ôyec…ôra …Ēy…Ē mes mam…Ēk…Ē mata m…õlar…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēl…Ēl…ôs Pol dis. K'…õŇčkaf…ôl…õ, k'oloku Ňč…ĒŇčk: ¬ęTewe ta Yesu Krist ilok'…ôm, m…ôwur w…ôyec…ôra w…ôkaw…õ d…ôris!¬Ľ Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčowur k…Ē d…ôris.
\p 
\v 19 Nt…õ ab…õ …Ēn Ňčan…ôŇčk a t…Ēs…Ēt…Ēn…õ taŇčan p…ôsam t…Ēs…Ēl…ôr Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr Pol k…Ē Silas, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ Ňča nde abaŇčka Ňča dare dac…Ē ab…õ a dare f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 20 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčament…ôr Ňča aboc kiti, Ňčacloku: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ p…ôyamayama p…Ē Ňčayi k…ôb…õrs…õn…õ dare dosu. ASuyif Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ,
\v 21 aŇč…õ Ňčayi k…ôcam m…Ēy…Ē maŇčan mm…õ p…ônt…Ēmar su k…ôwos…õ k…ôy…Ē ka mi, s…ôna aŇč…õ s…ôy…Ēn…õ aka Rom m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē k…ônay ka afum Ňčay…õf…õ k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ Ňča d…ôb…ôk…ôc. K…Ē aboc kiti a dare dad…Ēk…Ē Ňčawur…õ Ňča yamos, k'asut…õ Ňča c…ôŇčgban-gban.
\v 23 Nt…õ alip k…ôsut Ňča p…ôlar…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr Ňča d…ôbili, k…Ē ab…õ Ňčaloku w…ôbum bili a p…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ Ňča belbel.
\v 24 Nt…õ w…ôbum bili ene moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr Ňča nde bili mb…õ Ňčant…Ētam k…ôwur m…Ē, k'oŇčkot…ôr…õn…õ Ňča w…ôc…ôk m…ômboŇčk ma t…Ēk.
\p 
\v 25 C…õk-c…õk c…ôndeb…ôp, Pol k…Ē Silas Ňčactola Kanu, ŇčacleŇč…ôs meleŇč mokor-kor…õ Kanu, k…Ē ayi d…ôbili ŇčaŇčne sim s…ôŇčan.
\v 26 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē ant…Ēf Ňčeyikc…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k…ôl…Ē ka bili tant…Ēf k…ôcek…ôl…õ. K…Ē cumba f…ôp c…ôŇčgbit…õ, k…Ē gbekce f…ôp yoŇčkoŇč…õ.
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôbum bili entim…õ, k'…õn…ôŇčk nt…õ cumba ca bili c…ôŇčgbit…õ m…Ē, k'owur…õ dakma d…Ēn p…ôck…Ē k…ôdifn…õ, bawo …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ a afum aŇč…õ amb…õr d…ôbili m…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ.
\v 28 K…Ē Pol oŇčkul…õ-kul…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč: ¬ęTa m…ôy…Ēn…õ p…ôl…õc, s…ôyi nn…Ē f…ôp fosu!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 29 K…Ē w…ôbum bili ewe n…õnc, k'…õmb…õr…õ kat…ôna kat…ôna, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôt…õmp…õn…õ f…Ēr ya Pol k…Ē Silas kiriŇč, p…ôcyikc…õ k…ônes…õ disr…õ.
\v 30 K'owur…õn…õ Ňča nde doru k'eyif Ňča: ¬ęAb…õ, c…ôke c…Ē p…ômar iy…Ē nt…õ tendeyac im m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 31 Pol k…Ē Silas Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôlaŇč Mariki Yesu, andek…Ēyac …ôm, m…ôna k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē kam disr…õ f…ôp.¬Ľ
\v 32 K…Ē Ňčaloku k…Ē toloku ta Mariki, k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi nde k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 33 Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…ôbum bili …õl…õk Ňča, k'eŇčkek…ôr…õ Ňča k…ôk…Ēyak gbali yaŇčan. W…ôbum bili k…Ē afum …Ēn f…ôp Ňčas…Ēt…Ē gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun teta Kanu.
\v 34 K'…õmp…õn…õ Ňča nde nd…Ēr…Ēn, k'…õnc…ômb…ôr am…õsa, k…Ē Ňčawol…ôs k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ p…ôbotu pa k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Kanu.
\p 
\v 35 Nt…õ dec d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k…Ē aboc kiti a dare Ňčasom afum aŇčan al…Ēma k…ôk…Ēloku w…ôbum bili: ¬ęM…ôsak afum akaŇč…õ.¬Ľ
\v 36 K…Ē w…ôbum bili oluks…õ moloku mam…Ēk…Ē Pol: ¬ęAboc kiti a dare Ňčasom afum nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, a isak nu. Awa n…ôwur n…ôk…Ēn…õ b…ôk…ôc yoforu.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 37 Mba k…Ē Pol oloku Ňča: ¬ęNt…õ Ňčalip oŇč k…ôsut su f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč m…Ē, ta aŇčkiti su-…õ, s…ôna aŇč…õ s…ôy…Ēn…õ aka Rom m…Ē, Ňčab…õr su d…ôbili. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč y…Ēky…Ēk y…Ē ŇčandefaŇč k…ôsak su ba? Tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēf…Ēyi, Ňčader Ňčas…ôrka Ňčasak su!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 38 K…Ē as…Ēdar ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčaluks…õ moloku mm…õ aboc kiti, k…Ē Ňčanes…õ nt…õ Ňčanane a Pol k…Ē Silas aRom Ňč…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ m…Ē.
\v 39 K…Ē aboc kiti a dare Ňčander Ňčal…õts…õn…õ Pol k…Ē Silas k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ, k…Ē Ňčasak Ňča. Ňäacloku a Ňčawur dare dand…õ.
\v 40 Nt…õ Ňčawur d…ôbili m…Ē, Pol k…Ē Silas ŇčaŇčk…Ē ndena Ludy. K…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč, k…Ē Ňčac…ôp…ôs Ňča b…ôk…ôc. K…Ē Ňčasump…ôr d…Ēp…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē.
\c 17
\s1 Pol k…Ē Silas nde dare da T…õsaloni
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ Ňčancep…ôr AŇčfipoli k…Ē Apoloni m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ dare da T…õsaloni, nde aSuyif Ňčanay…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu m…Ē.
\v 2 K…Ē Pol …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēncy…Ē m…Ē, simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm maas Ňčacgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ d…ôyecic…ôs yecempi k…Ē Ňča.
\v 3 Pol …õncment…ôr Ňča p…ôs…Ēk p…õs d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku a p…ônamar dis d…Ēl…Ēl Krist, a p…ôdey…õf…õ afi dac…Ē. Pol oncloku Ňča: ¬ęYesu nw…õ ind…ôŇčk…ôr nu tet…Ēn m…Ē, nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ Krist, w…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 4 Anas…õp haŇč k'…õŇčkaf…ôli al…Ēma Ňča dac…Ē k…Ē ŇčalaŇč ti, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôm…õ moloku ma Pol k…Ē Silas dar…ôŇč, k…ôb…ôp ka akor-koru Kanu aKresi alar…ôm, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ s…Ē aran abeki al…Ēma.
\p 
\v 5 Mba k…Ē aSuyif aka dare da T…õsaloni al…Ēma Ňčay…Ē k…ôraca. K…Ē ŇčaloŇčka afum al…õc al…Ēma d…Ēp…Ē dac…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayekti p…ôyamayama dare disr…õ. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčam…õpn…õ k…ôl…Ē ka Yason, Ňčact…õn Pol k…Ē Silas k…ôkek…ôr…õ Ňča k…ônay ka afum f…Ēr kiriŇč.
\v 6 Nt…õ Ňčanat…Ēn…ôŇčk Pol k…Ē Silas m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaliŇč…ôs Yason k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč al…Ēma f…Ēr ya ab…õ a dare kiriŇč. Ňäackul…õ: ¬ęAfum akaŇč…õ ŇčaŇčkaf…ôli-kaf…ôli doru dand…õ f…ôp m…Ē, Ňčayi oŇč nn…Ē,
\v 7 k…Ē Yason nk…Ēn …õmbaŇč Ňča!¬Ľ Afum akaŇč…õ f…ôp Ňčance moloku mm…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp oloku m…Ē, Ňčacloku a w…ôb…õ w…ôl…Ēma eyi, pacwe k…Ē Yesu!¬Ľ
\v 8-9 Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ Ňčayekti p…ôyamayama k…ônay ka afum dac…Ē. Nt…õ ab…õ a dare Ňčane ti m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčambaŇč…ôr Yason k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč p…ôsam, k…Ē Ňčasak Ňča.
\s1 Pol k…Ē Silas nde dare da Bere
\p 
\v 10 Pibi pap…Ēk…Ē disr…õ k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč Ňčasak Pol k…Ē Silas k…ôk…Ē dare da Bere. Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ di m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif.
\v 11 Akak…Ē Ňčanab…Ēt mes Ňčatas aka T…õsaloni, k…Ē Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl toloku ta Kanu belbel p…ôbotu disr…õ. Ňäack…Ēkc…õ s…Ē Yecic…ôs Yosoku belbel d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a moloku min mayi m…Ē k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē Pol k…Ē Silas ŇčaŇčloku Ňča d…ôk…ôtola Kanu m…Ē.
\v 12 K…Ē afum alar…ôm Ňča dac…Ē Ňčay…Ēn…õ alaŇč, k…ôl…õk…õn…õ aran aKresi aŇč…õ Ňčanab…õk d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ m…Ē, k…Ē arkun alar…ôm.
\p 
\v 13 Mba nt…õ aSuyif aka T…õsaloni Ňčanadec…ôr…õ a Bere s…Ē Pol eyi k…ôcam toloku ta Kanu m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčander s…Ē d…ôndo k…ôdeyekti p…ôyamayama Ňčab…õr…ôs k…ônay ka afum dac…Ē.
\v 14 K…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč Ňčamb…õlk…ôr k…ôkek…ôr…õ Pol k…ôca ka d…ôk…ôba, mba Silas k…Ē Timote Ňčayi d…ôndo Bere.
\v 15 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanasol…õ Pol m…Ē, Ňčanakek…ôr…õ k…Ē haŇč dare da At…õn. D…ôk…ôlukus daŇčan k…Ē Pol osom Ňča nde Silas k…Ē Timote Ňčayi m…Ē, a Ňčab…õl…ôr k…Ē kat…ôna kat…ôna.
\s1 Pol nde dare da At…õn
\p 
\v 16 Nt…õ Pol …õnckar Silas k…Ē Timote nde dare da At…õn m…Ē, k…ôn…ôŇčk ka dare dad…Ēk…Ē d…õlar…õ m…õr…ôŇčka k…ônacu k…Ē Pol d…õb…ôk…ôc.
\v 17 Pol …õncgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē aSuyif k…Ē al…Ēma ak…Ē Ňčanader k…ôkor-koru Kanu nde d…ôk…ôtola d'aSuyif m…Ē, p…ôcgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ s…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčancyi nde abaŇčka Ňča dare m…Ē.
\v 18 Ac…õps…õ m…õt…ôks…õ ma Epikuru k…Ē ma Seno dar…ôŇč al…Ēma Ňčander ŇčacaŇč k…Ē moloku. Al…Ēma Ňčacloku: ¬ęW…ôlok-loku …Ēf…Ē w…ôkaw…õ! C…ôke c'…õfaŇč k…ôloku tant…õ?¬Ľ Ak…Ē Ňčacloku: ¬ęW…ôkaw…õ p…ôwur…õn…õ p…ôm…Ē nt…õ endecam teta canu c…ôcik…ôra m…Ē!¬Ľ Ňäanaloku ti bawo toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Yesu k…Ē k…ôy…õf…õ k…Ēn afi dac…Ē k…Ē Pol oncloku.
\p 
\v 19 Awa k…Ē Ňčal…õk Pol, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē t…õp…õsa mp…õ ancwe Areyopako m…Ē k…ôroŇč, k…Ē Ňčayif Pol: ¬ęM…ôloku su k…ôt…ôks…õ k…ôfu kaŇčk…õ m…ôyi k…ôloku ta ki m…Ē,
\v 20 bawo moloku mam…õ m…ôyi k…ôloku m…Ē, m…Ēy…Ēn…õ l…ôŇč…ôs yosu mofu. S…ôfaŇč k…ôc…ôr…õ tedisr…õ ta mi.¬Ľ
\v 21 Awa d…ôm…Ēy…Ē ma aka dare da At…õn k…Ē acik…ôra aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē f…ôp, Ňčanccep…ôr…õn…õ di t…õm taŇčan f…ôp k…ôcloku, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, Ňčacc…ôŇčk…ôl moloku mofu.
\p 
\v 22 Pol p…ôc…ôm…õ t…õp…õsa ta Areyopako k…ôroŇč, k'oloku: ¬ęArkun a dare da At…õn, in…ôŇčk a afum asump…ôr din…õ belbel Ňč…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ.
\v 23 Nt…õ indenak…Ēt dare donu m…Ē, k'in…ôŇčk m…õr…ôŇčka monu, k'iŇčk…Ēkc…õ tetek toloŇčn…õ tonu t…Ēl…Ēma pacic ti nt…õ: ‚ÄĻTa kanu nk…õ ant…Ēc…ôr…õ m…Ē.‚Äļ Awa tes t…Ēk…Ē n…ôŇčkor-koru ta n…ônc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē, tat…Ēk…Ē yati t'inder k…ôloku nu.
\p 
\v 24 Kanu nk…õ k…ôlomp…ôs doru k…Ē daka nd…õ d…Ēy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp, nk…Ēn nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ W…ôb…õ w…ôka k…Ēm k…Ē ant…Ēf …Ēf…Ētam k…ôyi k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč nk…õ alomp…ôs…õ waca wa fum teta k…ôkor-koru k…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 25 Waca wa fum w…Ēf…Ētam k…ômar Kanu k…ôyi, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ k…ôŇčfaŇč…ôr fum t…Ēl…Ēm m…Ē. Nk…Ēn ompoc…õ afum yeyin…õ yaŇčan doru, k…ôp…õn…õ kifir k…Ē k…ôtor…õ, k…ôb…ôp ka ca y…õl…ôp…ôs ny…õ f…ôp.
\v 26 D…ôfum w…ôkin Kanu k…ôwur…õ t…Ēf ya afum alp…ôs a doru aŇč…õ f…ôp, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčand…õ ant…Ēf f…ôp k…ôroŇč m…Ē. K…Ē Kanu k…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôcic c…ôl…ônc…ôr ca t…Ēf yay…Ēk…Ē f…ôp. K…Ē k…ôlomp…ôs d…õr…ôn k…Ē k…ôt…ôn teren o teren disr…õ.
\v 27 Kanu k…ônay…Ē ti nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčat…õn k…Ē haŇč Ňčan…ôŇčk k…Ē k…ôbuma-buma disr…õ m…Ē, bawo Kanu k…ômb…Ēl…õ f…õ nw…õ o nw…õ.
\v 28 Nt…õ t…Ē n…ône moloku mam…õ: ‚ÄĻNk…Ēn …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôyi doru, nk…Ēn …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôcep…õ, nk…Ēn …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ su k…ôyi tant…õ ayi m…Ē.‚Äļ It…Ē aleŇčs…õ anu al…Ēma Ňčaloku:
\p ‚ÄĻK…ôb…ônda ka dokom da Kanu k…Ē s…ôna s…Ē s…ôyi.‚Äļ
\m 
\v 29 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a k…ôb…ônda ka dokom d…Ēn k…Ē s…ôna s…Ē s…ôyi-…õ, p…ômar f…õ a pac…õm-c…õmn…õ a Kanu k…ôwur…õn…õ k…Ē k…õma, k…Ē gb…õti, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, tasar mp…õ fum …õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ k'…õmpat…õ d…õc…õr…ôŇč d…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 30 Kanu k…ônac…õps…ôr f…õ afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi t…õm nt…õ anat…Ēc…ôr…õ mes m…Ē, mba k…ôfaŇč oŇč afum a doru f…ôp a Ňčas…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc.
\v 31 K…Ē Kanu k…ômbonc d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ k…ôndek…Ēboc…õ afum a doru f…ôp kiti k…ôlompu m…Ē. Kanu k…ônay…õk-y…õk fum nw…õ endek…Ēboc kiti kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ afum f…ôp k…ôc…ôr…õ w…ôkayi nt…õ k…ônayekti k…Ē afi dac…Ē m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 32 Nt…õ Ňčane Pol p…ôcloku teta k…ôy…õf…õ ka defi m…Ē, k…Ē al…Ēma Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôfani k…Ē, mba al…Ēma Ňčaloku: ¬ęS…ôndes…Ēc…ôŇčk…ôl …ôm k…ôloku ka tat…Ēk…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma.¬Ľ
\v 33 K…Ē Pol owur Ňča dac…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē.
\v 34 K…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčasump…ôr moloku m…Ēn k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka alaŇč a Yesu, p…ôm…Ē Denis w…ôka k…ôgba ka Areyopako, w…ôran w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Damaris, k…Ē afum al…Ēma.
\c 18
\s1 Pol nde dare da K…Ēr…õnt
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ tat…Ēk…Ē tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Pol …õy…õf…õ dare da At…õn k'…ĒŇčk…Ē K…Ēr…õnt.
\v 2 K'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp di w…ôSuyif w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Akila, nw…õ anakom dare da P…Ēnt m…Ē, p…ôt…õp k…ôcder at…Ēf Ňča Itali k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn Pirsila, bawo w…ôb…õ K…ôlod …õnaloku a aSuyif f…ôp Ňčawur Rom. K…Ē Pol …ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôb…ôp Ňča.
\v 3 Nt…õ t…õnasur…õn…õ ŇčapaŇčn…õ y…õb…ôc yin yayi m…Ē, k…Ē eyi ndaraŇčan, Ňčacb…ôc, Ňčaclomp…ôs c…ôbal.
\v 4 Simiti o simiti d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôŇčes…ôm Pol …õncgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôl…Ē ka d…ôk…ôtola da aSuyif p…ôcs…õp d…ômoloku a aSuyif k…Ē aKresi Ňčawos…õ k…ôc…ôm…õ moloku m…Ēn dar…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 5 Nt…õ Silas k…Ē Timote Ňčanator Masedon m…Ē, k…Ē Pol …õnc…ôm…õ oŇč gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…ôcam toloku t…Ēt…Ēt, p…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ aSuyif k…ôlaŇč a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ôy…õk-y…õk m…Ē.
\v 6 Mba nt…õ aSuyif Ňčancgb…õk…ôl k…Ē Ňčacl…Ēms…õn…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k'oŇčkoŇč-koŇč…ôr k…ôf…ôl ka yamos y…Ēn teta k…ôyeŇčk k…ôŇčan s…ôbomp nn…ô eyi m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęDoru donu deyi nu d…ôwaca! K…Ē ina, is…Ēk ti disr…õ. Nd…õk…ôl oŇč, nda at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif indek…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē Pol …õy…õf…õ di, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nda Titi Yusutu w…ôkor-koru Kanu w…ôl…Ēma, nw…õ k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn k…ônas…ôŇčk…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif m…Ē.
\v 8 Krisp…Ēs, w…ôb…õ ka k…ôl…Ē ka d…ôk…ôtola w…ôl…Ēma …õnalaŇč teta Mariki k…Ē aka k…ôl…Ē k…Ēn disr…õ f…ôp. K…Ē aK…Ēr…õnt alar…ôm aŇč…õ Ňčancc…ôŇčk…ôl m…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ alaŇč, k'aŇčgb…ôt Ňča d…ôromun teta Kanu.
\p 
\v 9 Pibi disr…õ k…Ē Mariki oloku Pol k…ôn…ôŇčk disr…õ: ¬ęTa m…ônes…õ! M…ôlok-loku, ta m…ôcaŇčk de,
\v 10 bawo ina iyi k…Ē m…ôna! Fum o fum …Ēf…Ēsump…ôr …ôm k…ôca k…ôy…Ē …ôm tes t…õl…õc, bawo iy…Ē afum alar…ôm dare dand…õ disr…õ.¬Ľ
\v 11 K…Ē Pol eyi Ňča dac…Ē teren tin k…Ē yof cam…ôt-tin p…ôct…ôks…õ Ňča toloku ta Kanu.
\p 
\v 12 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē Rom d…õnad…ôs Kaliy…ĒŇč k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôb…õ nde at…Ēf Ňča Akaya. K…Ē aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē Pol, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē d…ôŇčkiti.
\v 13 K…Ē Ňčaloku: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ, afum Ňč'…õfaŇč a Ňčakor-koru Kanu Ňčac…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēn dar…ôŇč, d…Ēp…Ē nd…õ denciyan…õ k…Ē nd…õ sariy…õ s…ôloku m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 14 Pol …õy…õf…õ k…ôk…Ēloku, mba Kaliy…ĒŇč oloku aSuyif: ¬ęP…ôcy…Ēn…õ a fum endif, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, tes t…õl…õc t…Ēp…ĒŇč t…Ēl…Ēma t…Ēy…Ē-…õ, k'inc…ôŇčk…ôl nu, n…ôna aSuyif!
\v 15 Mba nt…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ a d…ômoloku, d…ômewe, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti, teta sariy…õ sonu n…ôna as…ôrka s…Ē n…ôyi k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ m…Ē, n…ôna Ňč…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēm…Ēm…ôn. Ina intola f…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôboc kiti kaŇčk…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē Kaliy…ĒŇč …õmb…õl…ôs Ňča d…ôndo d…ôŇčkiti.
\v 17 K…Ē aSuyif ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčasump…ôr S…Ēst…õn w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu waca, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôsut k…Ē d…ôndo d…ôŇčkiti, mba Kaliy…ĒŇč …õnawe f…õ ti ali daka.
\s1 Pol olukus Antiy…Ēk
\p 
\v 18 K…Ē Pol owon dare da K…Ēr…õnt mataka m…Ēl…Ēma, k'ender p…ôlemb…ôrn…õ aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč, k'…õl…õk abil k…ôk…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Siri, nk…Ēn, Pirsila k…Ē Akila. K'ofonn…õ domp nde dare da SeŇčk…ôre k…ôment…ôr ka k…ôlip ka tes nt…õ …õnaderm…õ teta Kanu m…Ē.
\v 19 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ dare da Efesi m…Ē, k…Ē Pol …õsak Pirsila k…Ē Akila. K…Ē Pol …ĒŇčk…Ē k…ôl…Ē ka d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif k…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē Ňča.
\v 20 K…Ē akak…Ē Ňčantola k…Ē k…ôyi ka d…ôndo dare daŇčan k…ôr…õsna, mba …õnawos…õ f…õ.
\v 21 K'elemb…ôrn…õ Ňča p…ôcloku: ¬ęIndelukus nn…Ē ndoronu k…Ē Kanu k…ôwos…õ-…õ.¬Ľ K'…õl…õk abil dare da Efesi,
\v 22 k'ontor dare da Sesari nde …õnacop m…ôr…ônt m…Ēn m…Ē. K'…õmp…õ k…ôr…õsna Yerusal…õm k…ôk…Ēyif alaŇč. Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'ontor dare da Antiy…Ēk Ňča Siri.
\p 
\v 23 Nt…õ t…õm t…Ēl…Ēma tencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Pol …ĒŇčk…Ē k'encep…ôr at…Ēf Ňča Kalat k…Ē Firiki p…ôcc…ôp…ôs ac…õps…õ a Yesu b…ôk…ôc f…ôp.
\s1 Apolos nde s…ôdare sa Efesi k…Ē K…Ēr…õnt
\p 
\v 24 W…ôSuyif w…ôl…Ēma ancwe Apolos, …õnader Efesi. Dare da Al…õksand…ôr\f + \fr 18:24 \fq Al…õksand…ôr\ft = dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč nde Misira nde afum alar…ôm a doru f…ôp ŇčaŇčk…Ē k…ôt…ôk…ôs mes.\f* d…Ē anakom k…Ē, fum w…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôlok-loku …õnayi, p…ôc…ôr…õ s…Ē Yecic…ôs Yosoku belbel.
\v 25 D…Ēp…Ē da Mariki d…Ē anat…ôks…õ k…Ē, k…Ē k…ôsump…ôr ka mes belbel, kance k'onclok…õ, p…ôct…ôks…õ teta Yesu, mba m…õn…õ k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun ka SaŇč gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē …õnac…ôr…õ.
\v 26 K'…õy…õf…õ k…ôlok-lok…õ k…ôlaŇč disr…õ nde d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif. Nt…õ Pirsila k…Ē Akila Ňčane k…Ē k…ôlok-loku m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčal…õk k…Ē ndaraŇčan, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôt…ôks…õ k…ôc…ôr…õ k…ôŇčk…Ē k…ônabut k…Ē teta d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu m…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 Nt…õ Ap…Ēl…Ēs …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôcep…ôr ka Akaya m…Ē, k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča alaŇč ŇčaŇčgbiŇč…ôr k…Ē. K…Ē Ňčancic…õ ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč aŇč…õ Ňčayi Akaya m…Ē areka, Ňčacloku Ňča k…ôbaŇč k…Ē belbel. Nt…õ …õmb…õr…õ m…Ē, k'entes…õ afum aka di, ak…Ē k…ômar ka Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ alaŇč m…Ē.
\v 28 Bawo f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr f…Ē Ap…Ēl…Ēs …õncgb…õk…ôl…õ aSuyif f…Ēr ya afum alar…ôm kiriŇč p…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku a Yesu …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôb…õ nw…õ Kanu k…ônay…õk-y…õk m…Ē.
\c 19
\s1 Pol nde dare da Efesi
\p 
\v 1 T…õm nt…õ Apolos …õnayi K…Ēr…õnt m…Ē, Pol nw…õ …õnacep…ôr s…ôdare sa m…Ēr…Ē m…Ē, ontor dare da Efesi. K'…õmb…ôp di ac…õps…õ a Mariki Yesu dar…ôŇč al…Ēma.
\v 2 K'eyif Ňča: ¬ęN…ônas…Ēt…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ n…ônay…Ēn…õ alaŇč Yesu m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\p K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ Pol: ¬ęS…ôntane f…õ yati teta Amera Ňäecempi.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 3 K…Ē Pol eyif Ňča s…Ē: ¬ęK…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun k…ôre k…Ē n…ôs…Ēt…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p K…Ē Ňčaluks…õ Pol: ¬ęK…ôgb…ôt ka SaŇč.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 K…Ē Pol oloku: ¬ęK…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun ka SaŇč, k…ôs…ôkp…ôr mera yati k…ônayi teta Kanu. Mba SaŇč oncloku afum a ŇčalaŇč w…ôk…Ē endeder nk…Ēn tadar…ôŇč m…Ē, it…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē Yesu.¬Ľ
\v 5 Nt…õ Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē k…Ē Ňčas…Ēt…Ē k…ôgb…ôt d…ôromun tewe ta Mariki Yesu.
\v 6 K…Ē Pol endeŇč…ôr Ňča waca, k…Ē Amera Ňäecempi Ňčender Ňča, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôc…Ēp cusu nc…õ Ňčant…Ēc…ôr…õ m…Ē, Ňčacd…ôŇčk s…Ē moloku m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ Kanu k…ônasom Ňča k…ôd…ôŇčk m…Ē.
\v 7 Arkun akak…Ē Ňčancb…ôp w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 8 K…Ē Pol …õmb…õr…õ d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, p…ôclok-lok…õ di k…ôb…ôkn…õ disr…õ haŇč yof maas, p…ôcgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ, p…ôcs…õp k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôc…ôr…õ mes ma d…õb…õ da Kanu.
\v 9 Mba nt…õ ayeŇčki s…ôbomp al…Ēma Ňčancfati k…ôlaŇč m…Ē, Ňčacfani d…Ēp…Ē da Mariki nn…Ē k…ônay k…ôyi m…Ē. K…Ē Pol …Ēmb…Ēl…õ Ňča, k'…õl…õk…õn…õ ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč al…Ēma, k…Ē Ňčaw…õnn…õ k…ôs…ôk, k…Ē ŇčaŇčlok-lok…ôr…õn…õ d…Ēs…Ēk o d…Ēs…Ēk nde d…ôk…ôt…ôks…õ da Tirano.
\v 10 Tat…Ēk…Ē t…õnawon meren m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ aSuyif k…Ē aKresi aŇč…õ Ňčanayi at…Ēf Ňča Asi m…Ē k…ône toloku ta Mariki.
\s1 Awut a Sefa
\p 
\v 11 Kanu k…ôncs…ĒŇč…õ waca wa Pol k…ôy…Ē mes m…õw…õy-w…õy mm…õ m…õnacuca k…ôn…ôŇčk m…Ē.
\v 12 T…õnas…ĒŇč…õ pacb…ôc…ôs…õ acuy c…ôloto, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ k…ôpol nk…õ k…ôŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ Pol m…Ē, k…Ē ay…Ē ti-…õ, docu doncwur w…ôkayi, k…Ē y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc yocwur s…Ē w…ôkayi d…ôris.
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē aSuyif al…Ēma ŇčaŇčk…Ēs-k…Ēs mofo m…õlar…ôm, k…Ē Ňčatubucn…õ Pol k…ôb…õl…ôs ka y…ĒŇčk y…õl…õc nn…Ē acuy Ňčayi m…Ē, Ňčacloku: ¬ęIlok'…ôm: M…ôwur w…ôcuy w…ôkaw…õ tewe ta Yesu w…ôk…Ē Pol …õncam m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 14 W…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka aSuyif w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi pacwe k…Ē Sefa. Awut …Ēn at…õmp cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč Ňča Ňčancy…Ē m…Ēy…Ē mam…Ēk…Ē.
\v 15 Mba k…Ē Ňčawak k…ôb…õl…ôs Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc-…õ, Ňči Ňčoloku Ňča: ¬ęYesu, inc…ôr…õ k…Ē. K'iŇčn…õp…ôl s…Ē belbel fum nw…õ Pol …Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, mba n…ôna, an'…Ē n…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ?¬Ľ
\v 16 K…Ē fum w…ôk…Ē Ňč…ĒŇčk Ňč…õl…õc Ňč…õnayi m…Ē …õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ Ňča k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ, k'…õntam Ňča f…ôp k'ombop…ôr-bop…ôr at…õmp aŇč…õ, k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ f…ôp faŇčan dis fos k…Ē Ňčasak k…ôl…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 ASuyif k…Ē aKresi aka dare da Efesi Ňčanc…ôr…õ toloku tat…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôyi Ňča f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčalel…ôs oŇč tewe ta Mariki Yesu.
\v 18 Afum alar…ôm aŇč…õ Ňčanawos…õ k…ôlaŇč Yesu m…Ē, Ňčancder Ňčacc…õŇč f…Ēr ya afum f…ôp kiriŇč p…ôl…õc mp…õ Ňčancy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 19 K…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanay…Ēn…õ dure m…Ē, Ňčanck…õr…õ s…ôbuk s…ôŇčan sa dure k…Ē Ňčanc…Ēf si f…Ēr ya afum f…ôp kiriŇč. K…ôway ka s…ôbuk sas…Ēk…Ē k…ônab…ôp m…õnc…ômb…ôl ma gbeti wul w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt (50.000).
\v 20 Ti disr…õ k…ôtam ka Mariki disr…õ k…Ē toloku ta Kanu t…õsams…ôr k…Ē t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr.
\s1 P…ôyamayama dare da Efesi
\p 
\v 21 Nt…õ tencep…ôr m…Ē k…Ē Pol olomp…ôsn…õ k…ôk…Ē dare da Yerusal…õm p…ôccep…ôr…õn…õ t…Ēf ya Masedon k…Ē Akaya. K'oloku: ¬ęK'iŇčk…Ēb…õr…õ Yerusal…õm-…õ, m…õn…õ idek…Ēs…Ēm…Ēm…ôn Rom.¬Ľ
\v 22 K…Ē Pol osom Masedon amar …Ēn m…õr…ôŇč Timote k…Ē Erasto, mba k…Ē nk…Ēn Pol eyi mataka m…Ēl…Ēma at…Ēf Ňča Asi.
\p 
\v 23 T…õm tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ē p…ôyamayama p…Ēp…ĒŇč p…õnayi Efesi teta d…Ēp…Ē da k…ôlaŇč ka Mariki Yesu.
\v 24 W…ôgb…õc w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi di, pacwe k…Ē Demeteri, p…ôctubucn…õ k…ôlomp…ôs ka w…Ēl…Ē wa t…õr…ôŇčka mp…õ ancwe Artemi m…Ē. Agb…õc a w…Ēl…Ē wa gbeti waw…Ēk…Ē Ňčancs…Ēt…Ēn…õ wi daka d…õlar…ôm.
\v 25 K…Ē Demeteri oloŇčka agb…õc k…Ē ak…Ē Ňčancdin…õ y…õb…ôc yay…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęArkun! N…ônc…ôr…õ ti belbel a y…õb…ôc yay…õ y'andin…õ.
\v 26 Mba n…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē n…ône a nn…Ē Efesi k…ôb…ôp ka at…Ēf Ňča Asi Pol pamp…õ …õs…õp k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ afum alar…ôm k…ôlaŇč haŇč p…ôckaf…ôli Ňča mera k…ôloku a m…õr…ôŇčka mm…õ waca wa fum wolomp…ôs m…Ē, baf…Ē canu c…Ē.
\v 27 Moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…õntam k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ y…õb…ôc yosu k…ôl…õc…õ. T…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ s…Ē teta k…ôl…Ē ka t…õr…ôŇčka Artemi t…Ēy…Ē s…Ē ab…Ēc. Af…Ēde s…Ē pacloku a Artemi t…õr…ôŇčka a kanu k…Ē, kanu k…ôran nk…õ afum f…ôp ŇčaŇčkor-koru nn…Ē at…Ēf Ňča Asi, k…Ē doru k…Ērk…Ēr m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 28 Nt…õ afum Ňčane moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē m…õt…õl…õ mencep…ôr…ôr Ňča, k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęArtemi kanu ka Efesi k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč!¬Ľ
\v 29 K…Ē p…ôyamayama pap…Ēk…Ē posump…ôr dare f…ôp, k…ôt…ôŇčn…õ disr…õ k…Ē afum Ňčamb…ôps…õn…õ abaŇčka ŇčaŇčan Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč. K…Ē ŇčaliŇč…ôs asol a Pol Kayus k…Ē Aristarko, aŇč…õ Ňčanay…õf…õ Masedon m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ.
\v 30 Pol …õnafaŇč k…ôk…Ēment…ôrn…õ afum f…Ēr kiriŇč, mba ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč Ňčanawos…õn…õ f…õ k…Ē ti.
\v 31 Ab…õ al…Ēma a at…Ēf Ňča Asi, aŇč…õ Ňčanay…Ēn…õ anapa a Pol m…Ē, Ňčanasom afum nn…Ē eyi m…Ē Ňčacl…õts…õn…õ k…Ē a ta p…ôk…Ē d…ôndo abaŇčka ŇčaŇčan Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč de!
\p 
\v 32 K…Ē p…ôyamayama poncop afum dac…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčackul-kul…õn…õ nt…õ, ak…Ē Ňčackul-kul…õn…õ t…Ēk…Ē. Afum alar…ôm Ňča dac…Ē Ňčanac…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ anab…ôps…õn…õn…õ m…Ē.
\v 33 K…ônay kaŇčk…Ē dac…Ē k…Ē afum al…Ēma Ňčal…Ēm…ôr Al…õksand…ôr, nw…õ aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčanac…ĒŇč…ôs k…ôk…Ēlok-loku f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč m…Ē. K…Ē Al…õksand…ôr …õf…õk k…ôca, p…ôfaŇč k…ôlok-loku p…ôyacn…õ.
\v 34 Mba nt…õ Ňčanaden…õp…ôl a Al…õksand…ôr w…ôSuyif …Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē f…ôp f…ôy…õf…õ k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ haŇč dec m…õr…ôŇč: ¬ęArtemi kanu ka Efesi k…ôy…Ēn…õ k…ôp…ĒŇč!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 35 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôl…Ēma w…ôka di …õntam k…ôtor…õ-tor…õ afum b…ôk…ôc p…ôcloku: ¬ęArkun a Efesi, an'…Ēt…Ēc…ôr…õ a dare da Efesi d…Ēt…Ēmp…ôr k…ôbum ka k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka kanu kosu Artemi k…Ē t…õr…ôŇčka t…Ēn mp…õ pontor k…ôy…õf…õ darenc m…Ē-…õ?
\v 36 Fum …Ēf…Ētam k…ôgb…õk…ôl tat…Ēk…Ē, p…ômar n…ônd…õ n…ôcaŇčk ta n…ôb…õlk…ôr k…ôy…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ.
\v 37 Nt…õ t…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, afum aŇč…õ n…ôŇčk…õr…õ m…Ē Ňčal…ôs…ôr f…õ k…ôl…Ē kosu k…ôp…ĒŇč, Ňčal…Ēm…ôs f…õ s…Ē kanu kosu Artemi.
\v 38 K…Ē Demeteri k…Ē aw…õnc aŇča apaŇčn…õ …Ēn y…õb…ôc Ňčay…Ē k…ôbok…õn…õ teta fum-…õ, d…ôk…ôboc kiti deyi k…Ē aboc kiti Ňčayi, d…ôndo p…ômar Ňčak…Ē Ňčabok…õn…õ!
\v 39 K…Ē n…ôy…Ē s…Ē tobok…õn…õ t…Ēl…Ēma-…õ, andek…Ēlomp…ôs ti p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē nde aboc kiti ŇčaŇčloŇčkan…õ m…Ē.
\v 40 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, bawo antam k…ôbonc…õ su k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôyamayama pamp…õ k…ôyi, teta mes mam…õ mencep…ôr d…õ m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, bawo ali toloku s…ôf…Ētam k…ôs…Ēt…Ē k…ôloku nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôb…ôps…õn…õ tant…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ Nt…õ w…ôb…õ elip k…ôloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'oloku nw…õ o nw…õ k…ôlukus nde nd…Ēr…Ēn.
\c 20
\s1 Pol nde t…Ēf ya Macedon k…Ē Kresi
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ p…ôyamayama p…õsak m…Ē, k…Ē Pol …õwe ac…õps…õ a Yesu dar…ôŇč, k'…õnc…ôp…ôs Ňča b…ôk…ôc. Nt…õ elip k…ôlemb…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē Masedon.
\v 2 Nt…õ …õncep…ôr at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'…õnc…ôp…ôs alaŇč b…ôk…ôc d…ômoloku m…õlar…ôm, k'ender at…Ēf Ňča Kresi.
\v 3 K'eyi di yof maas. T…õm nt…õ …õnadefaŇč k…ôyekti ab…õla k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča Siri m…Ē, k'as…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ a aSuyif Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôy…Ē k…Ēn p…ôl…õc, k'…õnc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē d…Ēp…Ē da at…Ēf Ňča Masedon.
\v 4 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ômb…ôr k…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanay…Ēn…õ: Sopateri wan ka Purus w…ôka Bere, Aristarko k…Ē Sekondu aka T…õsaloni, Kayus w…ôka D…õrb…õ, Timote, Tikiko, k…Ē Tirofimo aka at…Ēf Ňča Asi.
\v 5 Afum akak…Ē Ňčanayi su kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčakar su Torowas.
\v 6 K…Ē s…ôna nt…õ mataka ma k…ôsata ka c…ôcom c…ôt…Ēy…Ē lebin mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôl…õk abil dare da Filipi. Mata k…ôcam…ôt disr…õ k…Ē s…ômb…ôp Ňča dare da Torowas, nde s…ônacep…ôr…õn…õ mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôcep…ôr k…ôl…ôp…ôs ka Paul dare da Torowas
\p 
\v 7 Tataka t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē ta tataka toluks…ôr, k…Ē s…ôloŇčkan…õ k…ôtepi ka k…ôcom. Pol nw…õ p…ônamar k…ôk…Ē d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē eyi k…ôlok-lok…ôr Ňča, k'…Ēmb…Ēls…õ moloku haŇč c…õk-c…õk.
\v 8 S…ôlamp s…ôlar…ôm s…ônayi d…ôndo dukul…Ē da darenc dad…Ēk…Ē s…ônaloŇčkan…õ m…Ē.
\v 9 W…ôt…õmp w…ôl…Ēma pacwe k…Ē Eyutik …õnand…õ biŇčk…ôli ba wund…õr k…ôroŇč t…õm tat…Ēk…Ē Pol onclok-loku m…Ē. K…Ē mere m…õŇčgb…ôp…ôrn…õ k…Ē, k'…õnt…õmp…õn…õ k…ôy…õf…õ dukul…Ē dak…ôroŇč da maas. AŇčk…Ēl…õk k…Ē, t…õt…ôŇčn…õ efi.
\v 10 K…Ē Pol ontor, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôsipn…õ k…Ē, k'…õl…õk k…Ē d…ôwaca, k'oloku: ¬ęTa p…ôyi nu yamayama. Eyi w…ôyeŇč!¬Ľ
\v 11 Nt…õ Pol …õmp…õ s…Ē m…Ē, k'entepi k…ôcom k…ôs…Ēm, k'oncop s…Ē moloku m…Ēn haŇč d…Ēs…Ēka. Nt…õ elip m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē.
\v 12 K'aŇčk…õr…õ w…ôt…õmp w…ôkak…Ē p…ôyi w…ôyeŇč, k…Ē t…Ēy…Ēn…õ t…õc…ôps…õ b…ôk…ôc t…Ēp…ĒŇč.
\s1 Mar…ônt k…ôy…õf…õ Torowas haŇč Mileto
\p 
\v 13 S…ôna, s…ônanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôl…õk abil k…ôk…Ē dare da As…Ēs nde Pol …õnaloku a s…ôndek…Ēl…õk k…Ē m…Ē, bawo k…ôroru k'…õnafaŇč k…ôk…Ē.
\v 14 Nt…õ …õnab…ôp su As…Ēs m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôl…õk k…Ē k…ôk…Ē ka Mitil…õn.
\v 15 Nt…õ s…ôy…õf…õ k…ôcali d…ôk…ôba d…ôndo m…Ē, k…Ē s…ômb…õr…õ d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk Kiyo. D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk dam…õr…ôŇč k…Ē s…ôŇčgbuŇč…õn…õ Sam…Ēs, tataka ta maas k…Ē s…ômb…ôp Mileto.
\v 16 Pol …õnafaŇč k…ôcep…ôr dare da Efesi tak…ôroŇč ta …õnc…ômb…ôr…ôs di-…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta owon s…Ē Asi m…Ē. Yerusal…õm …õncb…õlk…ôr k…ôb…ôp, k…Ē t…õntam k…ôyi-…õ, a d…Ēs…Ēk da k…ôsata ka tataka ta w…ôco k…ôcam…ôt d…õcb…ôp.
\p 
\v 17 T…õm nt…õ …õnayi Mileto m…Ē, k'osom dare da Efesi k…ôk…Ēwen…õ k…Ē abeki a k…ôlonkan…õ ka alaŇč aka di.
\v 18 Nt…õ Ňčander k…ôwe k…Ēn m…Ē, k…Ē Pol oloku Ňča nt…õ: ¬ęN…ônc…ôr…õ f…ôp fonu t…Ēk…Ē isump…ôr nu m…Ē, k…ôl…õk d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē nd…õ inc…ômb…ôr k…ôc…ôk at…Ēf Ňča Asi m…Ē.
\v 19 Imb…ôc…õ Mariki k…ôtor…õ banca disr…õ, icbok, ict…Ēr…Ē, bawo aSuyif ŇčancfaŇč k…ôy'em p…ôl…õc.
\v 20 Tes o tes t…õntam k…ôtes…õ nu iloku nu ti f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč k…ôk…Ē haŇč d…ôw…Ēl…Ē wonu disr…õ, ali tin im…õŇčk…ôr f…õ nu.
\v 21 K'iŇčgbiŇč…ôr s…Ē aSuyif k…Ē aKresi k…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc Ňčakaf…ôl…õ nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē, Ňčagb…õk…ôr k…ôlaŇč Mariki mosu Yesu.
\p 
\v 22 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč Amera Ňča Kanu Ňčesek…ôt im, Yerusal…õm iŇčk…Ē. Inc…ôr…õ f…õ nt…õ t…ĒŇčk…Ēb…ôp im di m…Ē,
\v 23 m…õn…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu ŇčoŇčlok'im dare o dare nt…õ: A k…ôt…Ēr…Ē k'inder, pab…õr im d…ôbili.
\v 24 Teta ina, mes ma ina dar…ôŇč meyi, t…õfaŇč ta ina t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ k…ôsom nk…õ asom im m…Ē, mes mm…õ Mariki Yesu olok'im k…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp m'ifaŇč k…ôy…Ē, nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…ôment…ôr sede sa Kibaru K…ôt…Ēt k…Ē k…ômar ka Kanu m…Ē.
\p 
\v 25 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč intas, inc…ôr…õ a n…ôf…Ēs…Ēn…ôŇčk im, n…ôna f…ôp aŇč…õ inacep…ôr k…ôcam d…õb…õ da Kanu m…Ē.
\v 26 Ilip k…ôloku nu moloku f…ôp mm…õ Kanu k…ônasom im k…ôloku nu teta k…ôyac konu m…Ē. K…Ē n…ônt…Ēy…Ē oŇč t…Ēk…Ē inat…ôk…ôs…õ nu m…Ē, te mi teyi f…õ s…Ē ti,
\v 27 bawo iloku nu m…õfaŇč ma Kanu f…ôp, ali tin im…õŇčk…ôr f…õ nu.
\v 28 N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ n…ônas…ôrka k…ôb…ôp ka alaŇč aŇč…õ Ňčayi p…ôm…Ē y…Ēc…Ēl ny…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…Ēs…ĒŇč nu k…ôk…õk m…Ē. N…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Kanu, mecir m…Ēn yati m…Ēs…Ēt…Ēn…õ Ňča.
\v 29 Inc…ôr…õ a k'indek…Ēt-…õ, afum al…õc Ňčandet…Ēr…ôs k…ôloŇčkan…õ konu p…ôm…Ē calma c…ôw…õy-w…õy nc…õ c…ônt…Ēsak y…Ēc…Ēl m…Ē.
\v 30 K'inc…ôr…õ a al…Ēma n…ôna dac…Ē yati Ňčandey…õf…õ k…ôloku yem, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ac…õps…õ alaŇč Ňčac…ôm…õ Ňča dar…ôŇč m…Ē.
\v 31 N…ôde n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ, ta n…ôp…ôler a meren mm…õ maas pibi k…Ē daŇč isak f…õ k…ôloku nu d…ôm…õnc…ôr a n…ôk…õmb…ôrn…õ!
\p 
\v 32 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč is…ĒŇč nu Kanu k…Ē toloku ta k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ k…Ēn. Toloku tat…Ēk…Ē t…õntam k…ôc…ôp…ôs nu b…ôk…ôc k…Ē k…ôs…ĒŇč nu k…õ, n…ôna aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ afum …Ēn m…Ē.
\v 33 InafaŇč f…õ p…ôsam, inafaŇč f…õ k…õma, inafaŇč f…õ yamos ya fum.
\v 34 N…ôna yati n…ônc…ôr…õ a waca wem waw…õ w'imb…ôc…õ k…ôt…õn ka yeri yem k…Ē ya afum aŇč…õ iŇčsol…õ m…Ē.
\v 35 Iment…ôr nu a k…Ē m…ôŇčb…ôc tat…Ēk…Ē-…õ, m…õn…õ n…ômar at…Ēy…Ē f…ôn…Ēnt…ôr. M…ôcc…õm-c…õmn…õ moloku ma Mariki Yesu, nk…Ēn nw…õ …õnaloku: ‚ÄĻK…ôpoc…õ k…ôncep…ôr k…ôs…Ēt…Ē.‚Äļ ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 36 Nt…õ Pol elip k…ôloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'…õnc…ôp suwu k…ôtola Kanu k…Ē Ňča f…ôp faŇčan.
\v 37 Afum f…ôp k…ôbok disr…õ Ňčan…õps…ôrn…õ Pol d…ôkilim Ňčaccup k…Ē,
\v 38 n…Ēn…Ēf…Ēr d…õnanaŇčkan…õ k…ôyi Ňča nt…õ Pol …õnaloku a Ňčaf…Ēs…Ēn…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē. Nt…õ telip m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčanc…ômb…ôr k…Ē nde d…ôk…ôt…ônta.
\c 21
\s1 Pol …ĒŇčk…Ē Yerusal…õm
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ s…ômbaŇč…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôyekti ab…õla k…ôk…Ē ka K…Ēs. D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē s…ôncep…ôr s…Ē haŇč Rodu, k…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ d…ôndo k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē dare da Patara.
\v 2 Nt…õ s…ômb…ôp di abil nŇč…õ Ňč…õnccali k…ôba k…ôk…Ē ka ntende at…Ēf Ňča Fenisi m…Ē, k…Ē s…ômb…õk…õ Ňči, k…Ē s…ôncali.
\v 3 S…ônadet…õf…ôrn…õ Sip…ôr, k…Ē s…ôsak si k…ôca k…ômeriya, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē k…ôca ka at…Ēf Ňča Siri, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôp…õ dare da Tir nde p…ônamar abil Ňčotor…õ ca y…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õnay…Ē disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 4 Nt…õ s…ônab…ôp di ac…õps…õ a Yesu m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôyi di mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč. K…ôc…ĒŇč…ôs ka Amera Ňča Kanu disr…õ k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbiŇč…ôr Pol a ta p…ôp…õ Yerusal…õm.
\v 5 Nt…õ kiyi kosu d…ôndo k…ônalip m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē. K…Ē alaŇč f…ôp Ňčanc…ômb…ôr su, k…ôy…õf…õ aran k…ôb…ôp awut haŇč k…Ē s…ôwur dare disr…õ, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôc…ôp suwu d…ôndo d…õgb…õp k…ôtola Kanu.
\v 6 Nt…õ s…ônalemb…ôrn…õ Ňča m…Ē, k…Ē s…ômb…õk…õ debil, k…Ē Ňča Ňčalukus ndaraŇčan.
\p 
\v 7 K…Ē s…ôna, k…ôl…ôp…ôs kosu k…ôk…Ēt k…Ē s…ômb…õk…õ dare da Tir k…ôk…Ē ka dare da P…ôtolemay. Nde s…ônak…Ē s…ôyif aw…õnc asu aŇča alaŇč m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ di d…Ēs…Ēk din.
\v 8 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk d…Ē s…ônay…õf…õ di k…ôk…Ē dare da Sesari. D…ôndo s…ônab…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē ka Filip, w…ôcam ka toloku t…Ēt…Ēt, nw…õ …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôkin ka afum cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč aŇč…õ anay…õk-y…õk Yerusal…õm m…Ē. K…Ē s…ôncep…ôrn…õ d…ôndo mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 9 Filip …õnay…Ē awut aran maŇčk…ôl…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanat…Ēc…ôr…õ arkun m…Ē, aŇč…õ Ňčancd…ôŇčk moloku mm…õ Kanu k…ôncmar Ňča k…ôcam m…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 Nt…õ s…ônayi di mataka m…õlar…ôm m…Ē, k…Ē sayib…õ s…ôl…Ēma s…ôntor dare da Sesari k…ôy…õf…õ ka at…Ēf Ňča Yude, pacwe k…Ē Akabus.
\v 11 Nt…õ encder nn…Ē s…ôyi m…Ē, k'…õl…õk b…õl…õt ba Pol, k'oŇčkotn…õ w…õc…ôk k…Ē waca. K'oloku: ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl nt…õ Amera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňčoloku m…Ē: Fum nw…õ …Ēy…Ē b…õl…õt bamb…õ m…Ē, tant…õ t…Ē ab…õ aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčandekot k…Ē Yerusal…õm, Ňčab…õr k…Ē at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif d…ôwaca.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 Nt…õ s…ône toloku tat…Ēk…Ē k…Ē afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi su k…ôs…ôk m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôl…õts…õn…õ Pol ta p…ôp…õ Yerusal…õm.
\v 13 Mba k…Ē Pol oluks…õ su: ¬ęTa ake t…Ē n…ômbok…õ, n…ôs…ĒŇč'em ab…ôk…ôc k…ôl…õc…õ-…õ? Iwos…õ k…ôkot kem, iwos…õ s…Ē k…ôfi kem Yerusal…õm teta tewe ta Mariki Yesu.¬Ľ
\v 14 Nt…õ anas…õp k…Ē ant…Ētam Pol d…ômoloku m…Ē, k…Ē s…ônce k…Ē. K…Ē s…ôntola: ¬ęKanu k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ t…õfaŇč ta Mariki teyi!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 15 Nt…õ s…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ mataka mam…Ēk…Ē dare da Sesari m…Ē k…Ē s…ôlomp…ôsn…õ, k…Ē s…ôl…õk d…Ēp…Ē k…ôp…õ ka Yerusal…õm.
\v 16 K…Ē s…ôsol k…Ē ac…õps…õ a Yesu al…Ēma aŇč…õ s…ônader k…ôy…õf…õ ka dare da Sesari m…Ē. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ su nda fum w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ p…ônamar s…ôyi nd…Ēr…Ēn m…Ē, pacwe k…Ē Manas…ĒŇč. W…ôSip…ôr …õnayi, …õnay…Ēn…õ w…ôc…õps…õ w…ôka Yesu dar…ôŇč k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē.
\s1 Pol ndena Sak
\p 
\v 17 K…ôb…õr…õ kosu Yerusal…õm, k…Ē aw…õnc asu aŇča alaŇč Ňčasel…õn…õ su p…ôbotu disr…õ.
\v 18 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē s…ôsol k…Ē Pol, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē ndena Sak. K…Ē abeki a k…ôloŇčkan…õ ka alaŇč a Yerusal…õm f…ôp Ňčamb…ôps…õn…õ d…ôndo.
\v 19 K…Ē Pol …õfayn…õ Ňča, k'…õy…õf…õ k…ôl…Ēm…ôr Ňča tin tin tin mes f…ôp mm…õ Kanu k…ônamar k…Ē k…ôy…Ē aSuyif dac…Ē m…Ē.
\p 
\v 20 Nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl Pol m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčayek-yek…ôs Kanu. K…Ē Ňčaloku Pol: ¬ęM…ôm…Ēm…ôn w…õnc kosu, afum asu wul w…õlar…ôm Ňčay…Ēn…õ alaŇč a Yesu k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr…õn…õ s…Ē Sariy…õ waca m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 21 Awa aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčac…õm-c…õmm…õ k…ône a k…ôt…ôks…õ kam disr…õ a m…ôloku aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčayi afum acuru dac…Ē m…Ē a Ňčasak sariy…õ sa Musa: Ta Ňčak…ônc awut, ta Ňčac…ôm…õ m…Ēy…Ē mokur ma aSuyif dar…ôŇč.
\v 22 C…ôke c'andey…Ē-…õ? Bawo ŇčaŇčk…Ēne a m…ônder nn…Ē.
\v 23 Awa m…ôy…Ē t…Ēk…Ē s…ôndelok'…ôm m…Ē. S…ôy…Ē nn…Ē arkun maŇčk…ôl…õ aŇč…õ Ňčanas…ĒŇč Kanu temer m…Ē.
\v 24 M…ôl…õk Ňča, n…ôk…Ē k…ôl…Ē k…Ēp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, m…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ k…Ē Ňča. K…Ē m…ôwos…õ-…õ, m…ôl…õk k…ôwur…õ p…ôsam pa k…ôway k…ôŇčan ka k…ôloŇčn…õ, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčafonn…õ s…ôbomp m…Ē. Ti disr…õ f…ôp f…ôndetam k…ôc…ôr…õ a mes m…Ēk…Ē as…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ tetam m…Ē f…ôp m…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…õ kance, a m…ôna s…Ē yati m…ôlel…ôs teta sariy…õ sa Musa.
\v 25 Nt…õ t…Ēy…Ēn…õ ta at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ alaŇč m…Ē, s…ôn…ôŇčk a p…ôntes…õ k…ôcic…õ Ňča reka k…ôboc…õ Ňča t…Ēnc: A ta Ňčas…Ēm s…õm ny…õ aloŇčn…õn…õ m…õr…ôŇčka m…Ē, ta Ňčamun mecir, ta Ňčas…Ēm s…õm ny…õ ant…Ēfay mera m…Ē, ta Ňčasump…ôr dalak…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē Pol …õl…õk afum aŇč…õ, k…Ē Ňčancop k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ, k'…õmb…õr…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôbonc d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ k…ôs…Ēk…ôsn…õ k…ôŇčan k…ôndelip m…Ē, k…Ē d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ andeloŇčn…õn…õ nw…õ o nw…õ m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôsump…ôr ka Pol nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ
\p 
\v 27 D…ôk…ôl…ôp…ôs…ôr da mataka mam…Ēk…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, nt…õ aSuyif al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčay…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Asi Ňčan…ôŇčk Pol k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ b…ôk…ôc ya afum f…ôp, k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr k…Ē.
\v 28 Ňäackul…õ-kul…õ: ¬ęArkun a Yisrayel, n…ôder n…ômar su! W…ôkaw…õ …õnt…ôks…õ afum f…ôp k…ôfo o k…ôfo t…Ēk…Ē t…Ēnt…Ētes…õ afum asu, sariy…õ sosu, k…Ē nn…Ē k…ôfo kaŇčk…õ m…Ē! Ali aKresi …õmb…õrs…õn…õ Ňča nn…Ē k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, k'eyik-yik…ôs k…ôfo k…ôsoku kaŇčk…õ!¬Ľ
\v 29 Ňäanabok…õn…õ nt…õ bawo t…Ēc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk Pol k…Ē Tirofimo w…ôka Efesi Ňčasol dare disr…õ, k…Ē Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a Pol …õnab…õrs…õn…õ k…Ē k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ.
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē dare m…ôlm…ôl deyi yamayama, k…Ē afum Ňčay…õf…õ waca f…ôp k…Ē Ňčasump…ôr Pol, k…Ē ŇčaliŇč…ôs k…Ē k…ôwur…õn…õ abaŇčka Ňča k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ, k'ancaŇč…ôs cumba katina.
\v 31 Nt…õ Ňčanayi k…ôs…õp k…ôdif k…Ē m…Ē, k'aŇčk…Ē paloku w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom a p…ôyamayama peyi Yerusal…õm f…ôp.
\v 32 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôp…ĒŇč nw…õ …õl…õk as…Ēdar k…Ē ab…õ aŇčan al…Ēma k…Ē Ňčay…õks…õ k…ôk…Ē di. Nt…õ aSuyif Ňčan…ôŇčk as…Ēdar aŇč…õ k…Ē ab…õ aŇčan m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasak k…ôsut Pol.
\p 
\v 33 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôs…Ēdar nw…õ …Ēnc…ĒŇčn…õ, k'osump…ôr Pol, k'osom a pakot…õ k…Ē gbekce m…õr…ôŇč. K'eyif fum nw…õ …Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē t…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē m…Ē.
\v 34 K…ônay kaŇčk…Ē dac…Ē, al…Ēma Ňčackul…õ nt…õ, ak…Ē Ňčackul…õ t…Ēk…Ē. Nt…õ …õnader p…ôyi oŇč ta eŇčne t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm teta p…ôyamayama pap…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ oloku a pakek…ôr…õ Pol d…ôk…ôdir…õ da as…Ēdar.
\v 35 Nt…õ Pol …õmb…ôp d…ôkusuŇčka m…Ē, k…Ē as…Ēdar Ňčasipn…õ k…Ē, bawo Ňčananes…õn…õ k…Ē p…ôlec p…Ēk…Ē afum ŇčanafaŇč k…ôy…Ē k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 36 K…ônay ka afum k…ônac…ôm…õ Pol dar…ôŇč, Ňčackul…õ: ¬ęPam…ôl…ôk k…Ē!¬Ľ
\s1 Pol k…ôyacn…õ k…Ēn d…ômoloku
\p 
\v 37 T…õm nt…õ anadek…ĒfaŇč k…Ē k…ôb…ôrs…õn…õ d…ôk…ôdir…õ da as…Ēdar m…Ē, k…Ē Pol eyif w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar c…ôKresi: ¬ęAŇčwos'em k…ôlok'…ôm tes t…Ēl…Ēma ba?¬Ľ K…Ē w…ôb…õ eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ônc…ôr…õ k…ôc…Ēp c…ôKresi ba?
\v 38 Baf…Ē w…ôMisira m…ôy…Ēn…õ, w…ôk…Ē …õnt…õp k…ôcs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôyamayama k…ôyi m…Ē, m…ôk…õr…õ adif…ôt afum wul maŇčk…ôl…õ (4000) nde d…ôt…õgb…ôr…õ ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 39 K…Ē Pol oloku: ¬ęAwoŇč! Ina, w…ôSuyif iy…Ēn…õ, dare da Tar…ôs at…Ēf Ňča Silisi aŇčkom im, fum w…ôka dare d…Ēp…ĒŇč de! Intol'am, m…ôwos…õ ilok-lok…ôr afum.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 40 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar owos…õ k…Ē ti. K…Ē Pol …õmp…õ k'…õnc…ôm…õ d…ôkusuŇčka, k'…õf…õk afum k…ôca. K…Ē afum f…ôp ŇčancaŇčk, k'…Ēnc…Ēp…ôr Ňča c…ôEbre, kusu ka aSuyif aka di.
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča, Abek'em aŇča!¬Ľ Pol oncloku, ¬ęN…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl oŇč moloku mm…õ iy…Ē m…õyacn…õn…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 2 Nt…õ Ňčane p…ôcc…Ēp…ôr Ňča kusu k…ôŇčan c…ôEbre m…Ē, k…Ē p…ônaŇčkan…õ k…ôy…Ē yeŇč.
\p K'oloku:
\v 3 ¬ęW…ôSuyif iy…Ēn…õ, pakom im dare da Tar…ôs, at…Ēf Ňča Silisi. Mba nn…Ē dare dand…õ d'andusum im nn…Ēna Kamaliyel nw…õ afum f…ôp Ňčanc…ôr…õ m…Ē. Nw…õ …õnt…ôks'em belbel sariy…õ sa atem asu m…Ē, k'inasump…ôr s…Ē teta Kanu belbel k…Ē ab…ôk…ôc f…ôp, p…ôm…Ē tant…õ p…ôyi n…ôna s…Ē m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē.
\v 4 K'inat…Ēr…ôs afum al…Ēma aŇč…õ Ňčanac…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Yesu dand…õ dar…ôŇč m…Ē haŇč k…Ē Ňčafi. K'iŇčkot aran k…Ē arkun, k'imb…õr Ňča d…ôbili.
\v 5 W…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf f…ôp Ňčay…Ēn…õ at…ôŇčn…õ aka ti. Inas…Ēt…ôr Ňča reka k…ôken…õ afum em aka Damas, nde inck…Ē k…ôk…Ēsump…ôr alaŇč ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē, ik…õr…õ Ňča f…Ēr ya ab…õ kiriŇč nde Yerusal…õm pak…Ēsut.
\s1 Pol …Ēl…Ēm t…õc…ôm…õ t…Ēn d…Ēp…Ē d…Ēt…Ēt
\p 
\v 6 D…Ēp…Ē inayi icl…Ēt…ôrn…õ Damas, daŇč peŇč, gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, k…Ē p…ômot p…Ēp…ĒŇč p…õy…õf…õ darenc k…Ē p…õŇčk…õl im p…ôwaŇčk…ôra.
\v 7 K'int…õmp…õn…õ d…ônt…Ēf, k'ine dim nd…õ donclok'im: ‚ÄĻSol, Sol, ta ake t…Ē m…ônt…Ērs'em-…õ?‚Äļ
\p 
\v 8 K'iyif: ‚ÄĻ Mariki, m…ôna an'…Ēf…Ē-…õ?‚Äļ
\p K'olok'im: ‚ÄĻIna, Yesu w…ôka Nasar…õt iy…Ēn…õ, nw…õ m…ôna m…ôyi k…ôt…Ēr…ôs m…Ē.‚Äļ
\v 9 Afum aŇč…õ s…ônasol m…Ē Ňčanan…ôŇčk p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pap…Ēk…Ē belbel, mba Ňčanane f…õ dim da nw…õ onclok-lok…ôr im m…Ē.
\p 
\v 10 K'iyif k…Ē: ‚ÄĻC…ôke c…Ē p…ômar iy…Ē-…õ, Mariki?‚Äļ
\p K…Ē Mariki olok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôy…õf…õ, m…ôk…Ē dare da Damas, d…ôndo aŇčk…Ēlok'…ôm t…Ēk…Ē p…ômar …ôm k…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\v 11 Mba nt…õ p…ôwaŇčk…ôra pa p…ômot pap…Ēk…Ē p…õnas…ĒŇč'em k…ôt…Ēn…ôŇčk m…Ē, afum ak…Ē s…ônasol m…Ē Ňčasump…ôr im k…ôca k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr'em haŇč k…Ē imb…õr…õ Damas.
\p 
\v 12 Mba fum w…ôl…Ēma …õnayi di pacwe k…Ē Ananiyas, p…ôc…ôm…õ t…õfaŇč ta Kanu dar…ôŇč p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku ti m…Ē. Nw…õ aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanand…õ di Ňčanac…ôr…õ d…Ēt…Ēt amera m…Ē.
\v 13 K…Ē Ananiyas ender nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, k'…õnc…ôm'em k…ôs…ôk, k'olok'im: ‚ÄĻSol, w…õnc im, m…ôluks…ôrn…õ s…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk.‚Äļ Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē k'in…ôŇčk nk…Ēn Ananiyas.
\p 
\v 14 K…Ē Ananiyas olok'im: ‚ÄĻKanu ka atem asu k…ôs…ĒŇč …ôm k…ôc…ôr…õ ka t…õfaŇč t…Ēn, m…ôn…ôŇčk W…ôlompu, m…ône s…Ē dim d…Ēn,
\v 15 bawo m…ôndek…Ēy…Ēn…õ k…Ē sede f…Ēr ya afum f…ôp kiriŇč ta nt…õ m…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē nt…õ m…ône s…Ē m…Ē.
\v 16 Nd…õk…ôl oŇč ta ake t…Ē m…ôyi k…ôwon…õ-…õ? M…ôy…õf…õ m…ôy…Ē pagb…ôt …ôm d…ôromum teta Kanu, payak kiciya kam k…ôwe ka Mariki disr…õ.‚Äļ
\s1 K…ôsom ka Pol decik…ôra
\p 
\v 17 Nt…õ ilukus Yerusal…õm m…Ē, ictola nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, k…Ē k…ôn…ôŇčk k…ônder im k…ôy…õf…õ darenc.
\v 18 Ti disr…õ, k'in…ôŇčk Mariki Yesu, nw…õ …õnalok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôkuf…õ m…ôwur Yerusal…õm, bawo Ňčaf…Ēdewos…õ k…ône sede s…ôk…Ē m…ôsump…ôr tetem m…Ē.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 19 K'iloku k…Ē: ‚ÄĻMariki, Ňčanc…ôr…õ a inck…Ē d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, icsut, icb…õr afum d…ôbili aŇč…õ ŇčanalaŇč tetam m…Ē.
\v 20 Nt…õ analoŇč mecir ma sede sam Etiy…õn m…Ē, ina w…ôkaw…õ yati inayi di, k…Ē mes maŇčan m…Ēmb…Ēt im. In'…õnam…õŇčk…õ akak…Ē Ňčanadif k…Ē m…Ē yati yamos.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 21 Mba k…Ē Mariki olok'im: ‚ÄĻM…ôk…Ē! P…ôb…Ēl…õ p…Ē ina indesom …ôm, nde at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif Ňčayi m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\s1 Pol k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom
\p 
\v 22 Afum Ňčanac…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē haŇč t…õm nt…õ …õnaloku toloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, mba nd…õk…ôl oŇč k…Ē Ňčamp…õn…õ sim Ňčacloku: ¬ęPam…ôl…ôk k…Ē! Ta pasak fum p…ôm…Ē w…ôkaw…õ p…ôyi doru.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 23 K…Ē ŇčaŇčkul…õ-kul…õ, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbal suma s…ôŇčan k…Ē Ňčal…ôm k…ôbof darenc.
\v 24 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom osom as…Ēdar …Ēn a pab…õrs…õn…õ k…Ē d…ôk…ôdir…õ daŇčan. K'oloku a pasut Pol nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ p…ôloku-loku, pac…ôr…õ te t…Ēk…Ē …Ēy…Ē nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ afum k…ôkul…õ-kul…õ tet…Ēn m…Ē.
\v 25 Nt…õ anakot Pol k…ôk…Ēsut k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Pol eyif w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôk…Ē …õnayi di m…Ē: ¬ęAwos'am k…ôsut w…ôkom w…ôRom nw…õ ant…Ēkiti m…Ē ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 26 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar nw…õ ene toloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē p…ôyif w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôp…ĒŇč, p…ôcloku: ¬ęC…ôke m…ôndey…Ē-…õ? W…ôkom w…ôRom …Ēf…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom ender k'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôlok'im kance, w…ôkom w…ôRom m…ôy…Ēn…õ ba?¬Ľ
\p K…Ē Pol owos…õ: ¬ę∆źy.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 28 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom nw…õ oloku s…Ē: ¬ęIna, p…ôsam p…õlar…ôm p'is…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôRom!¬Ľ
\p K…Ē Pol oloku: ¬ęIna, aŇčkom em ti k…ôkom…õ d…ôm.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 29 Gb…ôncana bab…Ēk…Ē, ak…Ē p…ônamar Ňčas…ĒŇč…õ Pol k…ôlok-loku m…Ē Ňčamb…Ēl…õ, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar enes…õ, k'…õnc…ôr…õ a w…ôkom w…ôRom yati nk…Ēn w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar …Ēs…ĒŇč…õ k'aŇčkot.
\s1 Pol nde f…Ēr ya aboc kiti kiriŇč
\p 
\v 30 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk w…ôb…õ w…ôka as…Ēdar nw…õ p…ôfaŇč k…ôc…ôr…õ tes t…Ēk…Ē aSuyif akak…Ē Ňčambonc…õ Pol m…Ē, k'oloku a pasik…ôli k…Ē, k'oloku s…Ē aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē aboc kiti aSuyif f…ôp k…ôloŇčkan…õ. K…Ē w…ôb…õ …õŇčk…õr…õ Pol k'…õnc…ômb…ôr k…Ē f…Ēr yaŇčan kiriŇč.
\c 23
\s1 Pol k…ôyacn…õ k…Ēn nde f…Ēr ya aboc kiti kiriŇč
\p 
\v 1 Pol p…ôgb…ôtn…õ aboc kiti aSuyif aŇč…õ, k'oloku: ¬ęK…Ē ina, aw…õnc im aŇča, amera Ňčosoku p…õs Ňč'iŇčk…Ēt…õn…õ f…Ēr ya Kanu kiriŇč haŇč m…Ēk…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 2 Ananiyas w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč oloku ak…Ē Ňčanayi Pol k…ôs…ôk m…Ē a Ňčafer k…Ē k…ôca d…ôkanca.
\v 3 K…Ē Pol oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKanu k…ôndesut …ôm, m…ôy…Ēn…õ p…ôm…Ē damba dete nd…õ anc…õm alom Ňčefer m…Ē! M…ônd…õ nn…Ē m…ôckit im p…ôm…Ē t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôloku m…Ē, mba m…ôcloku a pasut im, t…Ēk…Ē sariy…õ s…ôm…Ēn…õ m…Ē!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 4 Afum ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē, Ňčaloku: ¬ęW…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu m…ôyi s…Ē k…ôl…Ēm…ôs ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 5 K…Ē Pol oluks…õ Ňča: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča, inc…ôr…õ f…õ a nk…Ēn …Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč. It…Ē ancic d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku disr…õ disr…õ: ‚ÄĻP…ômar f…õ m…ôl…Ēm…ôs w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka afum am.‚Äļ\x - \xo 23:5 \xt ‚ÄĻP…ômar f…õ m…ôl…Ēm…ôs w…ôkiriŇč w…ôka afum am.‚Äļ \xt K…ôwur 22.28\x*¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 Nt…õ t…õnay…Ēn…õ a aloŇčkan…õ Ňčanayi k…ôs…ôk kin aSadisi k…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē aFarisi m…Ē. K…Ē Pol …õy…õf…õ k'…õmp…õn…õ dim d…ôndo aboc kiti aSuyif Ňčancyif…ôt k…Ē m…Ē: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča! Ina s…Ē, w…ôFarisi iy…Ēn…õ, wan ka aFarisi! K'anc…ômb…ôr im k…ôkiti-…õ, k…ôlaŇč kem a afi Ňčandey…õf…õ defi k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ ti!¬Ľ
\v 7 Nt…õ Pol oloku moloku mam…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôyi aFarisi k…Ē aSadisi dac…Ē, k…Ē k…ôgb…õy…õn…õ k…ôyi.
\v 8 K…Ē aSadisi Ňčaloku a k…ôy…õf…õ defi k…ôyi f…õ, m…õl…õk…õ meyi f…õ, y…ĒŇčk k…Ē arkifin yeyi f…õ. AFarisi k…ôca k…ôŇčan, ŇčanalaŇč a mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp meyi doru.
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē sim s…ômp…õ haŇč, k…Ē at…ôks…õ sariy…õ k…ôca ka aFarisi Ňčay…õf…õ k…Ē Ňčambup…ôr…õ p…ôp…ĒŇč, Ňčacloku: ¬ęS…ôn…ôŇčk f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ t…õl…õc nn…Ē fum w…ôkaw…õ eyi m…Ē! Anc…ôr…õ f…õ: T…Ēl…Ēma Ňč…ĒŇčk, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, m…õl…õk…õ molok-lok…ôr k…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 10 Nt…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôncc…ĒŇčn…õ oŇč k…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ d…ôm kiriŇč m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôp…ĒŇč enes…õ a ta Ňčawat…ôri-wat…ôri Pol, k'oloku as…Ēdar a Ňčator Ňčak…Ē Ňčal…õk Pol Ňčaluks…õ k…Ē nde as…Ēdar Ňčandir…õ m…Ē.
\p 
\v 11 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk pibi k…Ē Mariki ender Pol k…ôn…ôŇčk disr…õ, k'oloku: ¬ęM…ôb…ôkn…õ! T…Ēk…Ē m…ônay…Ēn'em sede f…Ēr ya aboc kiti nde Yerusal…õm m…Ē, m…õn…õ m…ôk…Ē s…Ē m…ôy…Ēn'em si Rom.¬Ľ
\s1 K…ôsek k…ôdif ka Pol
\p 
\v 12 Nt…õ dec d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, k'aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčasek k…ôdif Pol, k…Ē Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ k…ôs…ĒŇč…õn…õ temer k…ôt…Ēdi yeri, k…ôt…Ēmun haŇč Ňčaclip ti.
\v 13 Afum aŇč…õ Ňčanasek k…ôdif Pol kaŇčk…Ē m…Ē, Ňčanck…Ē haŇč Ňčacep…ôr afum w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ.
\v 14 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf k…ôk…Ēloku Ňča: ¬ęS…ôs…ĒŇč…õn…õ temer k…ôt…Ēdi peri ta s…ôntalip k…ôdif Pol-…õ.
\v 15 N…ôna oŇč nd…õk…ôl k…ôb…ôp ka aboc kiti aSuyif, n…ôk…Ē n…ôtola w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar p…ôk…õr…õ nu Pol p…ôm…Ē nt…õ n…ôŇčfaŇč k…ôm…Ēm…ôn tet…Ēn belbel m…Ē. S…ôna s…ônc…ôm…õ s…ôckar k…ôdif k…Ēn ta …õntab…ôp nu-…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 16 Nt…õ wan ka w…ôkir…õ ka Pol ene pacloku toloku ta k…ôc…ôp…õ k…Ē towul p…õdif…õ p…Ēn m…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē nde as…Ēdar Ňčandir…õ m…Ē, k'…õmb…õr…õ k'oloku ti Pol.
\p 
\v 17 K…Ē Pol ewe w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôl…Ēma k'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęM…ôsol…õ w…ôt…õmp nw…õ m…ôken…õ k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom, bawo …õfaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē k…ôc…ôr…õ toloku t…Ēl…Ēma.¬Ľ
\v 18 K…Ē w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôkak…Ē …õl…õk k…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē ndena w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom.
\p K'oloku k…Ē: ¬ęKelmani Pol ew'em k'olok'im a ik…õr'am w…ôt…õmp w…ôkaw…õ, a …õfaŇč k…ôs…ĒŇč'am k…ôc…ôr…õ toloku t…Ēl…Ēm.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 19 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom osump…ôr k…Ē k…ôca k…Ē Ňčawurn…õ k…ôs…ôk. K'eyif k…Ē: ¬ęAke toloku t…Ē m…ôy…Ē nt…õ m…ôfaŇč k…ôlok'im m…Ē-…õ?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 20 K…Ē w…ôt…õmp nw…õ oloku: ¬ęASuyif al…Ēma Ňčant…ôŇčn…õ a Ňčawer …ôm alna Pol m…ôtor…õn…õ Ňča k…Ē ndena aboc kiti aSuyif, p…ôm…Ē nt…õ ŇčaŇčfaŇč k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē Ňčam…Ēm…ôn tet…Ēn belbel m…Ē.
\v 21 Mba m…ôs…õp ta Ňčatam …ôm d…ômoloku de! Bawo afum w…ôco maŇčk…ôl…õ k…Ē t…Ēl…Ēm Ňča dac…Ē Ňčayi k…ôc…ôp…õ Pol towul p…õdif…õ p…Ēn. Ňäas…ĒŇč…õn…õ temer k…ôt…Ēdi yeri, k…ôt…Ēmun ta Ňčantanim k…Ē-…õ. T…õm tant…õ Ňčalip k…ôlomp…ôsn…õ. K…ôwos…õ kam gb…ôc…ôr…ôm k…Ē Ňčayi k…ôkar.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom …õm…õŇčk…ôs w…ôt…õmp nw…õ a ta p…ôl…Ēm…ôr s…Ē nw…õ o nw…õ toloku tat…Ēk…Ē oloku k…Ē m…Ē, k'…õsak k…Ē, k'…ĒŇčk…Ē.
\s1 Pol nde f…Ēr ya w…ôb…õ Felik…ôs kiriŇč
\p 
\v 23 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom ewe as…Ēdar …Ēn ap…ĒŇč m…õr…ôŇč, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęN…ôl…õk as…Ēdar masar m…õr…ôŇč (200), ay…õks…õn…õ f…ôl…õs w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč, k…Ē at…Ēmp…ôr mb…ônc…ôran masar m…õr…ôŇč (200), Ňčalomp…ôsn…õ k…ôk…Ē ka Sesari pibi-ana.
\v 24 N…ôlomp…ôs s…Ē f…ôl…õs, nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ paken…õ w…ôb…õ Felik…ôs Pol p…ôyi w…ôyeŇč m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom encic…õ Filik…ôs areka nŇč…õ Ňč…õnaloku nt…õ m…Ē:
\p 
\v 26 ¬ęIna, Kolodu Lisiyas, incic'am areka ŇčaŇč…õ m…ôna w…ôb…õ kem Felik…ôs, icyif …ôm.
\p 
\v 27 W…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ, aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčal…õk k…Ē Ňčack…Ē k…ônim. Mba alok'im a w…ôkom w…ôRom …Ēf…Ē, it'…Ēs…ĒŇč em k…ôder k…Ē as…Ēdar em k…ôbaŇč…ôr Ňča k…Ē.
\v 28 Nt…õ ifaŇč k…ôc…ôr…õ tes nt…õ ambonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē, k'intor…õn…õ k…Ē nde aboc kiti aSuyif Ňčayi m…Ē.
\v 29 K'in…ôŇčk, k'ambonc…õ k…Ē tes-…õ, k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē nk…õ k…ôŇčkot…ôr…õn…õ sariy…õ s…ôŇčan m…Ē, mba ali tes …õl…ôs…ôr f…õ nt…õ p…ômar padif…õ k…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, pab…õr k…Ē d…ôbili m…Ē.
\v 30 Nt…õ alok'im k…ôsek k…ôdif ka w…ôrkun w…ôkaw…õ oŇč m…Ē, it…Ē iŇčken'am k…Ē kat…ôna. K'ilok…õn…õ abonc…õ …Ēn tes, Ňčak…Ē Ňčabok…õn…õ tet…Ēn nn…Ē m…ôna m…ôyi m…Ē. D…ônda …Ēf…Ē l…ĒŇčtaŇč.¬Ľ
\b
\p 
\v 31 K'as…Ēdar Ňčay…Ē p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē w…ôb…õ k…ôŇčan …õnasom Ňča m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčal…õk Pol k…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ k…Ē pibi disr…õ haŇč Antipatiri.
\v 32 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē as…Ēdar al…Ēma Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ nde Ňčandir…õ m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčasak ay…õks…õn…õ f…ôl…õs Ňčakek…ôr…õ k…Ē.
\v 33 Nt…õ Ňčamb…õr…õ Sesari m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…ĒŇč areka ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Felik…ôs w…ôb…õ ka d…Ēt…Ēf, k…Ē Ňčament…ôr k…Ē Pol.
\v 34 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ ka d…Ēt…Ēf elip k…ôkaraŇč areka nŇč…õ m…Ē, k'eyif Pol w…ôka at…Ēf Ňčere m…ôy…Ēn…õ-…õ. Nt…õ ene a w…ôka Silisi …Ēy…Ēn…õ m…Ē,
\v 35 k…Ē w…ôb…õ Felik…ôs oloku: ¬ęIndec…ôŇčk…ôl …ôm k…Ē abonc…õ am tes Ňčandeder-…õ.¬Ľ K'osom a pacaŇč…ôr Pol nde bili b…Ēk…Ē b…õnayi nde abaŇčka Ňča w…ôb…õ Herodu m…Ē.
\c 24
\s1 Ambonc…õ Pol mes
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ mata k…ôcam…ôt mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē w…ôloŇčn…õ w…ôp…ĒŇč Ananiyas ontor k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf al…Ēma k…Ē w…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ w…ôkin pacwe k…Ē T…õrtulu. K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčabok…õn…õ nn…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôka d…Ēt…Ēf eyi m…Ē teta Pol.
\v 2 K…Ē w…ôb…õ ka d…Ēt…Ēf osom k'awe Pol, k…Ē T…õrtulu oncop moloku m…Ēn nt…õ: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, m…ôn'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ s…ôyin…õ b…ôk…ôc yoforu m…Ē. K…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ d…õb…õ kam k…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē k…ôs…ôkp…ôr ka mes m…Ēl…Ēma teta at…Ēf Ňčosu ŇčaŇč…õ, bawo m…ônayay Ňči nt…õ tender m…Ē.
\v 3 W…ôb…õ Felik…ôs w…ôlel…ôs kosu, s…ôŇčs…Ēt…Ē p…ôt…Ēt pap…Ēk…Ē t…õm f…ôp k…Ē mofo f…ôp. S…ôŇčyek-yek…ôs'am ti.
\v 4 Mba nt…õ int…ĒfaŇč k…ôl…õk…ôr …ôm t…õm t…õlar…ôm m…Ē, it'intolan'am k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl su ab…ôk…ôc Ňč…Ēt…Ēt disr…õ t…õm tepic.
\p 
\v 5 S…ôŇčk…Ēkc…õ a fum w…ôkaw…õ w…ôb…õr…ôs afum dac…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ, nk…Ēn …ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ aSuyif f…ôp k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ doru mofo f…ôp. W…ôkiriŇč w…ôka k…ôgba ka afum a Nasar…õt …Ēy…Ēn…õ.
\v 6-7 ∆źnafaŇč yati k…ôyik-yik…ôs k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, it…Ē s…ônasump…ôr…õ k…Ē.
\v 8 M…ôna W…ôb…õ m…ôntam k…ôyif…ôt k…Ē, m…ôt…õn k…ôc…ôr…õ k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a t…Ēk…Ē s…ômbonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē kance k…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 K…Ē aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanayi di m…Ē, ŇčambaŇč…õ T…õrtulu, k…ôcloku: ¬ęIt…Ē teyi yati!¬Ľ
\s1 Pol f…Ēr ya Felik…ôs kiriŇč
\p 
\v 10 Nt…õ w…ôb…õ ka d…Ēt…Ēf …õf…õk Pol k…ôca a p…ôlok-loku m…Ē, k…Ē Pol oloku nt…õ: ¬ęW…ôb…õ, inc…ôr…õ a meren m…õlar…ôm m…Ē m…ôyi at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…õ m…ôckiti. K…ôlaŇč kaŇčk…Ē disr…õ k'indelok…õn'am k…ôyac kem.
\v 11 T…õntacep…ôr f…õ mata w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč nt…õ imp…õ dare da Yerusal…õm k…ôk…Ēkor-koru Kanu, m…ôntam ti k…ôyif…ôt.
\v 12 Amb…ôp f'em k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, amb…ôp f'em d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif, amb…ôp f'em dare disr…õ s…ôcgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…Ē afum, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, icgbiŇč…ôr afum k…ôy…õf…ôr…õn…õ.
\v 13 Ňäaf…Ētam s…Ē k…ôcment…ôr …ôm kance ka tes t…Ēk…Ē Ňčambonc em m…Ē.
\v 14 Kance intam k…ôwos…õ nn…Ē f…Ēr yam kiriŇč a Kanu ka atem em k'iŇčkor-koru, k'inc…ôm…õ d…Ēp…Ē da Kanu dar…ôŇč nd…õ Ňča Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a yem y…Ē m…Ē. Mba ina ilaŇč nt…õ o nt…õ ancic d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku Tawureta Musa k…Ē Sayib…õ m…Ē.
\v 15 IŇčgb…õk…ôr teta Kanu t…Ēl…Ēma amera, nt…õ Ňča abonc'em mes Ňča s…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…õk…ôr mera m…Ē: It'…Ēy…Ēn…õ a Kanu k…ôndeyekti afi, alompu k…Ē at…Ēlomp.
\v 16 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ ina s…Ē iŇčs…õp t…õm f…ôp k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ amera Ňč…Ēt…Ēt f…Ēr ya Kanu k…Ē afum kiriŇč m…Ē.
\p 
\v 17 Nt…õ meren m…õlar…ôm mencep…ôr m…Ē, k'inder nn…Ē Yerusal…õm k…ôdemar afum em, k'iloŇčn…õ s…Ē Kanu.
\v 18 K…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčab…ôp im ics…Ēk…ôsn…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ, baf…Ē afum ŇčaloŇčkan…õ di, baf…Ē pacgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ de.
\v 19 M…õn…õ aSuyif a at…Ēf Ňča Asi al…Ēma ak…Ē Ňčanayi di m…Ē, Ňča Ňč…Ē p…ômar k…ôder nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē Ňčacbonc'em mes, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a Ňčant…Ēmp…ôr em mi-…õ.
\v 20 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, afum akaŇč…õ Ňčaloku tes t…õl…õc nt…õ aboc kiti aSuyif Ňčanan…ôŇčk im nt…õ Ňčanakit'im m…Ē.
\v 21 M…õn…õ p…ôy…Ēn…õ toloku t…Ēk…Ē inalok…õ dim d…Ēp…ĒŇč, ic…ôm…õ Ňča dac…Ē m…Ē de: ‚ÄĻTeta k…ôdey…õf…õ defi nk…õ ilaŇč m…Ē, it'anc…ômb…ôr'em m…Ēk…Ē kiti nn…Ē f…Ēr yam kiriŇč!‚Äļ¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 T…õnab…ôp paloku Felik…ôs belbel mes ma d…Ēp…Ē da Mariki Yesu, k'oluk…ôs…õ kiti d…Ēs…Ēk d…Ēl…Ēma, p…ôcloku: ¬ęK…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôRom Lisiyas endeder-…õ, indem…Ēm…ôn tes tonu.¬Ľ
\v 23 K…Ē w…ôb…õ ka d…Ēt…Ēf oloku w…ôs…Ēdar a p…ôcaŇč…ôr k…Ē, mba ta p…ôkot k…Ē, ta p…ôm…Ēn…õ s…Ē afum …Ēn k…ômar k…Ē mes m…Ēl…Ēma.
\s1 Pol f…Ēr ya Felik…ôs k…Ē Durusil kiriŇč
\p 
\v 24 Nt…õ mataka m…Ēl…Ēma mencep…ôr m…Ē, Felik…ôs Ňčasol k…Ē w…ôran k…Ēn, Durusil, w…ôSuyif …õnayi, k…Ē Ňčander, k…Ē Ňčasom pak…Ēwen…õ Ňča Pol. K…Ē Ňčanc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē k…ôloku ka k…ôlaŇč k…Ēn Yesu Krist.
\v 25 Mba nt…õ Pol …õnat…õf…ôrn…õn…õ moloku m…Ēn teta p…ôlompu, teta k…ôsump…ôrn…õ, k…Ē kiti nk…õ k…ôndeder m…Ē, k…Ē k…ônes…õ k…ôyi Felik…ôs. K'oloku Pol: ¬ęP…ônt…ôŇčn…õ m…Ēk…Ē tant…õ. M…ôk…Ē k…ôr…õsna. K'indes…Ēt…Ē t…õm-…õ, indes…Ēw'am.¬Ľ
\v 26 Felik…ôs …õnaf…Ēt…Ēma a Pol …ĒŇčk…Ēs…ĒŇč k…Ē p…ôsam. It'oncsom…ôs…õ t…õm f…ôp, pak…Ēwen…õ k…Ē Pol Ňčaloku-loku.
\p 
\v 27 K…Ē Ňčayi ti disr…õ haŇč k…Ē meren m…õr…ôŇč mencep…ôr, k'as…ôkp…ôr Felik…ôs d…õb…õ, k'and…ôs P…Ērsiyus F…õstus. Mba nt…õ Felik…ôs …õnafaŇč k…ôb…Ēt…ôs ab…õ aSuyif mera m…Ē, k'…õsak Pol d…ôbili.
\c 25
\s1 Awe Pol f…Ēr ya w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp kiriŇč
\p 
\v 1 K…ôd…ôs ka F…õstus d…Ēc…Ēm da d…õb…õ tataka ta maas, k'…õy…õf…õ dare da Sesari k…ôk…Ē ka Yerusal…õm.
\v 2 AloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē afum alel a d…Ēt…Ēf aSuyif ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčabok…õn…õ nn…Ē eyi m…Ē, teta Pol.
\v 3 K…Ē ŇčaŇčgb…ôc Ňčactola F…õstus k…ômar k…ôŇčan pak…õr…õ Pol Yerusal…õm, mba k…Ē Ňčalomp…ôs towul mp…õ Ňčantam k…ôdif…õ Pol d…Ēp…Ē m…Ē.
\v 4 K…Ē F…õstus oloku Ňča a ancaŇč…ôr Pol dare da Sesari, a nk…Ēn yati p…ômar p…ôk…Ē di mata mam…Ēk…Ē.
\v 5 K'endeŇč…ôr, ¬ęAfum ac…ôr…õ k…ôlok-loku aŇč…õ Ňčayi nu dac…Ē m…Ē, Ňčasol k…Ē ina, s…ôk…Ē. K…Ē fum w…ôkaw…õ …õnal…ôs…ôr tes-…õ, Ňčak…Ē Ňčal…Ēm k…ôbok…õn…õ k…ôŇčan d…ôndo.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 6 F…õstus …õnacep…ôr…õn…õ f…õ mata cam…ôt-maas, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ mata w…ôco Yerusal…õm, k'olukus dare da Sesari. D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k'…õnd…õ d…ôŇčkiti, k'osom a pak…õr…õ Pol.
\v 7 Nt…õ Pol ender m…Ē, k…Ē aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanator Yerusal…õm m…Ē ŇčaŇčk…õl k…Ē, k…Ē Ňčambonc…õ k…Ē mes m…Ēp…ĒŇč m…õlar…ôm, mm…õ Ňčanat…Ētam k…ôs…Ēk…ôs m…Ē.
\p 
\v 8 Pol oncloku k…ôyacn…õ k…Ēn: ¬ęAli tes il…ôs…ôr f…õ! Inciya f…õ sariy…õ sa aSuyif, inciya f…õ k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu, inciya f…õ \wg Sesar\wg*.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 9 F…õstus, nw…õ …õnafaŇč k…ôb…Ēt…ôs aSuyif mera m…Ē, eyif Pol: ¬ęM…ôfaŇč k…ôp…õ Yerusal…õm pak…Ēkit'…ôm di f…Ēr yem kiriŇč ba?¬Ľ
\p 
\v 10 K…Ē Pol oloku: ¬ęF…Ēr ya d…ôŇčkiti da Sesar y'inc…ôm…õ kiriŇč tant…õ, dif…Ē p…ômar pakit'im. Ali tes il…ôs…ôr…õ f…õ aSuyif, p…ôm…Ē tat…Ēk…Ē m…ôna yati m…ônc…ôr…õ ti m…Ē.
\v 11 K…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a inciya, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a iy…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ p…ômar padif'em m…Ē-…õ, if…Ētola a paŇčaŇčn…õn'em. Mba k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ a mes mam…õ ambonc'em m…Ēy…Ēn…õ f…õ kance-…õ, p…ômar f…õ nw…õ o nw…õ p…ôs…ĒŇč im Ňča. Intola ti w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp p…ôkit'im.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 12 Awa F…õstus, nt…õ Ňčalip k…ôm…Ēm…ôn mes mm…õ k…Ē amar …Ēn m…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęNt…õ m…ôloku a Sesar m…ôfaŇč a p…ôkit'…ôm m…Ē, k…ôk…Ē k…Ē m…ônder Rom p…ôk…Ēkit'…ôm.¬Ľ
\s1 Pol f…Ēr ya Akripa k…Ē Bernis kiriŇč
\p 
\v 13 Nt…õ mataka m…Ēl…Ēm m…ôncep…ôr m…Ē, w…ôb…õ Akripa k…Ē w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn Bernis Ňčander dare da Sesari, k…ôdeyif F…õstus.
\v 14 Nt…õ Ňčawak di k…ôwon m…Ē, k…Ē F…õstus …Ēl…Ēm…ôr w…ôb…õ nw…õ teta Pol, p…ôcloku: ¬ęFelik…ôs …õnasak fum w…ôl…Ēma d…ôbili.
\v 15 Nt…õ inak…Ē Yerusal…õm m…Ē, aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč k…Ē abeki a d…Ēt…Ēf aSuyif Ňčanabok…õn…õ tet…Ēn, Ňčactola k…ôdif k…Ēn.
\p 
\v 16 K'iloku Ňča a aRom Ňčaf…Ēs…ĒŇč fum k…ôdif ta w…ôkayi Ňčantat…õf…ôr…õn…õ k…Ē abonc…õ …Ēn mes-…õ, p…ôyacn…õ moloku m…Ēk…Ē ambonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 17 It'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ Ňčat…Ēwon k…ôder…õn…õ nn…Ē m…Ē. D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, k'ind…õ d…ôŇčkiti, k'isom a pak…õr…õ fum w…ôkak…Ē.
\v 18 Nt…õ abonc…õ …Ēn mes Ňčander m…Ē, ali tes Ňčambonc…õ f…õ k…Ē nt…õ inaf…Ēt…Ēn…õ k…Ē m…Ē.
\v 19 ŇäaŇčgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ d…ôm teta din…õ daŇčan, k…Ē teta Yesu w…ôl…Ēma, nw…õ efi m…Ē, mba k…Ē Pol nk…Ēn oloku a eyi w…ôyeŇč.
\v 20 K…Ē ina, nt…õ int…Ēc…ôr…õ nt…õ indeloku teta mes ma din…õ daŇčan m…Ē, k'iyif Pol, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ oŇčwos…õ k…ôk…Ē Yerusal…õm pak…Ēkiti k…Ē d…ôndo-…õ.
\v 21 Mba Pol ontola nt…õ …õfaŇč m…Ē: A w…ôb…õ kosu w…ôlel p…ôkiti k…Ē, it'…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ iloku a pacaŇč…ôr k…Ē haŇč ictam k…ôken…õ k…Ē Sesar w…ôb…õ w…ôka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 22 K…Ē Akripa oloku F…õstus: ¬ęIna s…Ē, ifaŇč k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl fum w…ôkaw…õ.¬Ľ K…Ē F…õstus oloku: ¬ęAlna m…ônc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 23 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk Akripa k…Ē w…ôkir…õ k…Ēn Bernis Ňčander…õn…õ asos Ňčayesn…õ, k…Ē Ňčamb…õr…õ nde dukul…Ē d…Ēk…Ē aŇčkiti m…Ē, k…Ē ab…õ ap…ĒŇč as…Ēdar aRom, k…Ē afum alel a dare. K…Ē F…õstus osom k'aŇčk…õr…õ Pol.
\v 24 Awa k…Ē F…õstus oloku: ¬ęW…ôb…õ Akripa, k…Ē n…ôna f…ôp fonu aŇč…õ n…ôyi su dac…Ē m…Ē, n…ôn…ôŇčk fum w…ôkaw…õ, tet…Ēn t…Ē aSuyif alar…ôm akaŇč…õ Ňčambok…õn…õ nn…Ē iyi m…Ē. K…ôy…õf…õ Yerusal…õm haŇč nn…Ē, Ňčackul…õ-kul…õ a p…ômar f…õ p…ôyi doru.
\v 25 K…Ē ina, in…ôŇčk f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ p…ômar a padif…õ k…Ē m…Ē. Mba nt…õ nk…Ēn w…ôs…ôrka ontola a w…ôb…õ kosu w…ôlel p…ôkiti k…Ē m…Ē, it'inc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôdeken…õ k…Ē Pol w…ôkaw…õ.
\v 26 Nt…õ int…Ēy…Ē nt…õ o nt…õ tosoku tecic…õ w…ôb…õ kosu w…ôlel teta fum w…ôkaw…õ m…Ē, it'iŇčk…õr…õn…õ k…Ē f…Ēr yonu kiriŇč, p…ônaŇčkan…õ m…ôna w…ôb…õ Akripa, n…ôyif…ôt k…Ē nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ is…Ēt…Ē t…Ēk…Ē indecic m…Ē.
\v 27 Bawo, p…ôwur…õn'em k…ôyi samn…õ, k…ôs…ĒŇč kelmani packek…ôr…õ Rom ta m…ôs…Ēk…ôs k…ôcic mes m…Ēk…Ē ambonc…õ k…Ē m…Ē-…õ.¬Ľ
\c 26
\s1 Pol k…ôyacn…õ k…Ēn nn…Ē Akripa eyi m…Ē
\p 
\v 1 K…Ē Akripa oloku Pol: ¬ęAwos'am k…ôloku-loku tetam.¬Ľ
\p K…Ē Pol ondot k…ôca k…ôl…õk moloku k…ôyacn…õ.
\v 2 ¬ęP…ômb…Ēt im, W…ôb…õ Akripa, k…ôn…ôŇčkn…õ m…Ēk…Ē ideyacn…õ nn…Ē m…ôyi m…Ē mes mm…õ aSuyif al…Ēma Ňčambonc em m…Ē.
\v 3 M…ônc…ôr…õ belbel mes mokur aŇča ma aSuyif k…Ē k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ ka mi. Il…õts…õn'am m…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im belbel.
\p 
\v 4 ASuyif f…ôp Ňčanc…ôr…õ nt…õ t…õnay…Ēn…õ teyi tem k…ôy…õf…õ dowut dem m…Ē, d…ôk…ôcop nt…õ inayi afum em dac…Ē Yerusal…õm m…Ē.
\v 5 Ňäanc…ôr'em k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē, Ňčantam s…Ē k…ôbonc ti, bawo f…Ēr yaŇčan yati Ňčanat…ôŇčn…õ mes k…Ē m…Ēy…Ē ma doru dem f…ôp, a c…ôFarisi c'inayi, k…ôgba ka afum ak…Ē ŇčananaŇčkan…õ k…ôyeŇčk mes din…õ dosu m…Ē.
\v 6 M…Ēk…Ē ayi k…ôkit'im, bawo iŇčgb…õk…ôr amera temer nt…õ Kanu k…ônas…ĒŇč atem asu m…Ē.
\v 7 CusuŇčka cosu nc…õ w…ôco k…Ē m…õr…ôŇč c…ôŇčsali t…õm f…ôp, daŇč k…Ē pibi, Ňčay…Ē amera k…ôs…Ēt…Ē ka k…ôl…õk…õ temer kaŇčk…Ē. W…ôb…õ, teta k…ôgb…õk…ôr amera kaŇčk…Ē k…Ē aSuyif Ňčambonc em mes.
\v 8 Teta ake t…Ē n…ônt…ĒfaŇč…õ k…ôlaŇč a Kanu k…ôŇčs…ĒŇč…õ fum k…ôf…Ēt…õ d…ôdefi-…õ?
\p 
\v 9 Ina w…ôkaw…õ yati, inac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôsim…ôs k…Ē tewe ta Yesu w…ôNasar…õt s…ôp…Ē f…ôp.
\v 10 It'inay…Ē Yerusal…õm, ina w…ôkaw…õ yati inab…õr afum acempi alar…ôm d…ôbili k…ôtam disr…õ nk…õ ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ Ňčanas…ĒŇč im m…Ē. Nt…õ Ňčancloku k…ôdif k…ôŇčan m…Ē, ina s…Ē incwos…õ ti.
\v 11 Inck…Ē d…ôw…Ēl…Ē wa d…ôk…ôtola Kanu da aSuyif f…ôp, ict…Ēr…ôs alaŇč, incgb…ôc Ňča k…ôl…Ēm…ôs tewe ta Yesu. P…ôct…õl'em nn…Ē Ňčayi m…Ē, incb…õl…ôs Ňča haŇč s…ôdare s…ôcuru.¬Ľ
\s1 Pol …Ēl…Ēm k…ôkaf…ôl…õ k…Ēn amera
\p 
\v 12 ¬ęTi t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ d…Ēs…Ēk nd…õ indek…Ē dare da Damas m…Ē, k…ôtam k…Ē k…ôsom ka ab…õ a aloŇčn…õ ap…ĒŇč.
\v 13 DaŇč d…õcfaŇč k…ôb…ôp, W…ôb…õ Akripa, k'in…ôŇčk d…ôndo d…Ēp…Ē p…ôwaŇčk…ôra mp…õ p…õnak…õl im k…Ē afum ak…Ē s…ônasol m…Ē. P…ômot mp…õ p…ônay…õf…õ d…ôk…Ēm m…Ē, pocmot p…õtas dec.
\v 14 K…Ē s…ônt…õmp…õn…õ f…ôp fosu d…ônt…Ēf, k'ine dim doclok'im c…ôEbre: ‚ÄĻSol, Sol, ta ake t…Ē m…ônt…Ēr…ôs em-…õ? Ta ake t…Ē m…ômb…ôr…õ p…ôm…Ē wana c…ôŇčgbangban ca mariki mam d…ônt…Ēf-…õ.‚Äļ
\p 
\v 15 K'iyif: ‚ÄĻMariki, an'…Ēf…Ē-…õ?‚Äļ
\p K'oluks'em: ‚ÄĻIn'…Ēf…Ē Yesu, nw…õ m…ôna m…ôyi k…ôt…Ēr…ôs m…Ē.
\v 16 Mba m…ôy…õf…õ m…ôc…ôm…õ w…õc…ôk wam k…ôroŇč. M…ôc…ôr…õ tes nt…õ t…Ēs…ĒŇč'em k…ôwur…ôr …ôm m…Ē: Iy…õk-y…õk …ôm k…ôy…Ēn…õ ka w…ôb…ôc…õ kem, m…ôy…Ēn…õ s…Ē w…ôt…ôŇčn…õ mes m…Ēk…Ē m…ôn…ôŇčk nn…Ē iyi m…Ē k…Ē m…Ēk…Ē indes…Ēwur…ôr …ôm m…Ē.
\v 17 IndebaŇč …ôm afum am akaŇč…õ d…ôwaca k…Ē at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif nda aŇč…õ indesom …ôm m…Ē,
\v 18 k…ôk…Ēmepi Ňča f…Ēr. Nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčawur d…ôk…ôbump Ňčat…õf…ôrn…õ p…ôwaŇčk…ôra, Ňčawur k…ôtam ka Sentani Ňčayi k…ôtam ka Kanu disr…õ m…Ē. K…Ē ŇčalaŇč im-…õ, Ňčandes…Ēt…Ē k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ ka kiciya k…ôŇčan, Ňčas…Ēt…Ē d…ôk…ôc…ôm…õ afum dac…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčay…Ēn…õ aka Kanu m…Ē.‚Äļ¬Ľ
\s1 Pol oloku y…õb…ôc y…Ēn
\p 
\v 19 ¬ęTi disr…õ, W…ôb…õ Akripa, iyeŇčk…ôr f…õ k…ôn…ôŇčk nk…õ k…ôŇčy…õf…õ darenc m…Ē domp.
\v 20 Mba inacam k…ôr…õsna nn…Ē afum aka Damas k…Ē aka Yerusal…õm, k…ôb…ôp ka afum aka at…Ēf Ňča Yude f…ôp haŇč at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif. Iloku Ňča k…ôs…ôkp…ôr b…ôk…ôc Ňčakaf…ôl…õ nn…Ē Kanu k…ôyi m…Ē, Ňčay…Ē m…Ēy…Ē m…Ēt…Ēt mm…õ meŇčment…ôr k…ôs…ôkp…ôr k…ôŇčan b…ôk…ôc m…Ē.
\v 21 Tant…õ t…õnas…ĒŇč…õ k…Ē aSuyif Ňčasump…ôr im nde k…ôl…Ē k…ôp…ĒŇč ka Kanu disr…õ, ŇčacfaŇč k…ôdif im.
\v 22 Mba k…ôbum ka Kanu k…ôs…ĒŇč'em k…ôyi doru haŇč m…Ēk…Ē, iy…Ēn…õ sede s…Ēn nn…Ē awut k…Ē abeki Ňčayi m…Ē. If…Ēloku nt…õ o nt…õ sayib…õ k…Ē Musa Ňčanat…Ēloku m…Ē,
\v 23 k…ôc…ôr…õ a Krist endekek…ôr…õ p…ôcuca, k'…Ēy…Ēn…õ w…ôy…õf…õ w…ôc…Ēk…Ē-c…Ēk…Ē defi-…õ, nk…Ēn endecam teta p…ôwaŇčk…ôra nn…Ē aSuyif k…Ē at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif Ňčayi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\s1 Pol k…ôfaŇč k…Ēn k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Akripa k…ôlaŇč
\p 
\v 24 Nt…õ Pol oncloku moloku m…Ēn m…õyacn…õn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē F…õstus oŇčkul…ôrn…õ: ¬ęPol c…ôp…Ē m…ôtamn…õ f…õ? K…ôt…ôk…ôs kam k…ôlar…ôm k…ôs…ĒŇč'am k…ôt…Ētamn…õ.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 25 K…Ē Pol oloku: ¬ęDaka o daka d…Ēy…Ē f'em. Intamn…õ keŇč, W…ôb…õ kem w…ôlel, F…õstus! Moloku ma kance k…Ē molompu m'iyi k…ôloku.
\v 26 W…ôb…õ …õnc…ôr…õ mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, it'iŇčlok…õ mi k…ôlaŇč disr…õ f…Ēr y…Ēn kiriŇč. Inc…ôr…õ a m…ônc…ôr…õ mes mam…Ēk…Ē f…ôp, bawo m…õnacep…ôr f…Ēr ya afum kiriŇč.
\v 27 W…ôb…õ Akripa, m…ôlaŇč sayib…õ ba? Inc…ôr…õ belbel a m…ôlaŇč Ňča!¬Ľ
\p 
\v 28 K…Ē Akripa oloku Pol: ¬ęK…Ē m…ôs…õp k…ôb…õr…õn…õ p…ôpic-…õ, m…ôŇčs…ĒŇč'em k…ôy…Ēn…õ w…ôlaŇč Krist.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 29 K…Ē Pol oloku: ¬ęT…Ēy…Ēn…õ a nd…õk…ôl k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ, tekiriŇč, intola k…Ē Kanu k…ôwos…õ-…õ, k…ôy…õf…õ m…ôna haŇč ak…Ē Ňčayi k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl im m…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, n…ôyi p…ôm…Ē ina, mba ta gbekce yay…õ yeyi ti de.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 Awa w…ôb…õ ka at…Ēf, w…ôb…õ ka s…ôdare s…ôlar…ôm, Bernis, k…ôb…ôp ka afum ak…Ē Ňčanand…õ k…Ē Ňča m…Ē f…ôp Ňčay…õf…õ.
\v 31 Nt…õ Ňčancwur m…Ē Ňčaclok…õn…õ: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ …Ēy…Ē f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ p…ômar padif…õ k…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ pab…õr k…Ē d…ôbili m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 32 K…Ē Akripa nk…Ēn oloku F…õstus: ¬ęK'antam k…ôsak fum w…ôkaw…õ p…ôt…Ē-y…Ēn…õ f…Ē ewe w…ôb…õ w…ôka Rom-…õ.¬Ľ
\c 27
\s1 AŇčkek…ôr…õ Pol Rom
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ ant…ôŇčn…õ oŇč a s…ôb…õk…õ debil k…ôk…Ē ka at…Ēf Ňča Itali m…Ē, k'as…ĒŇč Pol k…Ē afum al…Ēma ak…Ē Ňčanayi d…ôbili m…Ē w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôl…Ēma nw…õ ancwe Yuliyus m…Ē. W…ôbum ka w…ôb…õ w…ôka Rom …õnay…Ēn…õ, k'asom k…Ē k…ôk…õk…ôs Ňča.
\v 2 K…Ē s…ômb…õk…õ d…ôbil k…ôy…õf…õ ka dare da Adaramit k…ôk…Ē ka c…ôgb…õp ca Asi k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôp…õ. Aristarko w…ôMasedon w…ôka dare da T…õsaloni …õnayi su dac…Ē.
\p 
\v 3 D…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē s…ômb…õr…õ Sid…ĒŇč. Yuliyus nw…õ …Ēncy…Ē Pol mes m…Ēt…Ēt m…Ē, owos…õ k…Ē k…ôk…Ē ndena anapa …Ēn k…ôk…Ēt…õn…ôr Ňča k…ômar k…ôl…Ēma.
\v 4 Nt…õ s…ôy…õf…õ d…ôndo m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôsump…ôr k…ôca ka Sip…ôr bawo s…ôncgbofn…õ afef.
\v 5 Nt…õ s…ôncali k…ôba nk…õ m…õnc moŇčsut t…Ēf ya Silisi k…Ē PaŇčfili m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôtor dare da Mira, at…Ēf Ňča Lisi.
\v 6 D…ôndo k…Ē w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar …Ēs…Ēt…Ē d…ôndo abil nŇč…õ Ňčanak…Ēy…õf…õ dare da Al…õksand…ôr k…ôk…Ē ka Itali m…Ē, k'…õmb…õk su Ňči disr…õ.
\v 7 Mataka m…õlar…ôm disr…õ s…ôck…Ēt m…õt…õn d…ôk…ôba. P…ôcuca disr…õ p…Ē s…ônadeb…ôp Sinidi, mba nt…õ afef Ňč…õnat…Ēwos…õ su k…ôk…Ē p…ôb…Ēl…õ m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôsump…ôr agb…õp Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Kr…õt, k…Ē s…ôncep…ôr Salm…Ēn.
\v 8 K…Ē s…ôŇčgbofn…õ dobo dad…Ēk…Ē p…ôcuca disr…õ, k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôb…ôp k…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē aŇčwe ¬ęC…ôt…ônta C…ôt…Ēt,¬Ľ ta p…ômb…Ēl…õn…õ di k…Ē dare da Laseya-…õ.
\p 
\v 9 Nt…õ t…õm t…õlar…ôm tenccep…ôr, ak…Ē k…ôk…Ēt…õn…õ abil k…ôncy…Ē k…ôy…Ē d…ôm w…õyw…õy m…Ē, k…Ē mata ma k…ôsuŇč mencep…ôr-…õ. K…Ē Pol eŇčgbiŇč…ôr Ňča:
\v 10 ¬ęAnapa, in…ôŇčk a k…ôk…Ēt kosu kaŇčk…õ k…ôy…Ē w…õyw…õy. Abil k…Ē y…õcam…ôs y…Ēk…Ē yeyi Ňči disr…õ m…Ē yendel…õc…õ, s…ôna aŇč…õ s…ôyi Ňči disr…õ m…Ē yati s…ôt…Ēr…Ē.¬Ľ
\v 11 Mba w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar p…ôlaŇč w…ôgb…õk abil k…Ē w…ôka Ňči, ta ewe moloku ma Pol daka-…õ.
\v 12 Nt…õ tendeŇč…ôrn…õ ti m…Ē, k…ôt…ônta k…ônates…õ f…õ k…ôc…ôp…ôr…õn…õ d…õr…ôŇč. K…Ē ayi a abil ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ alar…ôm Ňčaloku k…ôy…õf…õ ka di Ňčab…õl…ôr Fenik, k…ôt…ônta ka Kr…õt nk…õ k…ôŇčk…ôŇčk…ôn…õ afef Ňč…õd…õr…ôŇč m…Ē.
\s1 Afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč Ňčosut d…ôk…ôba
\p 
\v 13 K…Ē afef Ňčepic Ňč…õy…õf…õ k…ôwur k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt, k…Ē Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ a Ňčantam k…ôy…Ē t…õfaŇč taŇčan. K…Ē Ňčayekti ab…õla ŇčaŇčan k…Ē Ňčasoln…õ dobo da Kr…õt, Ňčagb…õp…õn…õ di.
\v 14 P…ôwon f…õ k…Ē afef Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč Ňč…Ēk…Ē ancwe ¬ę∆źrakil…ĒŇč¬Ľ m…Ē Ňčowur k…ôy…õf…õ ka m…Ēr…Ē ma dare.
\v 15 K…Ē afef ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč…õy…õf…õ k…ôc…õrn…õn…õ abil ta antam s…Ē k…ôc…ôm…õ afef ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē kiriŇč-…õ, k…Ē s…ôsakn…õ k…Ē ŇčeŇčkek…ôr…õ su nde Ňč…õnafaŇč m…Ē.
\v 16 S…ôyi k…ôcep…ôr mokuru m…õf…õt m…Ēl…Ēma tant…Ēf, mm…õ ancwe Koda m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôntam p…ôcuca disr…õ k…ôc…ômb…ôr…ôs abil.
\v 17 Nt…õ s…ôliŇč…ôrn…õ Ňči m…Ē, k…Ē aŇč…õ Ňčayi k…ôb…ôc abil disr…õ m…Ē ŇčaŇčkot…õ Ňči b…ônda y…Ēk…Ē y…õnay…Ēn…õ y…õm…õŇčk…ôrn…õ m…Ē, Ňčacnes…õ k…ôk…ĒloŇč…õ agb…õp Ňča at…Ēf Ňča Siriti, bawo k…õr…õr…õ ka as…ônc k…ônayi di. K…Ē ŇčaŇčgbal aŇčka, mba afef Ňčosol…õ Ňča.
\v 18 Nt…õ afef Ňč…õnanaŇčkan…õ k…ôyik…ôc su m…Ē, d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbal…ôs y…õcam…ôs y…Ēl…Ēma d…ôk…ôba.
\v 19 Tataka ta maas, k…Ē ab…ôc a debil Ňčasump…ôr gbalaŇči ba abil d…ôwaca k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbal bi d…ôk…ôba.
\v 20 Mataka m…õlar…ôm disr…õ dec k…Ē c…Ēs yoncwur f…õ, afef Ňč…õcb…õk oŇč k…ôb…õk d…ôm, t…õlp…ôs k…Ē s…ôwur…õ mera k…ôyi s…Ē doru.
\p 
\v 21 Ňäanadi f…õ yeri k…ôy…õf…õ nt…õ p…ônawon m…Ē. It…Ē k…Ē Pol …õy…õf…õ k'…õnc…ôm…õ Ňča dac…Ē, k'oloku: ¬ęAnapa, p…ôcy…Ēn…õ a n…ônac…ôŇčk…ôl im ta n…ôy…õf…õ Kr…õt n…ôyekti ab…õla-…õ, k…Ē n…ômbumn…õna p…ôcuy pamp…õ p…Ēs…Ēt…Ē su, k…Ē ca ny…õ y…Ēs…Ēl…ôr su m…Ē.
\v 22 Mba nd…õk…ôl oŇč, intola a anc…ôp…ôs nu b…ôk…ôc, bawo ali fum …Ēf…Ēfi nu dac…Ē, m…õn…õ abil Ňčendel…õc…õ.
\v 23 It…Ē nn…Ē pibi m…õl…õk…õ m…Ēl…Ēma ma Kanu nk…õ iy…Ēn…õ w…ôk…Ēn k…Ē nk…õ iŇčkor-koru m…Ē, mowur…ôrn'em.
\v 24 K…Ē molok'im: ‚ÄĻTa m…ônes…õ, Pol! M…õn…õ m…ôc…ôm…õ f…Ēr ya w…ôb…õ ka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp kiriŇč, tetam t…Ē Kanu k…ôsak…õ akaŇč…õ n…ôyi abil ŇčaŇč…õ disr…õ m…Ē f…ôp k…ôyi doru.‚Äļ
\v 25 N…ôc…ôp…ôsn…õ b…ôk…ôc arkun, bawo ilaŇč t…Ēk…Ē Kanu k…ôlokun'em m…Ē tendeyi.
\v 26 Mba m…õn…õ pak…ĒloŇč…õ mokuru m…Ēl…Ēma.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 27 Pibi pa w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ p'anak…Ē paf…õc…ôr…õn…õ su k…ôba ka Adiriya. Pibi dac…Ē k…Ē ak…Ēt…õn…õ abil Ňčanc…ôr…õ a al…Ēt…ôrn…õ ant…Ēf Ňčowosu.
\v 28 K…Ē Ňčantor…õ paka pelel pakot…ôr pi k…ôb…ônda, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk a putukum p…õmb…ôp m…õt…ôr w…ôco maas k…Ē cam…ôt-tin. K…Ē Ňčanc…ĒŇčn…õ kiriŇč k…Ē Ňčawak s…Ē, k…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk a p…ôtukum p…õmb…ôp m…õt…ôr w…ôco m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč.
\v 29 Nt…õ Ňčanes…õn…õ abil k…ôcaŇč…ôr…õn…õ masar m…Ē, it…Ē Ňčanagbal…õ aŇčka maŇčk…ôl…õ tadar…ôŇč, k…Ē Ňčand…õ Ňčackar p…ôwaŇčk…ôra, mba p…ôcwon Ňča.
\v 30 Mba nt…õ ab…ôc a debil ŇčanafaŇč k…ôy…õks…ôr abil m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčantor…õ agbaŇčk…õ, Ňčacloku a Ňčak…Ē Ňčagbal aŇčka tekiriŇč ta abil.
\v 31 K…Ē Pol oloku w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar k…Ē as…Ēdar, ¬ęK…Ē afum akaŇč…õ Ňčant…Ēyi debil-…õ, n…ôf…Ētam k…ôyi doru.¬Ľ
\v 32 K…Ē as…Ēdar Ňčancopu b…ônda ya agbaŇčk…õ, k…Ē Ňčasak Ňči k…Ē Ňč…õnt…õmp…õn…õ.
\p 
\v 33 Ňäayi k…ôkar dec k…ôs…Ēk, k…Ē Pol ewen…õ f…ôp fosu k…ôk…Ēdi yeri, k'oloku: ¬ęM…Ēk…Ē tataka ta w…ôco k…Ē maŇčk…ôl…õ nt…õ n…ôyi k…ôkar, ta n…ôndi yeri m…Ē.
\v 34 Intola nu oŇč k…ôdi yeri, bawo p…ômar n…ôdi yi nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ n…ôyacn…õ m…Ē. Ali w…ôkin nu dac…Ē, k…ôfon k…Ēn ka d…ôromp k…ôf…Ēs…Ēl…ôr k…Ē!¬Ľ
\v 35 Nt…õ Pol elip k…ôloku tat…Ēk…Ē m…Ē, k'…õl…õk k…ôcom k'eyif Kanu barka f…Ēr ya afum f…ôp kiriŇč, k'entepi ki, k'…õy…õf…õ ki k…ôs…Ēm.
\v 36 K…Ē f…ôp f…ônc…ôp b…ôk…ôc k…Ē Ňčay…õf…õ k…ôs…Ēm c…ôcom.
\v 37 S…ônayi afum masar m…õr…ôŇč w…ôco cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč k…Ē cam…ôt-tin (276) ak…Ē Ňčanayi abil ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē disr…õ m…Ē.
\v 38 Nt…õ f…ôp f…ôn…õmb…ôr…õ m…Ē, k…Ē ŇčaŇčgbal mal…Ē m…õlp…ôs d…ôk…ôba nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ abil Ňč…õb…õr…õn…õ k…ôfoy m…Ē.
\s1 K…ôloŇč…õ ka abil
\p 
\v 39 Nt…õ dec d…Ēs…Ēk m…Ē, ab…ôc a debil Ňčanan…õp…ôl f…õ ant…Ēf, mba Ňčanan…ôŇčk k…õr…õr…õ, k…Ē Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôc…ĒŇč…ôs abil haŇč Ňčab…ôp ki.
\v 40 K…Ē Ňčasik…ôli aŇčka k…Ē yontor d…ôk…ôba, k…Ē Ňčasik…ôl…õn…õ s…Ē b…ônda ya yas ny…õ ancgb…õk…õ abil m…Ē. K…Ē Ňčayekti ab…õla abil d…ôk…ôro, k…Ē afef Ňč…õl…õk Ňča, k…Ē Ňč…Ēnc…ĒŇč…ôs abil k…ôca ka d…ôk…õr…õr…õ.
\v 41 Mba k…Ē ŇčaŇčk…Ē Ňčap…ôt k…õr…õr…õ acir m…õr…ôŇč dac…Ē, k…Ē k…ôro ka abil k…ôm…ôtn…õ d…õs…ônc, Ňč…õntam f…õ s…Ē k…ôc…ĒŇčn…õ kiriŇč. K…Ē yam y…Ēp…ĒŇč yender yosut abil ŇčaŇčan k…Ē Ňč…õl…ôs…ôr Ňči tadar…ôŇč.
\p 
\v 42 K…Ē as…Ēdar Ňčanc…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ôdif ka kelmani-e, ta w…ôl…Ēma p…ôŇč…õr…ôŇč p…ôy…õks…ôr Ňča.
\v 43 Mba w…ôb…õ w…ôs…Ēdar nw…õ …õnac…õm-c…õmn…õ k…ômar Pol ta efi d…ôk…ôba m…Ē, …õyams…ôr as…Ēdar k…ôy…Ē ka t…õfaŇč taŇčan, k'oloku ak…Ē Ňčanac…ôr…õ k…ôŇč…õr…ôŇč m…Ē ŇčanuŇčk…õn…õ k…ôtor d…ôk…ôba ŇčaŇč…õr…ôŇč nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ Ňčap…õ p…ôwosu m…Ē.
\v 44 Afum alp…ôs ak…Ē Ňčandel…õk c…ôbam k…Ē c…ôpom ca abil ŇčaŇč…õr…ôŇč Ňčab…ôp Ňča d…ôndo d…ôp…ôwosu. K…Ē afum f…ôp Ňčamp…õ d…ôp…ôwosu, ali w…ôkin tes t…õnas…Ēt…Ē f…õ.
\c 28
\s1 Pol eyi Malit
\p 
\v 1 Nt…õ s…ômp…õ ta t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē fum m…Ē, k'aloku su a mokuru mam…Ēk…Ē m'aŇčwe Malit.
\v 2 K…Ē afum aka di Ňčasump…ôr su belbel. K…Ē ŇčaŇčkek…ôr…õ su k…ôk…Ēsay…õ n…õnc nd…õ Ňčanac…Ēl teta w…ôcaf…ôn w…ôk…Ē …õnacop k…ôtuf k…Ē k…ôfe m…Ē.
\v 3 Pol …õnaw…õt…ôs yancan y…Ēl…Ēma ny…õ …õnayi k…ôc…Ēl d…ôn…õnc m…Ē, mba teta p…ôwon, k…Ē d…Ēf dowur yancan disr…õ k…Ē d…õnd…õt…ôrn…õ k…Ē d…ôk…ôca.
\v 4 Nt…õ aka at…Ēf ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňčan…ôŇčk d…Ēf d…õd…õt…ôrn…õ Pol d…ôk…ôca m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčalok…õn…õ: ¬ęFum w…ôkaw…õ t…Ēl…Ēma w…ôdif afum …Ēy…Ēn…õ, bawo …õnt…õp k…ôccaf…õ d…ôk…ôba, mba P…ôlompu powos…õ f…õ nk…Ēn k…ôyi doru.¬Ľ
\v 5 Mba k…Ē Pol …õw…õs abok nŇč…õ d…ôn…õnc, ali ta p…ôncu k…Ē-…õ.
\v 6 Afum akak…Ē Ňčackar a p…ôŇčk…Ēk…ôf k…Ē d…ônda abok Ňč…õnad…õt…ôrn…õ m…Ē, k…Ē p…ôy…Ēn…õ f…õ ti-…õ p…ôt…õmp…õn…õ p…ôfi. Nt…õ ŇčaŇčkar k…Ē p…ôwon ta ŇčaŇčn…ôŇčk t…Ēl…Ēm o t…Ēl…Ēm t…Ēs…Ēt…Ē k…Ē m…Ē, k…Ē Ňčas…ôkp…ôr t…õc…õm-c…õmn…õ taŇčan, k…Ē Ňčaloku a kanu k…Ē …Ēy…Ēn…õ.
\p 
\v 7 K…ôfo kaŇčk…Ē k…ôs…ôk ant…Ēf Ňč…Ēp…ĒŇč Ňč…õnayi di Ňča fum w…ôbeki w…ôp…ĒŇč w…ôka mokuru mam…Ēk…Ē w…ôl…Ēma, pacwe k…Ē Pubiliyu. Nk…Ēn …õnas…ĒŇč su d…ôkiyi d…Ēt…Ēt mata maas.
\v 8 Papa ka Pubiliyu …õnaf…ônt…ôr…õ ta …õntamn…õ-…õ, fiba k…Ē kupur yeyi k…Ē. K…Ē Pol …õmb…õr…ôr k…Ē, k'…Ēntola Kanu, p…ôcdeŇč…ôr k…Ē waca, k'…õntam…ôs k…Ē.
\v 9 Ti disr…õ k…Ē acu aka mokuru alp…ôs ak…Ē Ňčander s…Ē, k…Ē Ňča s…Ē Ňčantamn…õ.
\v 10 K…Ē aka dare Ňčalel…ôs su belbel, nt…õ s…ôndey…õf…õ k…ôk…Ē m…Ē, k'as…ĒŇč su ca y…Ēk…Ē p…ônamar su k…ôy…Ē m…Ē f…ôp.
\s1 Pol k…ôb…ôp k…Ēn Rom
\p 
\v 11 Nt…õ s…ôncep…ôr…õn…õ yof maas m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôs…Ēt…Ē abil nŇč…õ Ňč…õy…õf…õ dare da Al…õksand…ôr, k…Ē Ňčencep…ôr…õn…õ d…õr…ôŇč mokuru ma Malit m…Ē. Abil ŇčaŇč…Ēk…Ē Ňč'ancwe ¬ęDiy…Ēskur.¬Ľ
\v 12 Nt…õ s…ômb…õr…õ dare da Sirakus m…Ē, k…Ē s…ôyi di mata maas.
\v 13 K…Ē s…ôy…õf…õ d…ôndo, s…ôsoln…õ agb…õp k…Ē s…ôŇčk…Ē s…ôsump…ôr dare da Resiyo. K…Ē afef Ňča k…ôca k…ôt…Ēt Ňč…õy…õf…õ d…Ēck…Ēs…Ēk, mata m…õr…ôŇč disr…õ k…Ē s…ômb…ôp dare da Pus…Ēl.
\v 14 Dif…Ē s…ônab…ôp aw…õnc su aŇča alaŇč ak…Ē Ňčanatola su k…ôyi di mata cam…ôt-m…õr…ôŇč m…Ē. T…Ēk…Ēt tant…õ t…Ē s…ônak…Ēt k…ôb…õr…õ dare da Rom.
\v 15 Aw…õnc su aŇča alaŇč a dare da Rom aŇč…õ Ňčanane tetosu m…Ē, Ňčander k…ôfayn…õ su haŇč nde makit ma Apiyus, k…Ē nde ancwe D…ôkiyi Maas m…Ē. Nt…õ Pol …õn…ôŇčk Ňča m…Ē, k'eyif Kanu barka, k'…õmb…õr…õn…õ s…Ē k…ôc…ôp ab…ôk…ôc.
\v 16 Nt…õ s…ômb…õr…õ Rom m…Ē, k'awos…õ Pol k…ôyi taciŇča k…Ē w…ôs…Ēdar w…ôk…Ē oncbum k…Ē m…Ē.
\s1 Pol k…ôcam k…Ēn toloku t…Ēt…Ēt ta Kanu Rom
\p 
\v 17 Nt…õ mata maas mencep…ôr m…Ē, k…Ē Pol ewe afum alel aSuyif aŇč…õ Ňčanayi Rom m…Ē. Nt…õ Ňčamb…ôps…õn…õ m…Ē, k'oloku Ňča: ¬ęAw…õnc im aŇča, ali tes il…ôs…ôr…õ f…õ afum asu, ali tes il…ôs…ôr f…õ ta mes mosu mokur ma atem asu, mba Ňčanasump…ôr im nde Yerusal…õm k…Ē Ňčamb…õr im aRom d…ôwaca.
\v 18 Nt…õ ayif…ôt im m…Ē, ab…õ akak…Ē ŇčanafaŇč k…ôsak im, bawo Ňčanan…ôŇčk f…õ nt…õ o nt…õ p…ômar padif'em m…Ē.
\v 19 Mba aSuyif Ňčawos…õ f…õ. Ti t…õnas…ĒŇč'em k…ôwe kiti ka w…ôb…õ ka t…Ēf ya Rom f…ôp ta ifaŇč k…ôbonc…õ afum em tes-…õ.
\v 20 Tes tat…Ēk…Ē t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ ifaŇč k…ôn…ôŇčk…õ nu, is…ĒŇč…õ nu ti k…ôc…ôr…õ m…Ē, bawo teta k…ôgb…õk…ôr amera ka afum a Yisrayel k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ nt…õ amb…õr im gbekce yay…õ m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 21 K…Ē afum alel a Rom Ňčaloku k…Ē: ¬ęAli areka Ňč…õf…õt Ňčin s…ôs…Ēt…Ē f…õ k…ôy…õf…õ at…Ēf Ňča Yude tetam. Ali aw…õnc su aŇča w…ôkin ender f…õ p…ôloku su p…õl…õc pam.
\v 22 Mba s…ôfaŇč a s…ôn'am k…ôlok-loku m…ôna yati t…Ēk…Ē m…ônc…õm-c…õmn…õ m…Ē, bawo s…ônc…ôr…õ a k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ k…ôyi mofo f…ôp teta k…ôgba nk…õ m…ôyi m…Ē.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 23 K…Ē Ňčamboc tataka, k…Ē nt…õ d…Ēs…Ēk dad…Ēk…Ē d…õmb…ôp m…Ē alar…ôm Ňčander nda Pol k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl k…Ē. K…Ē Pol …õncment…ôr Ňča p…ôsoku p…õs d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku disr…õ mes ma d…õb…õ da Kanu f…ôp, k…ôy…õf…õ sariy…õ sa Musa k…ôb…ôp yecic…ôs ya Sayib…õ. K…ôy…õf…õ b…ôtb…ôt haŇč d…Ēf…Ēy k…Ē Pol …õncs…õp k…ôs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôlaŇč teta Yesu.
\v 24 K'…õŇčkaf…ôli afum al…Ēma k…ôlaŇč t…Ēk…Ē oncloku m…Ē, mba al…Ēma ŇčanalaŇč f…õ ti.
\v 25 Nt…õ afum Ňčancsak…ôt…õn…õ k…ôgb…õk…ôl…õn…õ disr…õ d…ôndo onclok-loku m…Ē, k…Ē Pol endeŇč…ôr nt…õ gb…ôc…ôr…ôm: ¬ęAmera Ňäecempi Ňča Kanu Ňč…õnalok-lok…ôr atem anu belbel, d…ôYecic…ôs Yosoku ya aŇčnabi Esayi,
\p 
\v 26 nt…õ t'…õnaloku:
\q1 ‚ÄĻM…ôk…Ē nn…Ē afum akaŇč…õ Ňčayi m…Ē, m…ôloku:
\q1 N…ôndewon k…ôc…ôŇčk…ôl, mba n…ôf…Ēdec…ôr…õ!
\q1 N…ôndewon k…ôgb…ôtn…õ, mba n…ôf…Ēden…ôŇčk few,
\v 27 bawo s…ôbomp sa afum akaŇč…õ s…ôf…Ētam k…ôc…ôr…õ,
\q1 Ňčasunc l…ôŇč…ôs, k…Ē Ňčam…õp f…Ēr
\q1 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčan…ôŇčk…õ yi,
\q1 nt…õ t…ĒŇčs…ĒŇč…õ ta Ňčanen…õ l…ôŇč…ôs yaŇčan.
\q1 Ta b…ôk…ôc yaŇčan y…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ Ňča k…ôc…ôr…õ,
\q1 Ňčadekaf…ôl…õ, Ňčaluks…ôrn…õ nn…Ē iyi m…Ē, t…Ēs…ĒŇč…õ itam…ôs Ňča.‚Äļ\x - \xo 28:27 \xt Esayi 6.9-10\x*
\p 
\v 28-29 N…ôc…ôr…õ a k…ôŇčaŇčn…õ ka Kanu kaŇčk…õ at…Ēy…Ēn…õ aSuyif Ňč'anak…õr…õ ki, Ňča Ňčandec…ôŇčk…ôl ki.¬Ľ
\p 
\v 30 K…Ē Pol eyi k…ôl…Ē k…ôŇčk…Ē …Ēncs…ĒŇč k…ôway m…Ē meren m…õr…ôŇč, dif…Ē ak…Ē ŇčancfaŇč k…ôn…ôŇčk k…Ē m…Ē f…ôp Ňčancb…ôp k…Ē.
\v 31 Pol p…ôccam d…õb…õ da Kanu, p…ôct…ôks…õ afum teta Mariki Yesu Krist k…ôlaŇč f…ôp disr…õ, ali tes ta ayams…ôr k…Ē-…õ.
